msgstr "Ajali!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hiss!"
msgstr "Hiss! (sauti ya mshtuko)!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh!"
msgstr "Oh!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh, no!"
msgstr "Oh, hapana!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "OH, NO!"
msgstr "OH, HAPANA!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It wasn’t me!"
msgstr "Haikuwa mimi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey's Lost Bananas"
msgstr "Ndizi zilizopotea za ngedere mdogo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey’s home is always messy. One day, Little Monkey feels hungry but his house is so messy that he cannot find his bananas to eat! He asks the other animals in the forest if  they've seen his bananas. Do you think the other animals can help Little Monkey find his lost bananas?"
msgstr "Nyumbani kwa Ngedere mdogo daima kuna vurugu  hakuna mpangilio wa vitu. Siku moja Ngedere mdogo alijiskia njaa lakini nyumba yake ina vurugu sana kiasi kwamba hawezi kuona ndizi za kula! Anawauliza wanyama wengine msituni ikiwa wameona ndizi zake. Unafikiri wanyama wengine wanaweza kumsaidia Ngedere mdogo kupata ndizi zake zilizopotea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey lives in a house in a big tree. He never puts his things in order, so his house is very messy."
msgstr "Ngedere mdogo anaishi katika nyumba kwenye mti mkubwa. Yeye huwa haweki vitu vyake kwa mpangilio, hivyo nyumba yake imechafuka sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One morning, Little Monkey could be heard shouting from his tree house. \"Where are they? They are gone! My bunch of bananas! Where have they gone?\""
msgstr "Asubuhi moja, Ngedere mdogo alisikika akipiga kelele kutoka nyumbani kwake mtini.''wako wapi? wameondoka! Mkungu wangu wa ndizi! wameenda wapi?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey asked the bee. \"Bee! Bee! Did you eat my bananas?\" \"Buzz! Buzz! Buzz!\" responded the bee. \"I eat nectar and pollen. I don’t eat bananas.\""
msgstr "Ngedere mdogo alimuuliza nyuki.''Nyuki! Nyuki! Umekula ndizi zangu?'' Zzzz! Zzzz! Zzzz! alijibu nyuki. nakula majimaji na sehemu za katikati ya maua (pollen). sili ndizi,''."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey asked the snake. \"Snake! Snake! Did you eat my bananas?\" \"Hiss! Hiss! Hiss!\" responded the snake. \"I don’t know  anything about your bananas. Don’t disturb me!\""
msgstr "Ngedere mdogo alimuuliza nyoka.''Nyoka! Nyoka! Umekula ndizi zangu?' ''Ssss! Ssss! Ssss!'' Nyoka alijibu. ''Sijui chochote kuhusu ndizi zako. usinisumbue mimi!''!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey was hungry! \"I have searched everywhere! Inside and outside... but my bananas are gone!\""
msgstr "Ngedere mdogo alikuwa na njaa! ''Nimetafuta kila mahali ndani na nje... lakini ndizi zangu hazipo!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He kept searching, looking on the table and under the bed. \"I still can’t find them! I can’t find my bananas!\""
msgstr "Aliendelea kuzitafuta, anaangalia juu ya meza na chini ya kitanda, ''lakini siwezi kuzipata! Siwezi kuzipata ndizi zangu!\"\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey became very angry. He stomped his feet, crying, \"I'm so hungry! My bananas are gone, and I have nothing to eat!\""
msgstr "Ngedere mdogo alikasirika sana. Alipiga miguu chini kwa nguvu, \"Nimekasirika sana! Ndizi zangu hazipo, Na sina kitu cha kula!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Monkey looked sadly out from his balcony. \"Ah! Wait...\"he said. \"Those are banana peels! 1...2...3...4... so many!\""
msgstr "Kutokea kwenye veranda yake Ngedere mdogo alionekana mwenye huzuni. \"Ah! subiri....\" alisema. Yale ni maganda ya ndizi! 1.... 2... 3... 4... mengi sana!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh! There's the rabbit! So he’s the one who ate my bananas!\""
msgstr "''Oh! Kuna sungura! Kwa hiyo ndiye aliyekula ndizi zangu!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Rabbit! You’re eating my bananas!” shouted Little Monkey. \"No, Little Monkey. I’m not eating your bananas,\" responded the rabbit. \"Look over there. I grow bananas!\""
msgstr "''Sungura! Unakula ndizi zangu!'' Ngedere mdogo alipiga kelele. Hapana Ngedere mdogo. Sijala ndizi zako.''Sungura alijibu.'' Angalia pale. Ninalima ndizi!''!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The rabbit came over to the base of Little Monkey's tree. \"You sound very hungry,\" Rabbit said. \"Here - take a bunch of my bananas.\" Little Monkey was happy. \"Thank you! Thank you, Rabbit! But...\""
msgstr "Sungura alienda kwenye shina la mti wa Ngedere mdogo. \"Unasikia njaa sana,'' Sungura alisema. ''Chukua hapa kichane cha ndizi zangu.'' Ngedere mdogo alifurahi. ''Asante! Asante, Sungura! Ila...''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Who... Who...Who took MY bananas?\""
msgstr "''Nani... Nani... Nani amechukua ndizi zangu?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Suddenly, Little Monkey remembered. \"Oh... Now I recall! I was very hungry last night. I ate all the bananas!\""
msgstr "Ghafla, Ngedere mdogo alikumbuka. ''Oh... Sasa nakumbuka! nilikuwa na njaa sana jana usiku. Nikala ndizi zote!''!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Busy Mother Hen"
msgstr "Mama Kuku Mwenye shughuli nyingi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen sits patiently waiting for her eggs to hatch. How long will it take? Is she going to miss the fair?"
msgstr "Mama kuku amekaa kwa subira anasubiri mayai yake yaanguliwe, Yatachukua muda gani? Je atakosa maonyesho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen sits on her eggs. She waits and waits for her eggs to hatch."
msgstr "Mama kuku amekaa kwenye mayai yake, Anasubiri na kusubiri mayai yake yaanguliwe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Goat passes by.\"Will you go to the fair with me?” she asks Mother Hen. \"I'm busy with my eggs,\" Mother Hen answers."
msgstr "Mama mbuzi anapita. Je utakwenda na mimi kwenye maonyesho?'' Anamuuliza Mama Kuku, ''Nina shughuli nyingi na mayai yangu,'' Mama kuku alijibu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Pig passes by. \"Will you go to the fair with me?\" she asks. \"I'm busy with my eggs,” answers Mother Hen."
msgstr "Mama nguruwe anapita.,''Je utakwenda na mimi kwenye maonyesho? ''Anauliza.''Nina shughuli nyingi na mayai yangu,\" anasema Mama Kuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One, two, three, four, five, six. Six round eggs!"
msgstr "Moja, Mbili, tatu, nne, tano, sita. Mzunguko wa mayai sita!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Cow passes by. \"Will you go to the fair with me?\" she asks Mother Hen."
msgstr "Mama Ngo'mbe anapita. \"Je utakwenda na mimi kwenye maonyesho?'' Anamuuliza mama kuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I'm busy with my eggs,\" answers Mother Hen."
msgstr "''Nina shughuli nyingi na mayai yangu,'' anajibu mama kuku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen waits and waits. \"When will I see my chicks?\" she wonders."
msgstr "Mama Kuku anasubiri na kusubiri. Ni lini nitaviona vifaranga vyangu?''anashangaa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen feels something. What's happening?"
msgstr "Mama Kuku anahisi kitu. Nini kinaendelea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One, two, three, four, five, six. Crack! Crack! Crack! Crack! Crack! Crack!"
msgstr "Moja, mbili, tatu, nne, tano, sita Krack! Krack! Krack! Krack! Krack! Krack!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Six chicks have hatched."
msgstr "Vifaranga sita vimetotolewa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen is happy with her lovely chicks."
msgstr "Mama kuku anafurahi na vifaranga vyake vyakupendeza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Then she remembers. There is a fair today! Mother Goat, Mother Pig and Mother Cow have already left. Mother Hen is ready now. She will take her chicks to the fair. One, two, three, four, five, six!"
msgstr "Kisha akakumbuka. Kuna maonyesho leo! Mama Mbuzi, Mama Nguruwe na Mama Ng'ombe wameshaondoka. Mama kuku yuko tayari sasa. Atawachukua vifaranga vyake kwenye maonyesho. Moja, Mbili, Tatu, Nne, Tano, Sita!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother Hen and her six chicks have a fantastic time at the fair. What fun! Her chicks were worth the wait."
msgstr "Mama kuku na vifaranga vyake sita walikuwa na wakati mzuri kwenye maonyesho. Furaha iliyoje! vifaranga vyake vilistahili kusubiri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My First Day at School"
msgstr "Siku yangu ya kwanza shuleni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sesi is six years old and lives with her parents in Turiani. After her first day at school, she comes home and tells them something funny that happened at school. What do you think happened?"
msgstr "Sesi ana umri wa miaka sita na anaishi na wazazi wake Turiani. Baada ya siku yake ya kwanza shuleni, anarudi nyumbani na anasema jambo la kufurahisha lililotokea shule Unafikiri nini kilitokea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My name is Sesi. I am six years old. I am a new student at Manyinga Primary School."
msgstr "Jina langu ni Sesi, Nina umri wa miaka sita. Ni mwanafunzi mpya katika shule hii ya Msingi ya Manyinga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My first day at school was exciting. I got up early in the morning. My father took me to school. On the way there were many other students.Some were with their parents."
msgstr "Siku yangu ya kwanza Shuleni ilikuwa ni ya kufurahisha. Niliamka asubuhi na mapema, Baba yangu alinipeleka shuleni. Njiani kulikuwa na wanafunzi wengine wengi. Wengine walikuwa na wazazi wao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I heard the bell ringing, \"Gong! Gong! Gong!\" Other students started running."
msgstr "Nilisikia kengele inalia, ''Ngoo! Ngoo! Ngoo!'' Wanafunzi wengine walianza kukimbia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Each student took his or her place in a line. I ran and joined the others. When I looked at the other students, I felt very small. They seemed much older than me."
msgstr "Kila mwanafunzi alichukua nafasi yake kwenye mstari. Nilikimbia na kuungana nao. Nilipowatizama wanafunzi wengine, Nilijiona ni mdogo sana. Walionekana wakubwa zaidi yangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "An older girl took me by the hand to where students of my age were gathered. I was with the wrong class!"
msgstr "Msichana mkubwa alinishika mkono mpaka mahali ambapo wanafunzi wa rika langu walikuwa wamekusanyika. Nilienda kwenye darasa lingine kimakosa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "As I stood in line with the students my age, I heard someone yell, \"Madam, this boy has wet his shorts!\" We all turned back. I saw a little boy holding his shorts, looking sad."
msgstr "Nikiwa nimesimama kwenye mstari wenye wanafunzi wa rika langu, Nilimsikia mwanafunzi mmoja akipiga kelele, ''Bibi, kaptura ya huyu mvulana imeloana! wote tuligeuka nyuma. Nikamuona mvulana mdogo ameshikilia kaptula yake, anaonekana mwenye huzuni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Both his legs were wet. His eyes were wet with tears. An older boy came and took him by the hand to get help."
msgstr "Miguu yote miwili ilikuwa imeloana. Macho yake yalikuwa na machozi. Kijana mkubwa alikuja kumsaidia na alimshika mkono."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Then a teacher showed us our classroom. It was large and clean."
msgstr "Kisha mwalimu akatuonyesha darasa letu. lilikuwa kubwa na safi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One student came in late. He was holding his shoes. The teacher asked why. He said that his mother had taught him to always take off his shoes before stepping into a room. We all laughed."
msgstr "Mwanafunzi mmoja aliingia kwa kuchelewa. Alikuwa ameshika viatu vyake. Mwalimu aliuliza kwanini. Alisema kwamba, mama yake amemfundisha kuwa awe anavua viatu kabla ya kuinga ndani ya chumba. Sote tulicheka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The bell rang again, \"Gong! Gong! Gong!\" We rushed outside and stood in lines. A teacher came to us and told us that it was break time. There was no need to stand in lines. It was time to play!"
msgstr "Kengele ilipigwa tena, Gong! Gong! Gong! Tulikimbia nje na kujipanga kwenye mistari. Mwalimu alikuja na kutuambia kuwa ilikuwa ni muda wa mapumziko. Hakukuwa na haja ya kusimama mstarini. Ulikuwa muda wa kucheza!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "After a short while, the bell rang again. All other students were rushing into their classrooms. I was confused, I did not know where to go. I had forgotten my classroom!"
msgstr "Baada ya muda mfupi, kengele ilipigwa tena. Wanafunzi wengine wote walikimbilia kwenye madarasa yao. Nilichanganyikiwa. Sikujua niende wapi. Nilisahau darasa langu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I saw a classroom in front of me and stepped inside. Two other students followed me. None of us knew where to go."
msgstr "Niliona darasa mbele yangu na nikaingia ndani. Wanafunzi wengine wawili wakanifuata. Kati yetu hakuna aliyejua twende wapi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One of the students who was with me started crying. An older girl asked him what was wrong. He replied that he wanted to see his mother. Some of the other students laughed, but some wanted to help."
msgstr "Mmoja wa wanafunzi aliyekuwa na mimi alianza kulia. Msichana mkubwa alimuuliza, tatizo ni nini. Alijibu kuwa anataka kumuona mama yake. Baadhi ya wanafunzi wengine walicheka, lakini wengine walitaka kusaidia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One of the older girls took us to our classroom. Our teacher told us that soon it would be time to go home, and we should wait for our parents to pick us up from the classroom."
msgstr "Mmoja wa wasichana wakubwa alituchukua na kutupeleka kwenye darasa letu. Mwalimu wetu alituambia kwamba muda si mrefu ingekuwa muda wa kwenda nyumbani, na tunatakiwa kuwasubiri wazazi wetu kutuchukua kutoka darasani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The bell rang again, \"Gong! Gong! Gong!\" We were happy to see our parents waiting for us outside."
msgstr "Kengele ilipigwa tena, Gong! Gong! Gong! Tulifurahi kuona wazazi wetu wakitusubiri nje."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "After dinner, my father and mother asked me what my day at school had been like. I told them about how we lost our classroom. They laughed and said I should listen carefully to the teachers."
msgstr "Baada ya chakula cha jioni, Baba yangu na Mama waliniuliza siku yangu ilikuwaje shule. Niliwambia kuhusu jinsi tulivyopotea darasa letu. Walicheka na kusema natakiwa kusikiliza walimu kwa umakini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That night, I couldn't sleep. The night was long and I was eager to start my second day of school."
msgstr "Usiku ule, sikuweza kulala. Usiku ulikuwa mrefu na nilitamani kuanza siku yangu ya pili ya shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nichchumani Helps Out"
msgstr "Neli anatoa msaada"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nichchumani wants to help Pichhu, a lost and injured duckling. She takes her home, but she only finds more trouble there!"
msgstr "Neli anataka kumsaidia Pichchu, bata aliyepotea na aliyeumia. Alimchukua nyumbani kwake, lakini anapata shida zaidi hapo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One day, Nichchumani went out for a walk and saw a lost duckling crying. \"Why are you crying?\" she asked."
msgstr "Siku moja, Neli alikwenda nje kutembea na akamuona bata aliyepotea analia. ''Kwanini unalia?'' aliuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Poor Pichchu the duckling was hurt. She couldn't swim or play or do any of her favorite things. \"Don't worry,\" said Nichchumani. \"We will get you all fixed up!\""
msgstr "Maskini Pichchu bata alieumia. Hawezi kuogelea wala kucheza wala kufanya vitu anavyovipenda. ''Usiwe na wasiwasi,'' alisema Neli. Tutakushughulikia!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Uh Oh! Kitty spied Pichchu while she was taking a nap. \"What a good snack,\" purred kitty."
msgstr "Uh Oh! Kitty alimpeleleza Pichchu alipokuwa amepumzika. Ni vitafunwa vizuri,'' Paka msafi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"KITTY, NO!\" cried Nichchumani, as she grabbed kitty."
msgstr "''KITTY, Hapana''Nichchumani alilia, anapomkamata paka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Poor Pichchu needed to go see a doctor. Nichchumani carried her all the way there."
msgstr "Maskini Pichchu anahitaji kumuona Daktari. Neli alimbeba njia nzima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The doctor helped Pichchu and soon she was all better!"
msgstr "Doctor alimsaidia Pichchu na muda si mrefu alikuwa vizuri!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Soon, Pichchu's mother found her."
msgstr "Muda si mrefu. Mama yake Pichchu alimpata."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She took her home so she could swim and play and do all of her favorite things."
msgstr "Alimchukua nyumbani ili aogelee na kucheza na kufanya michezo yote anayoipenda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Bye, Pichchu!\" waved Nichchumani and her friends."
msgstr "''Kwaheri, Pichchu!'' Neli alimpungia rafiki yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No Smiles Today"
msgstr "Hamna Kucheka Leo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shanti was a happy girl. No one had seen her sad or quiet. Then one day she went very quiet. What had happened to Shanti?"
msgstr "Shanti alikuwa msichana mchangamfu. Hamna aliyewahi kumwona akiwa amesononeka au akiwa mkimya. Kisha siku moja alinyamaza tu. Ni nini kilimtokea Shanti?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shanti and Arun were good friends. They had so much fun together. They shared secrets in class. They ran races on the way home. She was always cheerful."
msgstr "Shanti na Aruna walikuwa marafiki wa chanda na pete. Walikuwa na wakati mzuri sana pamoja. Walibadilishana siri zao darasani. Walikimbizana walipokuwa wanarudi nyumbani. Shanti alikuwa mchangamfu saa zote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One day, Shanti came into the classroom slowly. Her head was bent. She looked sad. \"Did someone scold you?\" asked Arun. Shanti shook her head. She sat down and did not look up. She did not answer ‘Present!’ when Sona Miss called her name. Sona Miss called again, louder this time, \"Shanti Kumar!\" Shanti raised her hand."
msgstr "Siku moja,Shanti alikuja darasani pole pole. Alikuwa amesononeka. \"Kuna aliyekuhudhi?\" Aruna aliuliza. Shanti alitikisa kichwa chake. Aliketi chini na hakuangalia juu tena. Wala hakujibu \"Nipo\"mwalimu Sona alipoita jina lake.Bi.Sona aliita tena. Kwa sauti safari hii. \"Shanti Karama!\" Shanti aliinua mkono wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Do you have a sore throat?\" her teacher asked her. Shanti shook her head. Her cheeks were red and it looked like she had a fever. \"Are you feeling okay?\" Sona Miss asked. Shanti nodded, still not daring to look up."
msgstr "\"Una homa?\" mwalimu aliuliza. Shanti alitikisa Kichwa chake. Mashavu yake yalikuwa mekundu na alionekana kuwa na homa. \"Uko salama?\" Sona aliuliza. Shanti alitikisa kichwa, bado hakuangalia juu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Why does Shanti look so sad?\" \"Is your little brother okay?\" \"Is your puppy okay?\" \"Is your grandmother okay?\" Shanti kept nodding her head to each of her friends. But she did not look up."
msgstr "\"Mbona Shanti amekasirika?\" \"Mdogo wako yuko salama?\" \"Na mbwa wako yuko salama?\" \"Na Bibi yako yuko salama?\" Shanti alizidi kuonyesha ishara ya kuitikia kwa kutikisa kichwa tu kwa kila rafiki yake. Ila hakuangalia juu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Arun wanted to make her smile. He had an idea! He took out something from his bag. As he ran to show it to Shanti, it slipped out of his hands. Shanti saw something flying towards her and she grabbed it."
msgstr "Aruna alitaka kumfanya atabasamu. Alikuwa na wazo! Alichukua kitu kutoka kwenye mkoba wake. Alipokuwa anakimbia kumwonyesha, kilimponyoka kutoka mkononi kwake, Shanti aliona kitu kinapepea kuelekea kwake na akakikamata."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It was a BIG, green, rubber frog! Shanti's eyes flew open. Then she opened her mouth to laugh. THEN Arun and her friends saw why she had not smiled or talked all day! Four of her front teeth had gone missing!"
msgstr "Alikuwa chura mkubwa na wakijani. Shanti alikodoa macho. Kisha akafungua mdomo wake kucheka. Kisha Aruna na rafiki zake wakaona sababu iliyomfanya asicheke siku nzima! Meno yake manne ya mbele yalikuwa yamengóka!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pishi and Me"
msgstr "Pishi na Mimi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Chutku returns from his walks with his aunt, his pocket full of treasures and stories. Narrated from a child’s point of view, this is the story of the heartwarming relationship between an aunt and her nephew."
msgstr "Chacha alirudi kutoka matembezi na shangazi yake, mfuko wake ukiwa umejaa hazina na hadithi. Alisimulia kutokana na uelewa wa mtoto, hii ni hadithi ya uhusiano mzuri sana kati ya shangazi na mpwa wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I love going for walks. Especially with my Pishi."
msgstr "Napenda kwenda matembezi. Hasa na Pishi wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I like it when Pishi holds my hand. But I like it even more... when she lets it go."
msgstr "Napenda pale Pishi anaponishika mkono wangu. Lakini napenda zaidi... pale anapouachia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We never walk fast. We often stop to say hello to..."
msgstr "Kamwe hatutembei kwa haraka. Mara nyingi tunasimama kusalimia..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "a dog, a cat, a rat, a crow, a tree."
msgstr "mbwa, Paka, Panya, Kunguru, Mti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pishi loves picking up flowers from the street. I love picking up stones. Big ones, small ones, round ones, flat ones."
msgstr "Pishi anapenda kuokota maua kutoka mtaani. Napenda kuokota mawe. Makubwa, madogo, ya mviringo, membamba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But the best are the really tiny ones. So tiny, they get lost in my pocket."
msgstr "Lakini nzuri zaidi ni zile ndogo kweli. Ndogo sana, zimepotea ndani ya mfuko wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My pockets are full of things after my walks with Pishi."
msgstr "Mfuko wangu umejaa vitu baada ya matembezi yangu na Pishi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today, Ajji gave me a pod of peas from her basket."
msgstr "Leo, Furaha alinipa ganda la njegere kutoka kwenye kikapu chake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Dilip bhau gave me this clip from his magical shop."
msgstr "Dilip bhau alinipa hiki kipande kutoka kwenye duka lake la maajabu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nirmal didi gave me this sticker for quietly waiting, waiting and waiting."
msgstr "Nimal didi alinipa kibandiko hiki kwajili ya kusubiri sana na sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Anjum aunty gave me this button from her big button jar."
msgstr "Shangazi yake Shukuru alinipa kitufe hiki kutoka kwenye mtungi wake mkubwa wa kitufe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I get home, I’ll empty my pockets and keep it all in my yellow box."
msgstr "Nitakapofika nyumbani, Nitaiacha mifuko yangu ikiwa mitupu na nitavitunza vyote kwenye boksi langu la njano."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If I find the tiny stone in my pocket, I’ll give it to my Pishi."
msgstr "Kama nitakuta jiwe dogo kwenye mfuko wangu, nitampa Pishi wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tra's Red Bean Plant"
msgstr "Mmea wa maharagwe mekundu wa Tra"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tra is excited about her birthday gift. It's three red bean seeds and a book about gardening. She plants her seeds and waters them daily. But for some reason her plant begins to droop. What could be wrong?"
msgstr "Tiara amefurahishwa na zawadi yake ya kumbukizi ya siku ya kuzaliwa kwake. Ni mbegu tatu za maharage mekundu na kitabu kuhusu bustani. Alizipanda mbegu na kuzimwagilia kila siku. Lakini kwasababu flani mmea wake ulianza kudhoofika. Nini kinaweza kuwa ni tatizo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Room to Read, 2012. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Room to Read, 2012. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC. BY. 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On her birthday, Tra's mother gave her a special gift. \"Wow! Red beans and a gardening book,\" Tra said. \"Now I can grow my own red bean plant.\""
msgstr "Siku ya kumbukizi ya kuzaliwa kwake, Mama yake Tiara alimpa zawadi maalumu. \"Waoo! maharage mekundu na kitabu cha bustani,\" alisema Tiara. \"Sasa naweza kupanda mmea wangu mwenyewe wa maharage mekundu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "First, plant the seed, Tra read. So she did. \"You’re doing great, Tra!\" the book told her."
msgstr "Kwanza, panda mbegu, Tiara alisoma. Alifanya hivyo. \"Unafanya vizuri, Tiara!\" kitabu kilimwambia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, water it. La La La! Tra sang as she did just that."
msgstr "Sasa, mwagilia. La La La! Tiara aliimba alipofanya hivyo tu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"My red bean plant will soon grow up,\" Tra told her friends. \"You have to water it a lot to keep it healthy,\" they said. \"Just like kids have to drink a lot of milk to grow big and strong!\""
msgstr "\" Mmea wangu wa maharage mekundu utakua muda si mrefu,\" Tiara aliwaambia marafiki zake. \"Unatakiwa kuumwagilia sana kuufanya uwe na afya,\" walisema. Kama vile watoto wanatakiwa kunywa maziwa mengi ili kukua na wawe imara!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A few days later, the red bean sprouted. \"Look, Mom!\" Tra called. \"It's growing!\""
msgstr "Siku chache baadae, harage jekundu lilichomoza.\" tazama Mama!\" Tiara aliita. \"Linakua!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The next morning, Tra watered her plant again. \"La La La! Drink, drink, drink!\" she sang. \"If you drink more water, you'll grow up faster!\" \"Oh my, Tra, not like that!\" said the book."
msgstr "Asubuhi iliyofuata, Tiara alimwagilia tena mmea wake. \"La La La! Kunywa kunywa, kunywa!\" aliimba. Kama utakunywa maji zaidi, utakua haraka!\" \"Oh Tiara wangu sio hivyo!\" kilisema kitabu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tra watered again at noon. La La La! \"Oh my, Tra!\" the book said, louder now. \"My pages say not to water a plant at noon.\""
msgstr "Tiara alimwagilia tena mchana. La La La! \"Oh Tiara wangu!\" Kitabu kilisema, kwa sauti sasa. \"Kurasa zangu zinasema usimwagilie mmea mchana.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But Tra kept right on watering. La La La, La La La! Oh my, Tra! You've forgotten to read me!"
msgstr "Lakini Tiara aliendelea kumwagilia. La La La La La La! Oh Tiara wangu, Umesahau kunisoma!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The next day, Tra gave her mother instructions as she left for school. \"Give my plant more water at noon, please!\" \"Have you read the book?\" her mother asked."
msgstr "Siku iliyofuata, Tiara alimpa Mama yake maelekezo kwakuwa alikuwa anaenda shule. \"Mwagilia mmea wangu maji mengi zaidi mchana, tafadhali!\" \" Umesoma kitabu?\" Mama yake aliuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"In my pages, it says to water the plant only once a day,\"the book said sadly. Oh my, Tra!"
msgstr "\"Kwenye kurasa zangu, Inasema inabidi kumwagilia mmea mara moja tu kwa siku,\" kitabu kilisema kwa huzuni. Oh Tiara wangu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Three days later, Tra was sad, too. \"My poor plant!\" she cried."
msgstr "Siku tatu baadae, Tiara alihuzunika pia. \" Maskini mmea wangu!\" alilia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "At school, she talked to her friends. \"I have been taking such good care of my plant. Why is it so sad?\" \"What does the book say?\" they asked."
msgstr "Shuleni, alizungumza na rafiki zake. \"Nimekuwa nikiutunza vizuri sana mmea wangu. Kwanini unasikitika?\" \"Kitabu kinasemaje?\" waliuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh my,\" Tra said. \"I stopped reading it.\""
msgstr "\"Oh Tiara wangu\" alisema. \"Niliacha kukisoma.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "At home, Tra showed the plant to her mother. \"I'm sorry, Mom,\" Tra said. \"I'm going to read the book now.\" \"That's a great idea,\" her mother replied."
msgstr "Nyumbani Tiara alimuonyesha mama yake mmea.\"Samahani, Mama, \"Tiara alisema.\"Naenda kusoma kitabu sasa.\" \"Hilo ni wazo zuri,\" alijibu Mama yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do not water the plant too much, or its roots will become soggy. Tra read. The leaves will then droop and turn brown."
msgstr "Usimwagilie mmea kwa maji mengi, ukimwagilia maji mengi mizizi yake itakuwa laini. Tiara amesoma. Kisha majani yataanguka na kubadilika kuwa ya kahawia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I’m so sorry, Red Bean,\" Tra whispered."
msgstr "\"Samahani sana, harage jekundu\" Tiara alinong\"ona."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"The plant won’t be sad, because he knows you love him,\" her mother said. \"You can show him your love by learning how to take good care of him.\""
msgstr "\"Mmea hauwezi kusikitika, sababu unajua unaupenda,\" Mama yake alisema. \" Unaweza kuuonyesha upendo wako kwa kujifunza jinsi ya kuutunza.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"You can also say sorry to the book, because you ignored her. She needs your attention, too!\""
msgstr "\"Unaweza pia kukiambia kitabu samahani. sababu ulikidharau. Kinahitaji umakini wako pia!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A few days later, Red Bean was healthy again. Now Tra and her gardening book were best friends!"
msgstr "Siku chache baadae, harage jekundu lilikuwa na afya tena. Sasa Tiara na kitabu chake cha bustani walikuwa marafiki wakubwa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Under My Bed"
msgstr "Chini ya Kitanda changu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes strange things lurk under my bed. Would you like to know what I found the other night?"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine vitu vigeni hujificha chini ya kitanda changu. Ungependa kujua nini kilitokea usiku mwingine?"

