#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I wake up at night feeling thirsty. I want to get some water. I start looking for my slippers under the bed."
msgstr "Naamka usiku nikasikia kiu. Nahitaji maji. Naanza kutafuta ndala zangu chini ya kitanda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh my God! There is a tiger under my bed."
msgstr "Mungu wangu! Kuna duma chini ya kitanda changu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now what should I do?"
msgstr "Sasa nifanyeje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should I call Ma? What if the tiger roars?"
msgstr "Nimpigie Mama? Na duma akiunguruma?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should I just go back to sleep? But I am not sleepy any more."
msgstr "Au labda nirudi kulala? Ila sipati usingizi tena."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Then someone turns on the light. Ma is standing at the door."
msgstr "Kisha mtu anawasha taa. Mama amesimama mlangoni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What happened dear?Did you call me?\" asks Ma."
msgstr "\"Nini kimetokea mpendwa? Uliniita?\" Mama anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I point towards the tiger. Ma bends and pulls the tiger out from under the bed!"
msgstr "Namuelekeza kwa duma. Mama anainama na anaangalia chini ya kitanda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hey, this is no tiger. This is my thick yellow and black sweater. Its buttons shine like a tiger's eyes."
msgstr "Wewe! Huyu si duma,ni fulana kubwa nyeusi inayofanana na ngozi ya duma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I got scared for nothing! Ma gets me some water."
msgstr "Niliogopa bure. Mama ananipa maji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now I will sleep. And dream about real tigers in a jungle!"
msgstr "Sasa nitalala. Na nitaota duma wa kweli wa porini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A Very Green Day"
msgstr "Siku ya Kijani sana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Greeny has so much energy. She doesn't want to nap! One day, she decides to run away. After playing in the hot sun for a while, Greeny gets tired and wants to go home. But now she's lost! How will she get home to her dad?"
msgstr "Pendo ana nguvu sana. Hataki kulala usingizi! Siku moja, aliamua kukimbilia mbali. Baada ya kucheza kwenye jua kali kwa muda, Pendo alichoka na alitaka kwenda nyumbani. Lakini sasa amepotea! Atarudi vipi nyumbani kwa baba yake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Room to Read, 2013. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Room to Read, 2013. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC. BY. 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Greeny doesn’t want to nap. Today, she wants to be a tree!"
msgstr "Leo, Kijani hataki kupumzika, anataka kuwa mti!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Trees don’t need naps!"
msgstr "Miti haihitaji kupumzika!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Trees can play all day long."
msgstr "Miti inaweza kucheza siku nzima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Trees only need to be green."
msgstr "Miti inahitaji kuwa ya kijani tu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Uh-oh. Dad can’t find Greeny."
msgstr "Uh. oh Baba hamuoni Pendo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She’s hiding among the trees."
msgstr "Anajificha katikati ya miti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It's so fun to be a tree!"
msgstr "Inafurahisha sana kuwa mti!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But it is a bit hot playing under the sun, isn't it?"
msgstr "Lakini kuna joto kidogo kucheza chini ya jua. si ndio?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Actually, it’s too hot!"
msgstr "Kwa kweli, ni joto sana!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What should Greeny do?"
msgstr "Pendo afanye nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should she go home to Dad?"
msgstr "Je aende nyumbani kwa Baba?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But where is home? Greeny is lost!"
msgstr "Lakini nyumbani ni wapi? Pendo amepotea!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Dad is looking for Greeny. Greeny keeps walking until she reaches a river."
msgstr "Baba anamtafuta Pendo. Pendo anaendelea kutembea mpaka anafika mtoni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tired and scared, Greeny bursts into tears. Her tears cause the river to flood!"
msgstr "Nimechoka na ninaogopa, Pendo anatokwa na machozi. Machozi yake yanasababisha mto ufurike!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The whole city is flooded!"
msgstr "Jiji lote limefurika!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ah! Greeny has an idea. She will write messages for Dad on her leaves."
msgstr "Ah! Pendo ana wazo. Ataandika ujumbe kwaajili ya Baba yake kwenye majani yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The green world helps her too."
msgstr "Dunia ya kijani ilimsaidia pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thanks to the green world, Dad finally gets her messages."
msgstr "Asante kwa dunia ya kijani, hatimae baba amepata ujumbe wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Dad finds Greeny!"
msgstr "Baba amempata Pendo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DADDY! GREENY!"
msgstr "BABA! PENDO!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Greeny is so tired. Now, all she wants is her nap."
msgstr "Pendo amechoka sana. Sasa anachotaka tu ni kulala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Greeny, get ready for school!\" her dad calls. \"No,\" she says. \"I’m a cat today. Cats don’t go to school so early.\""
msgstr "''Pendo, jiandae kwenda shule! Baba yake anaita.''Hapana'' anasema.'' Mimi leo ni paka. Paka haendi shule mapema sana.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"8 Steps to becoming a tree (written and performed by Greeny)\n"
"1. Find a pot.\n"
"2. Fill it with soil.\n"
"3. Plant your feet inside. \n"
"4. Branch out your two hands."
msgstr ""
"Hatua nane za kuwa mti(Imeandikwa na ilifanywa na Pendo)\n"
"1. Tafuta chungu.\n"
"2. Jaza udongo.\n"
"3. Weka miguu yako ndani.\n"
"4. Nyoosha mikono yako kuwa matawi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"5. Water the plant.\n"
"6. Add fertilizer.\n"
"7. Wait.\n"
"8. Ta-da!\n"
"Congratulations, you are now a tree."
msgstr ""
"5. Mwagilia mmea.\n"
"6. Ongeza mbolea.\n"
"7. Subiri.\n"
"8. Ta-da!\n"
"Hongera, sasa wewe ni mti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Caution:\n"
"Sometimes, there may be incidents of incomplete change, as follows:\n"
"1. No change at all.\n"
"2. Thorns all over the body.\n"
"3. Becoming as stiff as wood.\n"
"4. Becoming a bush.\n"
"Oops! Just try again."
msgstr ""
"Tahadhari:\n"
"Wakati mwingine, kunaweza kuwa na mabadiliko yasiyokamilika, kama ifuatavyo:\n"
"1. Hakuna mabadiliko kabisa.\n"
"2. Miiba mwili mzima.\n"
"3. Kuwa mgumu kama kuni.\n"
"4. Kuwa kichaka.\n"
"Oops! Jaribu tu tena."

