msgid "Ideas for book activities"
msgstr "Mawazo ya shughuli za kitabu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"“When I grow up” is a great book for talking about different types of work and things that people can do. As you go through the book, ask your child questions like: “What clothes is she wearing? What is she doing? Why do you think she is doing that? What else can you see in the picture? \n"
" \n"
"Connect the story to your child’s world by asking if your child has seen any of these things in real life. Ask what they would like to do if they were in the story? And what would they like to be one day when they grow up? \n"
" \n"
"Remember to respond in a positive way to what your child says. Build your child up instead of breaking them down!"
msgstr ""
"“Nikiwa mkubwa” Ni kitabu kizuri kinachozungumzia kuhusu kazi tofauti na mambo mbalimbali watu wanaweza kufanya.. Unapopitia kitabu, muulize mtoto wako maswali kama: “ Je amevaa nguo gani? Anafanya nini? Unafikiri kwa nini anafanya hivyo? Ni nini kingine unaweza kukiona kwenye picha.?\n"
"\n"
"Unganisha hadithi na ulimwengu wa mtoto wako kwa kuuliza ikiwa mtoto wako ameona mojawapo ya mambo hayo katika maisha halisi. Uliza ungependa kufanya nini kama ungekuwa kwenye hadithi hiyo? Ungependa kuwa nani siku moja ukikua?\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka kuitikia kwa njia nzuri kwa kile mtoto wako anachosema. Mjenge mtoto wako badala ya kumvunja moyo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Invite your child to join you in a book activity"
msgstr "Mwalike mtoto wako kujiunga na wewe kwenye shughuli ya kitabu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sharing a book with your child is a great way to connect and spend quality time together. Start by inviting your child to join you in a book activity. If they don’t want to, rather try again another time. Keep asking them without putting pressure on them. You can also tell them about a particular book or story that you would like to share with them, to spark their interest.\n"
"As you go through the book, give your child your full attention. Notice and respond to what your child is interested in.Describe the animals, surroundings and characters and ask your child questions about what they see."
msgstr ""
"Kushirikishana kitabu na mtoto wako ni njia nzuri ya kuungana na kutumia muda pamoja. Anza kwa kumwalika mtoto wako kujiunga na wewe kwenye shughuli ya kitabu. Kama hataki ni bora ujaribu tena wakati mwingine. Endelea kumuomba bila kumlazimisha. unaweza pia kumwambia kuhusu kitabu flani au hadithi ambayo ungependa kumshirikisha, kuchochea kuvutiwa kwake.\n"
"Kadili mtakavyoendelea kupitia kitabu, mpe mtoto wako umakini wote.Tambua na itikia kile kinachomvutia mtoto wako. Elezea wanyama, mazingira na wahusika, muulize mtoto wako kuhusu kile anachokiona."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Be responsive during book activities"
msgstr "Kuwa msikivu wakati wa shughuli za kitabu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Name and describe what you see in the pictures"
msgstr "Taja na elezea kile unachokiona kwenye picha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watch this video to see how you can share this book to create a positive experience for you and your child."
msgstr "Tazama video hii ili kuona ni namna gani unaweza kushirikishana kitabu hiki kutengeneza uzoefu mzuri wewe na mtoto wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the pictures, mimic sounds and actions"
msgstr "Elezea picha, igiza sauti na vitendo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shongololo has many feet. This means he needs lots of shoes! But where have they all gone? Encourage your child to find all Shongololo’s shoes as you go through the book together. Ask your child questions about what the animals in the story are doing and what they are using the shoes for? Make it fun by acting out what the different animals are doing."
msgstr "Jongoo Shongololo ana miguu mingi. Hii ina maana kwamba anahitaji viatu vingi! Lakini vimeenda wapi vyote? Mhimize mtoto wako atafute viatu vyote vya Shongololo kadili manavyoendelea kupitia kitabu pamoja. Muulize mtoto wako maswali kuhusu kile wanachofanya wanyama wa kwenye hadithi na wanatumia viatu kwaajili ya nini? Ifanye iwe ya furaha kwa kuigiza kile ambacho wanyama wanafanya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watch this video to see how you can share this book with your child in a fun and playful way."
msgstr "Tazama video hii ili kuona ni namna gani unaweza kushirikishana kitabu hiki wewe na mtoto wako kwa njia ya kufurahisha na ya kucheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic sounds, actions and emotions"
msgstr "Igiza sauti, vitendo na hisia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lefa’s Bath has lots of animals and fun events that you can act out with your child. You can also describe what Lefa is doing and how she is feeling."
msgstr "Bafu la Lefa lina wanyama wengi na matukio ya kufurahisha ambayo unaweza kuigiza pamoja na mtoto wako. Unaweza pia kuelezea kile anachofanya Lefa na jinsi anavyojiskia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Count, talk about colors, shapes and sizes"
msgstr "Hesabu, zungumza kuhusu rangi, maumbo na ukubwa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Join Thabo and his sister Tumi as their mother creates all sorts of surprises for their lunch. \n"
"Count the different foods, ask questions about the food’s colors, shapes, sizes, textures and tastes. \n"
"Ask your child what food they know? And what do they like to eat? \n"
"And when you have dinner later, talk about the color, shape, texture and taste of your delicious food!"
msgstr ""
"Jiunge na Thabo na dada yake Tumi huku mama yao akitengeneza vyakula tofauti kwa ajili ya mchana. \n"
"Hesabu vyakula mbalimbali, uliza maswali kuhusu rangi, maumbo, ukubwa, muundo na ladha ya chakula\n"
"Muulize mtoto wako ni chakula gani anakijua? Na anapenda kula nini?\n"
"Na wakati wa chakula cha jioni baadae, zungumza kuhusu rangi, umbo, muundo na ladha ya chakula chako kitamu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask questions about what is happening and why"
msgstr "Uliza maswali kuhusu kile wahusika wanachofanya na kwanini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the pictures, ask questions, make it fun!"
msgstr "Elezea picha, uliza maswali, ifanye iwe ya furaha!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about feelings and how to manage them"
msgstr "Zungumza kuhusu hisia, na jinsi ya kuzithibiti"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Everybody gets scared sometimes. Use this book to talk to your child about different feelings: What makes us feel scared? What can we do when we feel this way?\n"
"Remember that it is normal for children to have big feelings sometimes! As their caregivers, you can show them that these feelings are okay, and you can be an example for how to cope when they feel this way."
msgstr ""
"Kila mtu hupata uoga wakati flani. Tumia kitabu hiki kuzungumza na mtoto wako hisia tofauti. Nini kinatufanya tuogope? Tunaweza kufanya nini tunapojiskia namna hii?\n"
"Kumbuka kwamba ni kawaida kwa watoto kuwa na hisia kubwa wakati flani! Kama walezi wao, mnaweza kuwaonyesha kwamba hisia hizi ni sawa, na mnaweza kuwa mfano wa jinsi ya kukabiliana wanapojiskia namna hiyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask questions about the characters and what they are doing"
msgstr "Uliza maswali kuhusu wahusika na kile wanachofanya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Fifi has a brown teddy that she loves very much. Use this story to describe different feelings, actions and events to your child. \n"
"Ask your child what the characters are doing and why they think they are doing that? This will help your child understand the story better. It will also help them to learn about different emotions and behaviors too."
msgstr ""
"Fifi ana mdoli wa rangi ya kahawia ambao anaupenda sana. Tumia hadithi hii kumuelezea mtoto wako hisia tofauti, vitendo na matukio.\n"
"Muulize mtoto wako wahusika wanafanya nini na kwanini anafikiri anafanya hivyo? Hii itamsaidia mtoto wako kuielewa vizuri zaidi hadithi. Pia itamsidia kujifunza kuhusu hisia tofauti na tabia pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about and demonstrate emotions from the story"
msgstr "Zungumza na onyesha hisia kutoka kwenye hadithi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This book is great for talking to your child about different emotions, experiences and events!\n"
"Use your face and voice to demonstrate what the characters are feeling. You could say: “Oh no! he is feeling sad. He lost his toy.”\n"
"Or you can say: “Hooray!! They found it! They are happy.”\n"
"You can ask: “What did this child lose? How is he feeling? Who will help him? What do you think will happen next?”\n"
"You can also ask your child how they would have felt if this happened to them, and what they would have done."
msgstr ""
"Kitabu hiki ni kizuri kwa kuzungumza na mtoto wako kuhusu hisia tofauti, uzoefu na matukio!\n"
"Tumia uso wako na sauti kuonesha kwa matendo kile wahusika wanachojiskia. Ungeweza kusema: “Oh, Hapana! anajiskia huzuni. Amepoteza mdoli wake.” Au unaweza kusema: “Hureee! Wamempata! Wanafuraha.”\n"
"Unaweza uliza: “Mtoto huyu alipoteza nini? Anajiskiaje? Nani atamsaidia? Unafikiri nini kitatokea baada ya hapo?\n"
"Unaweza pia kumuuliza mtoto wako angejiskiaje kama hii ingetokea kwake, na angefanya nini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connect to story to your child’s emotions and experiences"
msgstr "Unganisha hadithi, hisia na uzoefu wa mtoto wako"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Explore similarities and differences between the story and your child’s life"
msgstr "Chunguza mfanano na utofauti kati ya hadithi na maisha ya mtoto wako"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This book is great for connecting pictures and stories to your child’s own life and experiences. Explore with your child: “Zibu and Zizo walk to school – how about you? They like to eat banana bread – what do you like to eat?”\n"
"Show your child that different people can like different things, and that it’s okay. You can say: “Zibu likes soccer, Zizo likes drawing. What do you like to do? And how is that similar or different to what your friends like to do?”"
msgstr ""
"Kitabu hiki ni kizuri kwa kuunganisha picha na hadithi kwa maisha ya mtoto wako na uzoefu. Zungumza na mtoto wako: “Zibu na Zizo wanatembea kwenda shule - vipi kuhusu wewe? Wanapenda kula mkate wa ndizi - Unapenda kula nini?”\n"
"Muonyeshe mtoto wako kwamba watu tofauti wanaweza kupenda vitu tofauti, na hii ni sawa. Unaweza kusema: “Zibu hupenda mpira wa miguu, Zizo hupenda kuchora. Unapenda kufanya nini?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connect the events in the story to your child’s own experiences. How is it the same or different?"
msgstr "Unganisha matukio ya kwenye hadithi na uzoefu wa mtoto wako. Je yako sawa au ni tofaauti?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use the pictures to count, categorize and compare"
msgstr "Tumia picha kuhesabu, kuainisha na kulinganisha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bring the story to life"
msgstr "Ifanye hadithi iwe hai"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connect what happens in the story to similarities and differences in your child’s world."
msgstr "Unganisha kile kinatokea kwenye hadithi kama kinafanana au kipo tofauti kwenye ulimwengu wa mtoto wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about events and emotions"
msgstr "Zungumza kuhusu matukio na hisia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes how we feel can be hard to talk about. But everyone knows how to talk about the weather. \n"
" \n"
"You can use the pictures in this story to talk about different types of weather like sunshine, clouds, rain, or wind – and what we do when we experience these types of weather. \n"
" You can also use the pictures to talk about different emotions such as feeling happy, sad, angry, upset or excited. You can ask your child: “when do you feel that way? What do you do when you feel that way?”\n"
" Talking about feelings can feel strange at first but is a very effective way to help children learn to manage their emotions and behavior."
msgstr ""
"Wakati mwingine ni vigumu kuelezea tunavyojiskia. Lakini kila mmoja anajua kuzungumza kuhusu hali ya hewa.\n"
"Unaweza kutumia picha za kwenye hadithi hii kuzungumza kuhusu aina tofauti za hali ya hewa kama kuchomoza kwa jua, mawingu, mvua, au upepo-na tunafanyaje pale tunapopata aina hizi za hali ya hewa.\n"
"Pia unaweza kutumia picha kuzungumza kuhusu aina tofauti za hisia kama vile kujiskia furaha, huzuni, hasira, kukasirika, kufurahia. Unaweza kumuuliza mtoto wako:\n"
"“Umeanza kujiskia hivyo lini? Huwa unafanya nini unapojiskia hivyo?”\n"
"Kuzungumza kuhusu hisia kunaweza kuwa ni kitu cha ajabu mwanzoni: Lakini ni njia nzuri sana kuwasaidia watoto kujifunza kudhibiti hisia na tabia zao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Create positive experiences"
msgstr "Tengeneza uzoefu mzuri"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Respond in a positive way, make it fun and praise your child’s efforts."
msgstr "Itikia katika njia nzuri, ifanye iwe ya furaha na usifu juhudi za mtoto wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More ideas for book activities"
msgstr "Mawazo zaidi ya shughuli za kitabu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connect the story to real life"
msgstr "Unganisha hadithi na maisha halisi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Join Teacher Langa’s class as they share what they want to be when they grow up. Chef, builder, nurse or artist? Tell your child more about what these jobs involve or ask your child what jobs they have seen people do in their community? \n"
"Encourage your child to talk about what they want to be or do one day. Ask them why. Encourage them to tell you more about their dream."
msgstr ""
"Jiunge na darasa la Mwalimu Langa wanaposhirikisha wanataka kuwa nani wanapokuwa wakubwa. Mpishi, Mjenzi, Muuguzi au msanii? Mwambie mtoto wako zaidi kuhusu kazi hizo zinihusiana na nini au muulize mtoto wako ni kazi gani ameona watu wakifanya kwenye jamii yao?\n"
"Mhimize mtoto wako kuzungumza juu ya kile anachotaka kuwa au kufaanya siku moja. Muulize kwa nini. Mhimize akueleze zaidi kuhusu ndoto zake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use books in playful ways"
msgstr "Tumia vitabu kwa njia ya kucheza"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Learning Through Play"
msgstr "Kujifunza kupitia kucheza"

