#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How did @data.characters.f1_mother.name help her son to follow the instructions?"
msgstr "Ni kwa namna gani  @data.characters.f1_mother.name alimsaidia mtoto wake wa kiume kufuata maelekezo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She explained to him about what was happening"
msgstr "Alimwelezea kuhusu kile kilichotokea"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. She explained to @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name what his father was doing, and what the plan was – to put the baby to sleep and then play a game together."
msgstr "Hiyo ni sahihi. Alimuelezea @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name nini baba yake alikuwa anafanya, na mpango uliokuwepo - kumlaza mtoto na halafu kucheza mchezo pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She explained why they were asking him to be quiet"
msgstr "Alielezea kwanini walimuomba anyamaze"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes. She helped @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name to understand why it would help if he was quiet – that his brother would struggle to fall asleep if there were loud noises."
msgstr "Ndio. Alimsaidia @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name kuelewa kwanini ingesaidia kama angekuwa kimya - kwamba kaka yake angehangaika kupata usingizi kama kungekuwa na sauti kubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She said he would get punished if he was loud"
msgstr "Alisema angeadhibiwa ikiwa angeongea kwa sauti kubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not really. She did not say he would get punished. Instead, she explained why she wanted him to play a quieter game."
msgstr "Sio hivyo. Hakusema angeadhibiwa. Badala yake, alielezea kwanini alitaka acheze mchezo kwa utulivu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She used praise"
msgstr "Alimsifia"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes! Once @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name was playing quietly, she used praise to encourage him to continue."
msgstr "Ndio! Mara @data.characters.f1_child_boy.name alipocheza kimyakimya alimsifia kumtia moyo aendelee kufanya hivyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Book activities offer many opportunities for you and your child to talk and interact."
msgstr "Shughuli za vitabu zinatoa fursa nyingi kwako na mtoto wako kuzungumza na kuchangamana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some ideas for how you can use books to talk and interact:"
msgstr "Haya ni baadhi ya mawazo ya jinsi unavyoweza kuzungumza na kuchangamana:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Name and describe what you see in the pictures**\n"
"This helps your child learn new words and understand what is happening in the story."
msgstr ""
"**Taja na elezea unachokiona katika picha**\n"
"Hii humsaidia mtoto wako kujifunza maneno mapya na kufahamu kinachotokea katika hadithi.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Looking at this page, here are some ideas for what you can name and describe for your child:\n"
"Look, there is a bird sitting on that flower. The bird has a sharp beak and a long tail. I can see two other birds flying in the sky, can you see them? What do they look like? What else can we see that’s flying?”\n"
"“What animal can you see sitting on the rock? And what animal can you see sitting on the grass?\"\n"
"“Look, they are walking up the mountain. What does he have in his hand? The mountain is steep, so the stick helps him to keep his balance. What is he carrying on his back? What do you think is inside?”"
msgstr ""
"Ukiangalia ukurasa huu, hapa kuna baadhi ya mawazo ya nini unaweza kutaja na kumuelezea mtoto wako:\n"
" Tazama, kuna ndege amekaa kwenye lile ua.Ndege ana mdogo mkali ,na mkia mrefu. Naweza kuona ndege wengine wawili wanapaa angani, unaweza kuwaona? Wanafanana na nini? Tunaweza kuona nini kingine kinachopaa?”\n"
"Unaweza kuona mnyama gani amekaa kwenye mwamba? Na ni mnyama gani unaweza kumuona amekaa kwenye nyasi?”\n"
"“Tazama, wanatembea kwenda mlimani. Ana nini mkononi mwake? Mlima huo una mwinuko, hivyo fimbo humsaidia yeye kupata nguvu anapotembea. Amebeba nini mgongoni kwake? \n"
"Unafikiri ndani kuna nini?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Ask questions**\n"
" \n"
"This helps your child to talk about the pictures, and think about what is happening."
msgstr ""
"**Uliza maswali**\n"
"\n"
"Hii humsaidia mtoto wako kuzungumza kuhusu picha, na kufikiri kuhusu kile kinachotokea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Asking your child questions will help them talk about what they see in the pictures, and think about what is happening.\n"
"Using Who/What/Where/Why/How questions are great ways to encourage your child to answer using words other than “yes” and “no. \n"
"Questions like: \n"
"“Where is rabbit standing?\n"
"What are they eating? \n"
"Why are they lying down?”\n"
"Help your child understand events by asking them what is happening and why it is happening.\n"
"Help them understand the characters in the story better, by asking them why they think the character is doing that, or what the character might be thinking or feeling."
msgstr ""
"Kumuuliza mtoto wako maswali itamsaidia kuzungumza kuhusu nini anaona kwenye picha, na kufikiri kuhusu nini kinatokea.\n"
"Kutumia maswali ya Nani/Nini/Wapi/Kwanini/Namna gani ni njia nzuri ya kumtia moyo mtoto wako kujibu kwa kutumia maneno zaidi kuliko ‘ndio” na “hapana”\n"
"Maswali kama:\n"
"“Sungura amesimama wapi?\n"
"Wanakula nini?\n"
"Kwanini wamelala chini?\n"
"Saidia mtoto wako kufahamu matukio kwa kumuuliza nini kinatokea na kwanini inatokea.\n"
"Msaidie kufahamu vizuri wahusika wa kwenye hadithi, kwa kumuuliza kwanini anafikiri mhusika anafanya vile, au mhusika anaweza kuwa anafikiria nini au anajiskiaje."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Show your child you are listening.**\n"
"This will encourage your child to talk more."
msgstr ""
"**Muonyeshe mtoto wako unamsikiliza**\n"
"Hii itamtia moyo mtoto wako kuzungumza zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can I show my child that I am listening?"
msgstr "Nitawezaje kumuonyesha mtoto wangu kwamba ninamsikiliza?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "See examples:"
msgstr "Angalia Mifano:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"* Look at your child / make eye contact\n"
"* Nod your head\n"
"* Make encouraging sounds \n"
"* Respond to what they say"
msgstr ""
"* Mtazame mtoto wako/ fanya mawasiliano kwa macho \n"
"* Tikisa kichwa chako\n"
"* Tumia sauti za kutia moyo\n"
"* Itikia wanachosema"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Three easy ways to use book activities to talk:\n"
"1. Name and describe what you see in the pictures.\n"
"2. Ask questions about the story.\n"
"3. Show your child you are listening."
msgstr ""
"Njia tatu rahisi za kutumia shughuli za kitabu kuzungumza:\n"
"1. Taja na elezea unachokiona katika picha.\n"
"2. Muulize mtoto wako maswali kuhusu hadithi.\n"
"3. Muonyeshe mtoto wako kuwa unamsikiliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember to talk with kindness. Avoid being critical or negative."
msgstr "Kumbuka kuzungumza kwa upole. epuka kuwa mkosoaji au kuwa kinyume naye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Small actions, big results! Parents who practice at home get better results.\n"
"\n"
"For your home practice:\n"
"🤝 Remember the power of your words. Talk with kindness.\n"
"📖 Use book activities to talk, ask questions and interact with your child.\n"
"😌 Talking about what causes us stress can be helpful. Reach out to someone you trust if you are feeling stressed."
msgstr ""
"Matendo madogo, matokeo makubwa! Wazazi wanaofanya kwa vitendo nyumbani hupata matokeo makubwa. \n"
"\n"
"Kwa ajili ya kufanya kwa vitendo nyumbani\n"
"🤝Kumbuka nguvu ya maneno yako. Zungumza kwa upole.\n"
"📖 Tumia shughuli za kitabu kuzungumza, uliza maswali na changamana na mtoto wako\n"
"😌 Kuzungumza kuhusu nini kinachotusababishia msongo inaweza kusaidia. Muone yeyote unayemuamini kama unajiskia kuwa na msongo.\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who Took My Shoe?"
msgstr "Nani kachukua kiatu changu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jabulani has lost his school shoe. He can’t find it anywhere. Where can it be?"
msgstr "Jabulani amepoteza kiatu chake cha shule. Hawezi kukipata sehemu yoyote.Je kinaweza kuwa wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Come, Jabulani,\" Ma says.\"Why aren’t you ready? You’ll be late for school.\" \"I can’t find my shoe,\" says Jabulani."
msgstr "''Njoo, Jabulani,'' Mama anasema.''Kwanini hauko tayari? utachelewa shule.'\" Sioni viatu vyangu,\" anasemaJabulani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Did you look under your bed?\" says Ma. \"It’s not under my bed,\" Jabulani says."
msgstr "\"Ulliangalia chini ya kitanda chako\"? anasema Mama. \"Hakipo chini ya kitanda changu,\" anasema Jabulani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Did you look in the wardrobe?\" Ma asks. \"Yes, it’s not in the wardrobe.\""
msgstr "\"Uliangalia ndani ya kabati?\" aliuliza Mama.\"Ndio, hakipo ndani ya kabati\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I know where your shoe is,\" giggles Jabulani’s sister Lungi. \"Where?\" Jabulani asks. \"I’m not telling you!\" says Lungi"
msgstr "\"Ninajua kiatu chako kilipo\", huku akicheka Lungi dada yake Jabulani.''Wapi'' Jabulani anauliza ''Sikwambii!''anasema Lungi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Somebody’s taken it,\" Jabulani says."
msgstr "''Kuna mtu amekichukua'', Jabulani anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Why would someone take one shoe when they’ve got two feet?\" says Lungi."
msgstr "''Kwanini achukue kiatu kimoja wakati watu huwa wana miguu miwili?''anasema Lungi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I don’t know. Maybe they’ve hidden it to make me cross.\""
msgstr "\"Sijui. Labda wameificha ili kunifanya nihangaike\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Did you take my shoe?\" he asks Lungi."
msgstr "\" Ulichukua kiatu changu?\" alimuuliza Lungi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"No,\" says Lungi, \"your shoes are too big for me.\""
msgstr "\"Hapana\", alisema Lungi, \"Viatu vyako ni vikubwa sana kwangu\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Did you take my shoe?\" Jabulani asks Fruit Juice the Dog."
msgstr "\"Ulichukua kiatu changu?\"Jabulani alimuuliza Mbwa wake anayeitwa Sharubati."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She smiles her big dog smile at him and wags her tail."
msgstr "Anatabasamu kwa Mbwa wake mkubwa ametabasamu na akatingisha mkia wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Maybe a bird picked it up and flew away with your shoe,\" laughs Lungi."
msgstr "''Labda ndege alichukua na kuruka na kiatu chako'', anacheka Lungi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Maybe a monkey took it and left it up in a tree, \" says Jabulani."
msgstr "''Labda tumbili alikichukua na akakiacha juu ya mti,''anasema Jabulani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Don’t worry, we’ll find your shoe,\" says Ma. \"Everyone look for Jabulani’s shoe.\" But the shoe is nowhere to be found."
msgstr "''Usijali, tutapata kiatu chako'', anasema Mama.''Kila mtu atafute kiatu cha Jabulani.''lakini kiatu hakipatikani popote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"It’s all right,\" says Ma. \"You can wear your takkies to school today.\""
msgstr "''Ni sawa'', anasema Mama. unaweza kuvaa raba zako za michezo shuleni leo.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lungi comes rushing into the kitchen with a big smile on her face. \"I know where your shoe is,\" she shouts. \"Come and see.\""
msgstr "Lungi anakuja akikimbia jikoni akiwa na tabasamu kubwa usoni kwake. ''Najua kiatu chako kilipo,''anapiga kelele,''Njoo uone"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A Very Important Tree"
msgstr "Mti wa muhimu sana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Busi loves the big, beautiful tree outside her house. But her brother wants to cut it down. How will she stop him?"
msgstr "Busi anapenda mti mkubwa mzuri ulioko nnje ya nyumba yake. Lakini kaka yake anataka kuukata. Atafanyaje kumzuia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "An unexpected adventure"
msgstr "Tukio lisilotarajiwa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A boring afternoon turns into an exciting adventure when a little boy opens a book."
msgstr "Alasiri yaj kuchosha imegeuka kuwa tukio la kufurahisha pale mtoto mdogo wa kiume anapofungua kitabu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I don't want to go to sleep"
msgstr "Sitaki kwenda kulala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nandi doesn’t want to go to sleep. No way! She wants to go on an adventure. Join Nandi as she lets her imagination run wild and free."
msgstr "Nandi hataki kwenda kulala. Hakuna jinsi, anataka kuendelea na tukio. Ungana na Nandi kama anavyopata picha kuwa anakimbia porini na kwa uhuru."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"That’s enough now. Goodnight, Nandi.\""
msgstr "\"Imetosha sasa. Usiku mwema Nandi\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I ... don’t ... want ... to ... go ... to ... sleep.\""
msgstr "\"Sitaki kwenda kulala\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I want more supper. Another book! Just one more song?\" \"Goodnight, Nandi.\""
msgstr "\"Nataka chakula zaidi cha usiku. Kitabu kingine! Wimbo mmoja tu zaidi?' \"Usiku mwema, Nandi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I don’t want to go to sleep!\""
msgstr "\"Sitaki kwenda kulala\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"MAMA! ...I need a glass of water. Please? Please.\" \"It’s time to go to sleep now. Goodnight, Nandi.\""
msgstr "\"Mama!... Tafadhali nahitaji bilauri ya maji? Tafadhali. \" Ni muda wa kwenda kulala sasa. Usiku mwemza, Nandi\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I DON’T WANT TO GO TO SLEEP!\""
msgstr "\"SITAKI KWENDA KULALA\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama sighs: \"What about an adventure? Do you want an adventure?\""
msgstr "Mama anapumua;'''Vipi kuhusu utambuzi mpya? Unataka utambuzi mpya?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"...yes...\""
msgstr "''......ndio...''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Do you want to creep through the jungle on the trail of the fearsome hippocrocoturtleduck?\""
msgstr "''Unataka kutambaa msituni kwenye njia za kutisha za nyangumi kiboko na bata?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Yes! Yes! Yes!\""
msgstr "''Ndio!' 'Ndio! Ndio!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I want to fly across the sky! Leap from star to star! Fill my pockets with stardust!\""
msgstr "''Nataka kupaa kuzunguka anga! Kuruka kutoka nyota hadi nyota! Kujaza mifuko yangu na vumbi la nyota!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I want a Nandi-sized glass submarine to see the creatures at the bottom of the ocean! And a pet giant squid to do water ballet there with me!\""
msgstr "\"Nataka miwani kubwa kama ya Nandi ya kutumia kwenye manowari kutazama viumbe chini ya bahari na pweza mzuri na mkubwa wacheze na mimi kwenye maji!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I want to build myself a pair of butterfly wings and zoom to the roof of the sky where I’ll see all the world and everything in it!\""
msgstr "''Nataka kujitengenezea mabawa ya kipepeo na kuvuta hadi mawinguni ambapo nitauona ulimwengu wote na kila kitu ndani yake!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look here, Nandi. Here is your very own adventure boat. It’s waiting to take you wherever you want to go. See, put your head here...that’s right...and I’ll just tuck you in...there we go...now, off you go! Adventure awaits ...\""
msgstr "\"Tazama hapa Nandi. Hii ni boti yako kabisa ya kujivinjari. Inakusubiri ikupeleke popote unapotaka.Ona, weka kichwa chako hapa..., hiyo ni sawa... na nitakuvutia ndani... sasa tunaenda... ondoa boti! kujivinjari kunatusubiri\"..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Goodnight, Nandi.\""
msgstr "''Usiku mwema Nandi'',"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Draw your dreams here."
msgstr "Chora ndoto zako hapa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scared Tumi"
msgstr "Tumi anaogopa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What if there’s a monster under my bed?\" Tumi is scared. Mama tries to show him that everything is okay."
msgstr "''Je ikiwa kuna Zimwi chini ya kitanda changu?''Tumi anaogopa. Mama anajaribu kumuonyesha kwamba kila kitu kiko sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My name is Tumi and I am scared."
msgstr "Jina langu ni Tumi na ninaogopa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Mmh, the boy looks scared. I wonder what could have happened?"
msgstr "Sema, “Mmh, kijana anaonekana kuwa na hofu, nashangaa nini kimetokea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama says it’s okay to be scared. \"Everybody gets scared.\""
msgstr "Mama anasema ni sawa kuogopa.''Kilamtu huwa anaogopa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Sometimes I feel scared” Ask, “Have you ever felt scared? what do you think made you feel that way?”"
msgstr "Sema, \"Wakati mwingine ninaogopa\" Uliza, \"Je, umewahi kuogopa? unafikiri ni nini kilikufanya uhisi hivyo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if there is a monster under my bed?"
msgstr "Je ni vipi ikiwa kuna Zimwi chini ya kitanda changu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oh no, is that a monster under the bed? What is the boy going to do?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “show me what you do when you feel scared?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"La, hapana, je, huyo ni jini chini ya kitanda? Mvulana atafanya nini?\"\n"
"\n"
"Muombe, \"nionyeshe unachofanya unapohisi hofu?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Then I will tell it to go away and NEVER come back.\""
msgstr "''''Kisha nitakiambia kiondoke na KAMWE kisirudi tena'',"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “who do you go to when you feel scared? How do you feel when you are with them?”"
msgstr "Muulize.\"Huwa unakwenda kwa nani unapojiskia kuogopa?Huwa unajiskiaje ukiwa nao?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if there are eyes in the bath tub drain?"
msgstr "Je ikiwa kuna macho kwenye bomba la kuoga?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Oh no! Not another monster in the bathtub!”\n"
"Then point to each item and say, \"This is a bathtub (wait for the child to repeat). This is a tap (wait for the child to repeat). These are tiles (wait for the child to repeat). These are monster eyes! (wait for the child to repeat).”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"La! hapana! Hakuna jini lingine kwenye beseni la kuogea!\"\n"
"\n"
"Kisha onyesha kila kitu na useme, \"Hii ni beseni la kuogea (ngoja mtoto arudie). Hili ni bomba (subiri mtoto arudie). Hivi ni vigae (subiri mtoto arudie). Haya ni macho ya mnyama! (ngoja mtoto arudie)\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Then your big sister, Kamo, will pull you out of the bath.\""
msgstr "''Basi dada yako Kamo atakutoa nje ya bafu'',"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask, “Can you tell me what a bathtub is used for?” If the child does not know then help them by saying, “a bathtub is used to bath.”\n"
"\n"
"Say, “now tell me, do you enjoy bathing? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize,\"Je unaweza kuniambia beseni linatumika kwa matumizi gani?, \"Ikiwa mtoto hajui basi msaidie kusema beseni hutumika kwa ajili ya kuogea\".\n"
"\n"
"Sema,\" sasa niambie ,unafurahia kuoga?kwanini unafurahia na kwanini hufurahii?',"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if a whale swallows me at the beach?"
msgstr "Je itakuwaje ikiwa nyangumi ananimeza mimi nikiwa ufukweni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oh no, is that a whale at the beach? \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “how would you react if you saw a whale? why?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, Oh hapana, huyo ni nyangumi ufukweni?\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, Ungefanyaje kama ungemuona nyangumi? kwanini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Then Kamo and I will swim into the whale’s mouth to rescue you.\""
msgstr "''Kisha Kamo na mimi tutaogelea kwenye mdomo wa Nyangumi ili tukuokoe''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture of the boy in a whale and say, “oh no, the whale swallowed a boy. What are we going to do? \n"
"\n"
"Again say, “look, i think they are going to rescue the boy.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “how do you think the boy feels seeing them? Why?"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kwa kuelekezea kwenye picha ya kijana kwenye myangumi na useme, la, hapana, Nyangumi alimmeza mvulana. Tutafanyaje?\n"
"\n"
"Alafu sema, “tazama, Nafikiri wanakwenda kumuokoa mvulana.”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, Unafikiri mvulana anajisikiaje kuwaona? kwanini??"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if I can’t sing ABC and the other kids laugh at me?"
msgstr "Je itakuwaje kama siwezi kuimba ABC na watoto wengine wananicheka?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask, “how many people do you see in this picture? How many have hair?  What color is their clothes? Who is the tallest?”\n"
"\n"
"Say, “guess what, the tallest is the teacher.”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize, “ni watu wangapi unawaona kwenye picha hii? Wangapi wana nywele? nguo zao ni za rangi gani? nani mrefu zaidi?\n"
"\n"
"“Sema, Unajua nini, mrefu zaidi ni mwalimu”."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Then Teacher Jill will help you remember.\""
msgstr "''Kisha mwalimu Jill atakusaidia kukumbuka'',"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Do you have a teacher? Who is your teacher?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize, “Una mwalimu? Mwalimu wako ni nani?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if I'm scared of going to the dentist tomorrow?"
msgstr "Je itakuwaje kama ninaogopa kwenda kwa Daktari wa meno kesho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look! This looks like a dentist's room. Do you know what a dentist is?\"\n"
"\"Imagine your teeth are like little building blocks in your mouth. A dentist is a special helper who makes sure those building blocks stay strong and clean! They help keep your smile healthy and happy!”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! hiki kinafanana na chumba cha daktari wa meno. Unajua daktari wa neno ni nani?”\n"
"\n"
"“Fikiria meno yako yanafanana na matofari kwenye mdomo wako. Daktari wa meno ni mtoa msaada maalum ambaye huhakikisha yale matofari yanakuwa masafi na imara! wanasaidia kutunza furaha na afya ya tabasamu lako!”   "

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I will be right there holding your hand.\" Everybody gets scared. Mama says it’s okay."
msgstr "''Nitakuwa hapo nimekushika mkono'', kila mtu anaogopa, Mama anasema ni sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look! The boy is smiling! Maybe he's not scared anymore.\"\n"
"Then, smile really big and say, \"See? This is my smile! It makes me happy to smile!\"  Then ask: \"Now you show me your smile! How does it feel when you smile?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! Mvulana anatabasamu! nadhani haogopi tena.” \n"
"\n"
"Alafu, toa tabasamu kubwa na useme, “umeona? Hili ni tabasamu langu! ninajisikia mwenye furaha kutabasamu!” Alafu muulize: sasa unanionyesha tabasamu lako! unajisikiaje unapotabasamu?”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mom's Red Coat"
msgstr "Koti la mama Jekundu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mom needs to go away for work. I’ll miss her. Will it help if she leaves her red coat with me?"
msgstr "Mama anahitaji kusafiri kikazi, Nitamkumbuka sana. Akiniachia koti lake jekundu itasaidia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Book Dash, 2022. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Book Dash, 2002. Haki zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I love Mom’s coat! It’s red and long and warm. And it smells like Mom!"
msgstr "Napenda koti la mama! Ni jekundu, refu na lenye joto. Na lina linanukia kama mama!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what are they doing? What colour is her coat?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wanafanya nini? Koti lake ni la rangi gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I love doing things with Mom! We picnic outside. She hugs me when I come home from school. We work in the garden. At night, she holds me tight until I fall asleep."
msgstr "Napenda kufanya vitu na mama! Tunafanya pikiniki nje. Ananikumbatia ninapokuja nyumbani kutoka shule. Tunafanya kazi bustanini. Usiku, ananikumbatia sana mpaka ninalala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe what you see, or ask your child to tell you what they see."
msgstr "Elezea unachokiona, au mwambie mtoto wako akwambie wanaona nini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Good news!\" says Mom. \"I found a job! I will be away all week, but I’ll come home on weekends!\""
msgstr "\"Habari njema\" anasema mama.\" Nimepata kazi! Nitakuwa mbali wiki nzima, lakini nitakuja nyumbani siku wa mwisho wa wiki!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic actions from the pictures or story, like the mom being excited."
msgstr "Igiza matendo kutoka kwenye picha au hadithi, kama vile mama akiwa na furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Who will hold me at night, Mom?\" \"Who will hug me, picnic with me, garden with me?\""
msgstr "\"Nani atanikumbatia usiku, mama?\" \"Nani atanikumbatia, kufanya pikiniki na mimi, kufanya kazi za bustani na mimi?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I can see that you are sad. I will leave my red coat here with you.\" \"When you see it, remember that I love you and I’m coming back.\""
msgstr "\"Nakuona una huzuni,. Nitakuachia koti langu jekundu.\" \" Utakapoliona kumbuka kwamba nakupenda na nitarudi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help your child understand, explain what is happening. Say: Look, the mom has to go, but she is leaving her red coat behind for her son to comfort him."
msgstr "Kumsaidia mtoto wako kuelewa, elezea nini kinatokea. Sema: Tazama, mama anatakiwa kuondoka, lakini anaacha koti lake jekundu kwaajili ya kumfariji mtoto wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I drag the red coat outside – it’s my picnic blanket! It feels like Mom is with me."
msgstr "Ninavuta koti jekundu nje - ni blanketi langu la pikiniki! Najiskia kama mama yupo na mimi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oops! Juice spill!"
msgstr "Oops! Juisi imemwagika!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where is the boy? Where is his mom’s red coat? What is he doing?"
msgstr "Uliza: Kijana wa kiume yuko wapi? Koti jekundu la mama yake liko wapi? Anafanya nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sad that Mom’s not waiting at the door when I come home. I put on her coat. It’s warm and it smells like her. It feels like a hug!"
msgstr "Nina huzuni mama hajanisubiri mlangoni ninapokuja nyumbani. Nina vaa koti lake. Ni la moto na linanukia kama yeye. Najiskia kama nimekumbatiwa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oops! Paint!"
msgstr "Oops! rangi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use descriptive words to talk about the pictures. Say: Look, he is wearing his mom’s red coat. He is holding a paint brush in one hand and a picture in the other hand."
msgstr "Tumia maneno ya maelezo kuzungumzia picha. Sema tazama amevaa koti jekundu la mama yake. Ameshika brashi ya rangi mkono mmoja na picha kwa mkono mwingine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I help Gogo in the garden. The long coat on the branch scares away the chickens! It feels like Mom is gardening with us. Oops! Mud!"
msgstr "Namsaidia Bibi bustanini. Koti kubwa kwenye tawi linatisha kuku! Najiskia kama mama anafanya kazi bustanini na sisi. Oops! tope!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where is the red coat now? What animals can you see under the tree? Do they look the same, or are they different? Are they going in the same direction or in opposite directions?"
msgstr "Uliza: liko wapi koti jekundu sasa? Unaweza kuona wanyama gani chini ya mti? Je wanaonekana sawa au wako tofauti? Je wanaelekea upande mmoja au pande tofauti?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When it’s dark, I miss Mom most. Gogo covers me with her warm coat. It feels like Mom is holding me as I fall asleep. Oops! Cookie crumbs!"
msgstr "Ikiwa giza. Namkumbuka sana mama, Bibi ananifunika na koti lake lenye joto. Ninajisikia kama mama ananishikilia ninapolala. Oops! makombo ya vireja!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where is the red coat now? What is the boy doing? Why do you think he is doing that? Do you think he might be missing his mom?"
msgstr "Uliza: Koti jekundu liko wapi sasa? Je mvulana anafanya nini? unafikiri ni kwa nini anafanya hivyo? Unafikiri atakuwa amemkumbuka mama yake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mom’s red coat is warm and smells like...paint, juice, mud, and cookie crumbs! Oops! We need to wash it!"
msgstr "Koti la mama jekundu lina joto na linanukia kama....rangi, juisi,matope, na masalia ya vitafunwa!Oops! Tunahitaji kulifua!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: Look, the red coat is hanging on the washing line. Ask: Why do you think they washed the coat? What else is hanging on the washing line? How many socks can you see?"
msgstr "Sema: Tazama, koti jekundu linaning'inia kwenye kamba. Uliza: Unafikiri kwanini walifua koti? Ni kitu gani kingine kipo kwenye kamba ya kuanikia nguo? unaweza kuona soksi ngapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The wind blows the red coat off the washing line...up into the air! It flies over the fence! It flies over the taxi! Oops! Who did the coat fall on?"
msgstr "Upepo unapeperusha koti jekundu kwenye kamba...unalipeleka hewani! linapeperukia kwenye uzio! Linapeperukia kwenye taksi! Oops! Nani ameliangusha koti?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: Look, the wind blew the red coat away. Ask: who do you think is under the coat? Why do you think so?"
msgstr "Semaa: Tazama, upepo umelipeperusha koti jekundu mbali, Uliza: Unadhani ni nani yuko chini ya koti? Kwanini unafikiri hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I run and grab it! \"Found you, coat!\" The red coat smells like Mom again. \"Oh!\" \"Found you, Mom! You’re back!\""
msgstr "Nakimbia na kulikamata! \"Nimekukamata wewe koti\" Koti jekundu linanukia kama mama tena. \"Oh!\"\" Nimekupata, Mama! umerudi!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Demonstrate the emotions from the story. Say in a happy voice: hooray! His mom is back! Ask: how do you think he is feeling now?"
msgstr "Onyesha hisia kutoka kwenye hadithi. Sema kwa sauti ya furaha: huree! Mama yake amerudi! Uliza: Unafikiri anajiskiaje sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When Will Amma Be Back?"
msgstr "Ni lini Mama atarudi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Roja’s mother leaves for work early in the day. She promises to be back by bedtime. What will Roja do all day without Amma?"
msgstr "Mama yake Roja anaenda kazini mapema. Ameahidi kurudi muda wa kulala. Roja atafanya nini siku nzima bila mama?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Pratham Books, 2018. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Vitabu vya Pratham, 2018. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Roja is sad. Amma is going to work. \"I will be back before bedtime, kannamma,\" says Amma."
msgstr "Roja ana huzuni. Mama anaenda kazini. \"Nitarudi kabla ya muda wa kulala, kannamma,\" anasema mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"But at what time?\" asks Roja. \"At exactly 9 o’clock tonight,\" replies Amma. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 6 o’clock in the morning."
msgstr "\" Lakini ni muda gani?\"Roja anauliza. \"Saa tatu kamili usiku,\" mama anajibu. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa 12 kamili asubuhi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I want Amma to give me milk. Not you!\" says Roja to Appa. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 8 o’clock in the morning."
msgstr "\" Namtaka mama anipe maziwa. Sio wewe!\" Roja anamwambia baba. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa mbili kamili asubuhi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Let’s buy potatoes, Thaatha!\" says Roja. \"But we had potatoes just yesterday. How about brinjal today?\" Thaatha asks. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 10 o’clock in the morning."
msgstr "\"Na tununue viazi, babu\" Roja anasema. \"Lakini tulikuwa na viazi jana tu. Vipi kuhusu biringanya leo?\" Babu anasema. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa nne kamili asubuhi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Paati, let’s eat. Thaatha is making pappadam!\" Roja yells. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 1 o’clock in the afternoon."
msgstr "\"\"Paati, hebu tule. Babu anatengeneza vitafunwa!\" Roja alisema kwa sauti. Tick tock Tick tock! Ni saa saba kamili mchana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Honk! Honk! Roja’s Akka is back from school. \"Paati says I will go to school with you after this summer. Won’t that be fun,Akka?\" says Roja, excitedly. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 3 o’clock in the afternoon."
msgstr "Hodi! hodi! Kaka yake Roja amerudi kutoka shule.\"Paati anasema nitaenda shule na wewe baada ya majira haya ya joto. Si itakuwa ya kufurahisha kaka?\" anasema Roja kwa furaha. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa tisa kamili mchana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"It’s time to go home, Roja,\" Appa calls out. \"Just one last time!\" shouts Roja. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 5 o’clock in the evening."
msgstr "\"Ni muda wa kwenda nyumbani, Roja \" Baba aliita. \"Mara moja tu ya mwisho\" Roja alipiga kelele. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa kumi na moja jioni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Selvi, eat your dosai quickly! Only then will you become big and strong,\" says Roja. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 7 o’clock at night."
msgstr "\"Selvi, kula chapati yako haraka! Itakufanya uwe mkubwa na mwenye nguvu,\" anasema Roja, Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa moja kamili usiku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"And so, when the cap-seller threw down his cap, the monkeys threw their caps down too... \""
msgstr "\"Na hivyo, muuza kofia aliporusha chini kofia yake, ngedere walirusha kofia zao chini pia...\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"AMMMAAAA!\" Roja shouts. \"What did you do all day, Roja?\" Amma asks. Tick tock! Tick tock! It is almost 9 o’clock at night."
msgstr "\"Mamaaaaa\" Roja aliita kwa sauti. \"Ulifanya nini siku nzima, Roja?\" Mama anauliza. Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni takriban saa tatu kamili usiku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I had a lot of fun today, Amma! Appa fed me breakfast. I bought brinjal with Thaatha. He made pappadam for lunch."
msgstr "\"Nilikuwa na vingi vya kufurahisha leo, Mama! Baba alinilisha kifungua kinywa. Nilinunua bilinganya na babu. Alitengeneza chapati kwajili ya chakula cha mchana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I picked up Akka from the school van. I played in the park. I fed Selvi dinner. Appa told me a story and now you are back!\" Roja says, with a wide smile."
msgstr "Nilimpokea kaka kutoka gari ya shule. Nilicheza sehemu ya michezo. Nilimlisha Selvi chakula cha usiku. Baba alinisimulia hadithi and sasa umerudi!\" Roja anasema, kwa tabasamu kubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tick tock! Tick tock! It is 9 o’clock at night!"
msgstr "Tick tock! Tick tock! Ni saa tatu kamili usiku!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**My Day**\n"
"Here are some things that Roja does at different times of the day. What did you do at the same time yesterday? Draw pictures of yourself doing these different things on a piece of paper.\n"
"1. Roja eats breakfast at 8 o’clock. What did you do at 8 o’clock yesterday?\n"
"2. Roja goes shopping at 10 o’clock. What did you do at 10 o’clock yesterday?\n"
"3. Roja eats lunch at 1 o’clock. What did you do at 1 o’clock yesterday?"
msgstr ""
"**Siku yangu**\n"
"Hivi ni baadhi ya vitu ambavyo Roja anafanya katika wakati tofauti katika siku. Ulifanya nini muda huo huo jana? Chora picha yako katika kipande cha kariatasi inayoonyesha unafanya vitu hivi mbalimbali. \n"
"1. Roja anapata kifungua kinywa saa mbili kamili asubuhi. Ulifanya nini saa mbili kamili asubuhi jana?\n"
"2. Roja anaenda dukani saa nne kamili asubuhi. Ulifanya nini saa nne kamili asubuhi jana?\n"
"3. Roja anakula chakula cha mchana saa saba kamili. Ulfanya nini saa saba kamili mchana jana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"4. Roja picks up Akka from the school van at 3 o’clock. What did you do at 3 o’clock yesterday?\n"
"5. Roja plays in the park at 5 o’clock. What did you do at 5 o’clock yesterday?\n"
"6. Roja feeds Selvi at 7 o’clock. What did you do at 7 o’clock yesterday?"
msgstr ""
"4. Roja anampokea kaka kutoka kwenye gari ya shule saa tisa kamili alasiri. Ulifanya nini saa tisa kamili alasiri jana?\n"
"5. Roja anacheza kwenye sehemu ya michezo saa kumi na moja jioni. Ulifanya nini saa kumi na moja jioni jana?\n"
"6. Roja anamlisha Selvi saa moja kamili usiku. Ulifanya nini saa moja kamili usiku jana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover. Ask: What do you see? What is the bee doing? Where is the bee lying down?”"
msgstr "Jadili jalada la juu la kitabu: Muulize: Unaona nini? Unafikiri  nyuki anafanya nini? Nyuki amelala wapi?’’"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The Bee and the Elephant"
msgstr "Nyuki na Tembo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "An elephant tries to help a little lost bee find his home. Is it the nest? The cave? Where does he live?"
msgstr "Tembo anajaribu kumsaidia nyuki mdogo aliyepotea,kupata nyumbani kwao. Je ni kiota? Ni pango? Anaishi wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I am lost,\" said Little Bee. \"I cannot find my home!\" \"Can you please help me, Mr. Elephant?\""
msgstr ""
"\"Nimepotea,\" alisema nyuki mdogo. \"Siwezi pata nyumbani kwetu!\" \"Tafadhali unaweza\n"
"nisaidia, Bwana. Tembo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Oh no, I think the bee is lost, it is all alone.” Ask: “Can you tell how the bee is feeling? Why do you think so? Who do you see behind the bee?”"
msgstr "Sema:  “Oh hapana, nafikiri nyuki amepotea, yuko peke yake.” Muulize: unaweza kusema nyuki anajiskiaje? Kwanini unafikiri hivyo? Unamuona nani nyuma ya nyuki?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Is this nest your home, Little Bee?\" the elephant asked."
msgstr "\"Hiki kiota ni nyumbani kwako, Nyuki mdogo?\" Tembo aliuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, the bee is sitting on the elephant's trunk! What is the elephant doing? Where is he putting the bee? Why do you think he is putting him there?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Angalia Nyuki amekaa kwenye mkonga wa tembo! Tembo anafanya nini? Amemuweka wapi nyuki? Unafikiri kwanini anamuweka pale?” \n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh no!\" cried Little Bee. \"This is a bird’s home.\""
msgstr "\"Oh hapana!\" Alilia Nyuki mdogo. \"Hapa ni nyumbani Kwa ndege.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many animals can you see? Can you name them? Which one is the biggest? Which one is the smallest?”"
msgstr "Muulize: “Unaona wanyama wangapi” Unaweza kuwataja? Je ni yupi mkubwa zaidi? Ni yupi mdogo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Is this cave your home?\" asked the elephant."
msgstr "\"Hili pango ni nyumbani kwako?\" aliuliza tembo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, there is the cave. Where could the elephant be taking the bee?” Ask: “Would you go to the cave?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Tazama,kuna pango.Tembo anampeleka wapi  nyuki?’’ Muulize: Je unaweza kwenda kwenye pango?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh no! This is a bat’s home.\""
msgstr "\"Oh hapana! Hapa ni nyumbani Kwa Popo.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, the elephant and bee are running away!” (mimic the sound and the action). Ask: “What are they running from? Can you show me how you  can run?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: Tazama, Tembo na nyuki wanakimbia!” (Iga sauti na kitendo). Muulize:  “Wanakimbia nini? Unaweza kunionyesha jinsi  unavyoweza kukimbia?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Is this hive your home, Little Bee?\""
msgstr "\"Huu mzinga ni nyumbani kwako, Nyuki mdogo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Wala, there is a beehive! Finally, the bee is home!” Ask: How do you think the bee feels now? How do you think the elephant feels? How do you feel when you get home? Why do you feel like that?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Wala,Kuna mzinga wa nyuki! Hatimaye nyuki yuko nyumbani!” Muulize: \"Unafikiri nyuki anajiskiaje sasa? Unafikiri tembo anajiskiaje? Unajiskiaje unapofika nyumbani? Kwanini unajiskia hivyo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh yes!\" said Little Bee happily. \"This is my home.\""
msgstr "\"Oh ndio!\" alisema nyuki mdogo Kwa furaha. \"Hapa ni nyumbani Kwangu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use a picture to help your child count. Ask: “How many bees can you see? How many eyes do you see? Now count your eyes, how many eyes do you have?”"
msgstr ""
"Tumia picha kumsaidia mtoto wako kuhesabu. \n"
"Muulize: “Unaona nyuki wangapi? Unaona macho mangapi? Sasa hesabu macho yako, una macho mangapi?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Thank you for helping me, Mr. Elephant.\""
msgstr "\"Asante kwakunisaidia,Bwana Tembo.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, the bees, the bird and the bats are flying. What sound do bees make when they fly? And what about birds?” Ask: “How many bees can you see? And how many bats can you see?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Tazama, nyuki, ndege na popo wanaruka. Nyuki hutoa mlio gani wanaporuka? Na vipi kuhusu ndege?” Muulize: “Unaweza kuona nyuki wangapi? Na ni popo wangapi unaweza kuwaona?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What do you think about this story? How would you feel if you were in the story? What would you have done if you were the elephant?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: Unafikiri nini kuhusu hadithi hii? Ungejiskiaje kama ungekuwa kwenye hadithi? Ungefanyaje kama wewe ungekuwa tembo?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Katiiti’s Song"
msgstr "Wimbo wa Katiti"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Every day, Katiiti’s mother calls her with a beautiful song. One day, a crafty gorilla tries to sing as sweetly as her mother."
msgstr "Kila siku, Mama yake Katiti anamwita kwa wimbo mzuri. Siku moja, Sokwe mwerevu alijaribu kuimba vizuri kama mama yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Katiiti lived in a village next to a forest."
msgstr "Katiti anaishi kwenye kijiji karibu na msitu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She loved playing in the forest. Maama told her to be careful."
msgstr "Anapenda kucheza msituni. Mama alimwambia awe makini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Every day Maama would sing their special song to call her."
msgstr "Kila siku Mama anaimba wimbo wao maalumu kumwita."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One day, Katiiti bumped into a gorilla."
msgstr "Siku moja, Katiti alijigonga kwa Sokwe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She ran and hid in a cave."
msgstr "Alikimbia na kujificha pangoni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gorilla came and sang Maama’s song in a gruff voice."
msgstr "Sokwe alikuja na aliimba wimbo wa Mama kwa sauti nzito na kali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gorilla ate lots of bananas to make his voice sweeter."
msgstr "Sokwe alikula ndizi nyingi kufanya sauti yake iwe nzuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gorilla sang sweetishly."
msgstr "Sokwe aliimba vizuuuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gorilla went away and ate lots of honey to make his voice even sweeter."
msgstr "Sokwe alienda mbali na alikula asali nyingi kuifanya sauti yake iwe nzuri zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gorilla sang as sweetly as Maama."
msgstr "Sokwe aliimba vizuri kama Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maama came just in time to chase away Gorilla."
msgstr "Mama alikuja kwa wakati kumfukuza Sokwe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Katiiti and Maama sang all the way back home."
msgstr "Katiti na Mama waliimba njia nzima wakiwa wanarudi nyumbani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A Beautiful Day"
msgstr "Siku Nzuri"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s a beautiful day for a picnic. Everyone wants to join in the fun."
msgstr "Ni siku nzuri ya pikiniki. Kila mmoja anataka kujiunga kwenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What a beautiful day,\" says Mom. \"Wake up Nicholas.\""
msgstr "\"Siku nzuri namna gani,\" Mama anasema. \"Amka Nicholaus.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Hello sun,\" says Nicholas. \"Good morning birds.\""
msgstr "\"Haloo jua,\" Nicholaus anasema. \"Habari za asubuhi ndege.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, the boy just woke up.” Ask: “What do you think the mother is saying to the boy? Can you tell me how the boy is feeling? What is the baby pointing to? Who else sees what the baby sees?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Angalia, kijana ameamka.\" Uliza: \"Unafikiri mama anamwambia nini mvulana? Unaweza kuniambia jinsi mvulana anavyohisi? Mtoto anaonyesha nini? Nani mwingine anaona kile mtoto anachokiona?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"It’s a lovely day,\" says Dad. \"Let’s have a picnic by the river.\""
msgstr "\"Ni siku nzuri,\" Baba anasema. \"Wacha tukatembelee mandhari ya ufukwe wa mto.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Can my friend Jacob come?\" asks Nicholas."
msgstr "\"Je rafiki yangu Jakobo anaweza kuja?\" Nicholaus anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Wow, it's such a beautiful day.” Ask: What are they eating for breakfast? What did you eat for breakfast this morning? What can you see through their window? And what can you see through our window?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Wow, ni siku nzuri sana.\" Uliza: Wanakula nini kama kifungua kinywa? Umekula nini kama kifungua kinywa asubuhi ya leo? Unaweza kuona nini kupitia dirisha lao? Na unaweza kuona nini kupitia dirisha letu?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Don’t forget me. I love picnics!\" says Donkey. \"And me. I want to come too!\" says Dog."
msgstr "\"Usisahau. Napenda pikiniki!\" Punda anasema. \"Na mimi. Pia nataka kuja!\" Mbwa anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Follow us,\" say the birds."
msgstr "\"Tufuateni,\" Ndege wanasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many children can you see? How are they feeling? Can you name all the animals? How many birds can you see? Which bird is flying the highest? And which bird is flying the lowest?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Je! unaweza kuona watoto wangapi? Wanajisikiaje? Je, unaweza kutaja wanyama wote? Unaweza kuona ndege wangapi? Ni ndege gani anayeruka juu zaidi? Na ni ndege gani anayeruka chini zaidi?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Where do you think they are going? Who is walking in the front? And who is walking at the back?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Unafikiri wanaenda wapi? Ni nani anayetembea mbele yao? Na ni nani anayetembea nyuma?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I’ll race you to that tree,\" Nicholas says."
msgstr "\"Nitakukimbizia kwenye ule mti!\" Nicholaus anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Now the boy is pointing at the tree, I think they are getting ready to see who can reach the tree first. Ready, set, go!!!!!” Ask your child: “Who do you think will win the race? Let’s go to the next page to find out.”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Sasa Mvulana  anaonyesha kwa kuelekezea kwenye mti, nadhani wanajiandaa kuona ni nani anayeweza kufika kwenye mti kwanza. Tayari, weka, nenda!!!!!\" Muulize mtoto wako: “Unafikiri ni nani atashinda shindano hilo? Twende kwenye ukurasa unaofuata ili kujua.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I won, I won,\" says Donkey. \"Not fair,\" says Nicholas. \"You’ve got four legs.\""
msgstr "\"Nimeshinda, nimeshinda,\" Punda anasema. \"Sio sawa,\" Nicholaus anasema. \"Wewe una miguu minne anasema Nicholaus.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Hurray! The monkey won the race”. Ask: Who looks tired? Why do you think he is tired?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Haya! Ngedere ameshinda mbio.\" Muulize: Nani anaonekana amechoka? Unafikiri kwa nini amechoka?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look what I can do,\" says Nicholas."
msgstr "\"Angalia ninachoweza kufanya,\" Nicholaus anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I bet you can’t do this,\" says Jacob."
msgstr "\"Nabashiri huwezi kufanya hiki.\" Jakobo anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What are they doing? Can you do any of these moves? Show me!”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Wanafanya nini? Unaweza kufanya mojawapo ya matendo haya? Nionyeshe!\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Here’s our picnic spot,\" says Dad."
msgstr "\"Hapa ni eneo la mandhari yetu,\" Baba anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture by saying, “Wow, mom and dad have found a beautiful picnic spot next to the river.” Ask: “How do you think everyone is going to feel about it?”"
msgstr "Eleza picha hiyo kwa kusema, \"Lo, mama na baba wamepata sehemu nzuri ya pikiniki karibu na mto.\" Muulize: \"Unafikiri kila mtu atahisije kuhusu hilo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Race you to the water!\" says Jacob."
msgstr "\"Nakukimbizia kwenye maji!\" Jakobo anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What are they doing? Wheeee, they are jumping into the water! Who is making the biggest splash? Would you also jump in? Why or why not?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Wanafanya nini? Weeee, wanaruka ndani ya maji! Ni nani anayepiga maji zaidi? Je, unaweza pia kuruka kwenye maji? Kwa nini au kama huwezi ni kwa nini?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Come and eat, boys and girls,\" says Mom."
msgstr "\"Njooni tule, wavulana na wasichana,\" Mama anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What is everyone eating? What would you choose to eat? Is everyone eating food? What about the baby? And what about the donkey?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Kila mtu anakula nini? Ungechagua kula nini? Je, kila mtu anakula chakula? Vipi kuhusu mtoto? Na vipi kuhusu punda?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Time to go home,\" says Mom. \"Say goodbye to Jacob.\""
msgstr "\"Wakati wakurudi nyumbani,\" Mama anasema. \"Mwambie Jakobo kwa heri.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say: “Now it is time to go home (mimic waving and saying goodbye). Can you also wave?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask: “Now tell me, how do you feel when you have to leave your friends after playing together? Why do you feel that way?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: \"Sasa ni muda wa kwenda nyumbani (igiza kupunga mkono na kusema kwaheri). Je, unaweza pia kupunga mkono?\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize: “Sasa niambie, unajisikiaje unapolazimika kuachana na marafiki zako baada ya kucheza pamoja? Kwa nini unajiskia hivyo?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Help your child learn new words. Say: Look, the sky is dark and the stars are out, it is time to sleep.” Then say: What is on the roof of their house? Where is the pumpkin? And where are the bricks?”\n"
"\n"
"“Would you enjoy a picnic? Let’s have our lunch outside under the tree today and pretend to have our own picnic!”"
msgstr ""
"Msaidie mtoto wako kujifunza maneno mapya. Sema: Tazama mbingu ni giza na nyota ziko nje, ni wakati wa kulala. Kisha sema: Kuna nini juu ya paa la nyumba yao? Boga liko wapi? Na matofali yako wapi?\n"
"\n"
"Je, unaweza kufurahia pikiniki? Hebu tule chakula chetu cha mchana nje chini ya mti leo na tujifanye tuna pikiniki yetu wenyewe!\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A trip to the tap"
msgstr "Safari ya kwenda bombani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oluhle fetches water at the tap every day. She gets to carry her favourite pink bucket. But one day it gets lost …"
msgstr "Maria huwa anachota maji bombani kila siku. Anatakiwa abebe ndoo yake anayoipenda ya rangi ya pinki. Lakini siku moja ilipotea…"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oluhle wakes up early. She is excited to get water. “Come Mama, we have to be first today,” she calls."
msgstr "Maria anaamka mapema. Anafurahia kufata maji. \"Njoo Mama, tunatakiwa kuwa wa kwanza leo,\" aliita."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On the way they meet Nathi and Unathi. They are going to the tap with their mother."
msgstr "Wakiwa njiani walikutana na Tamala na Tamali. Wanaenda bombani na mama yao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oluhle and her friends play while the grown-ups get water. “Oluhle, your bucket is full,” says Mama."
msgstr "Oluhle na rafiki zake wanacheza wakati wakubwa wanachota maji. \"Oluhle, ndoo yako imejaa,\" anasema Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "At home, Oluhle takes a bath. Mama goes to work and Oluhle stays with Makhulu."
msgstr "Nyumbani, Olhle anaoga. Mama anenda kazini na Oluhle anabaki na Mkhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "In the afternoon Makhulu starts to make supper. She needs more water. She calls Oluhle so they can go to the tap."
msgstr "Mchana Makulu anaanza kupika chakula cha jioni. anahitaji maji zaidi. Anamwita Maria ili waende bombani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Makhulu, I can’t find my bucket. I searched everywhere,” says Oluhle. Makhulu helps her look, but the bucket is nowhere to be found."
msgstr "\"Makulu, siioni ndoo yangu. Nimetafuta kila mahali,\" anasema Maria. Makulu anamsaidia kutafuta, lakini ndoo haionekani popote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Makhulu thinks of a plan. She gets a 2-litre bottle from the cupboard and fetches paints and paint brushes."
msgstr "Makulu anafikiria mpango. Anachukua chupa mbili ndogo kutoka kabatini na anachukua rangi na brashi za kupakia rangi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Makhulu makes a bucket from the water bottle. She paints it pink. “Here’s a recycled bucket, Oluhle!”"
msgstr "Makulu anatengeneza ndoo kutoka kwenye chupa ya maji. Anapaka rangi ya pinki. \" Hii hapa ni ndoo iliyotengenezwa tena, Maria \""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Thank you, Makhulu,” says Oluhle. She is excited to go to the tap with her new recycled bucket."
msgstr "\"Asante, Makulu,\" anasema Maria. Anafurahia kwenda bombani akiwa na ndoo yake mpya iliyotengenezwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The next day Unathi and Nathi bring two bottles to Makhulu. “Makhulu, could you please make recycled buckets for us?”"
msgstr "Siku iliyofuata Tamala na Natanieli walimletea Makulu chupa mbili. \"Makulu, tafadhali unaweza kutugengenezea ndoo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Makhulu paints their buckets yellow and blue, their favourite colours. Nathi and Unathi are happy. Oluhle is happy too."
msgstr "Makulu anapaka ndoo zao rangi ya njano na bluu, rangi zao pendwa. Tamali na Tamala wamefurahi. Maria amefurahi pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The friends can’t wait to show off with their new buckets. “Can we go to the tap now?” they ask."
msgstr "Marafiki wana hamu ya kuringishia ndoo zao mpya. \" Tunaweza kwenda bombani sasa?\" waliuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi and Teddy"
msgstr "Fifi na Teddy"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi has a brown teddy bear that she loves very much. But where is Teddy?"
msgstr "Fifi ana mdori wa rangi ya kahawia ambaye anampenda sana. Lakini Teddy yuko wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi has loved Teddy since she was a baby."
msgstr "Fifi alimpenda Teddy tangu alipokuwa mdogo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, there is a girl and a teddy.” Ask: “Who do you think this teddy belongs to?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: \"Tazama, kuna msichana na mdoli.\" Muulize: \"Unafikiri mdoli huyu ni wa nani?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi eats with Teddy. Fifi plays with Teddy."
msgstr "Fifi anakula na Teddy. Fifi anacheza na Teddy."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and Ask: “What do you think the girl and teddy are doing?” Point to the picture of the girl on the swing and ask again: “How do you think she is feeling? Why do you say that?”"
msgstr "Elekeza kwenye picha na Muulize: \"Unafikiri msichana na mdoli wanafanya nini?\" Elekeza kwenye picha ya msichana aliye kwenye bembea na muulize tena: \"Unafikiri anajiskiaje? Kwa nini unasema hivyo?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi takes Teddy wherever she goes. And they curl up together every night."
msgstr "Fifi anaenda na Teddy popote anapoenda. Na wanacheza pamoja kila siku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Who is sitting at the back of the car? Where do you think they might be going? Where is teddy sleeping? Do you sleep with anything in your bed?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Nani ameketi nyuma ya gari? Unafikiri wanaweza kuwa wanaenda wapi? Mdoli analala wapi? Je, unalala na kitu chochote kitandani?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fifi knows she cannot take Teddy to school. So every morning she leaves Teddy on her bed."
msgstr "Fifi anajua hawezi kwenda shule na Teddy. Hivyo kila asubuhi anamuacha Teddy."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Oh no! Where is the girl? Teddy is alone. How do you think Teddy feels?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"La! Msichana yuko wapi? Mdoli  yuko peke yake. Unafikiri Mdoli anajisikiaje?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One day, when she comes back from school, Teddy is not there!"
msgstr "Siku moja, alipokuwa akirudi kutoka shule, Teddy hakuwepo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say: “Look who's back. Oh no, Teddy is not there.” Mimic for your child a surprised expression.\n"
"\n"
"Ask: “how would you feel if your special toy went missing?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: \"Angalia nani amerudi. La hasha, Mdoli hayupo.\" Muigizie mtoto wako usemi wa mshangao.\n"
"\n"
"Muulize: \"Ungejiskiaje kama mdoli wako pendwa haonekani?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What is the girl looking for? Where is she looking? Where do you think teddy might have gone?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Msichana anatafuta nini? Anatafuta wapi? Unafikiri mdoli anaweza kuwa ameenda wapi?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Where is she looking now? Where could teddy be hiding?” Mimic searching and feeling frustrated."
msgstr "Muulize: \"Anaangalia wapi sasa? Mdoli atakuwa amejificha wapi?\" Igiza kutafuta  na kuhisi kukatishwa tamaa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s wrong, Fifi?” asks Mom."
msgstr "\"Nini shida, Fifi alimuuliza Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe what is happening. Say: “The girl made a good plan. After searching on her own, she went to ask her mother for help. Remember that you can always ask for help if you need it.”"
msgstr "Eleza kinachoendelea. Sema: \"Msichana alifanya mpango mzuri. Baada ya kutafuta yeye mwenyewe, alikwenda kumuomba mama yake msaada. Kumbuka kwamba muda wowote unaweza kuomba msaada ukiuhitaji.\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teddy is missing!"
msgstr "Teddy haonekani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Poor girl, she is crying because she can’t find her teddy. Do you remember yesterday when you were crying because you were frustrated with your little sister? What helped you to feel less frustrated?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Maskini msichana, analia kwa sababu hampati mdoli wake. Je, unakumbuka jana ulipokuwa ukilia kwa sababu ulichanganyikiwa na mdogo wako wa kike? Ni nini kilikusaidia kupunguza kuchanganyikiwa?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“No, darling. Teddy just had a bath!”"
msgstr "\"Hapana. Teddy ametoka kuoga\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Jippy! Look, there is teddy! Why do you think teddy is hanging on the washing line?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Jippy! Tazama, kuna mdoli! Unafikiri kwa nini mdoli ananing'inia kwenye kamba ya kuanikia nguo?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“There you are, Teddy!”"
msgstr "\"Upo, Teddy!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Why is the girl smiling and jumping up and down? What has made you feel this happy lately? Do you remember feeling happy when you scored a goal when we were playing soccer together?”"
msgstr "Muulize: Kwanini Binti anatabasamu na kuruka ruka? Nini kimekufanya ujisikie furaha baadaye? Unaikumbuka ile hali ya furaha uliyojiskia ulipofunga goli wakati tunacheza mpira pamoja?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Now tell me, what did you think about this story? What did you learn?”"
msgstr "Muulize: Sasa niambie, ulifikiria nini kuhusu hadithi hii? Ulijifunza nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Boiled, scrambled or fried? How does Luzuko want his eggs?"
msgstr "Yamechemshwa. yamevurugwa wakati wa kukaanga yamekuwa vipande vipande, Ni Vipi Luzuko anataka mayai yake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Good morning, Luzuko!"
msgstr "Habari za asubuhi, Luzuko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s time for breakfast."
msgstr "Ni muda wa kifungua kinywa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you want your eggs?"
msgstr "Unataka mayai yako yaweje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do you want boiled eggs, Luzuko?"
msgstr "Unataka mayai ya kuchemshwa Luzuko?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I like boiled eggs, but ..."
msgstr "Napenda mayai ya kuchemshwa, lakini..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do you want scrambled eggs, Luzuko?"
msgstr "Unataka mayai ya kukaangwa yaliyovurugwa, Luzuko?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I like scrambled eggs, but ..."
msgstr "Napenda mayai yaliyokaangwa yaliyovurugwa, lakini..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do you want fried eggs, Luzuko?"
msgstr "Unataka mayai ya kukaangwa, Luzuko?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I like fried eggs, but ..."
msgstr "Napenda mayai ya kukaangwa, lakini ..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well? How do you want your eggs, Luzuko?"
msgstr "Vizuri? Unataka mayai yako yaweje, Luzuko?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today, I just want a bowl of porridge."
msgstr "Leo! Nataka tu bakuli la uji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lebo and Gogo's Tea Party"
msgstr "Tafrija ya Lebo na Bibi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lebo is excited to have a day of adventure with Gogo. When Gogo hurts herself, she can’t do anything that Lebo wants to do. What can Gogo and Lebo do to have fun together?"
msgstr "Lebo amefurahi kuwa na siku ya kwenda safari ya matembezi na bibi. Bibi alipojiumiza, hawezi kufanya chochote kila ambacho Lebo anataka kufanya. Bibi na Lebo wanaweza kufanya ili kufurahi pamoja?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lebo is at Gogo’s farm. She is bored with chasing the animals. \"Now you chase me, Gogo!\" Lebo shouts as she races past. \"Slow down, Lebo,\" Gogo says, hurrying to catch up."
msgstr "Lebo yupo shambani kwa bibi. Amechoshwa na kukimbiza wanyama.\"Sasa nikimbize mimi, Bibi!\" Lebo alisema kwa sauti huku akipita mbio. \"polepole, Lebo,\" Bibi anasema, unaharakisha kumkamata."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture by pointing at the different images and say, “Look at this! Who do we see here? It’s a little girl and her grandma. Do you think they might be at a farm? What do you think they are doing?”"
msgstr "Elezea picha kwa kuonyesha ukilekezea picha mbalimbali na sema,: \" Tazama hii! Tunaona nini hapa? Ni msichana mdogo na bibi yake. Unafikiri watakuwa shambani? Unafiriki wanafanya nini?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gogo trips over a rock while chasing Lebo. \"Ouch!\" she screams. Gogo has hurt her ankle."
msgstr "Bibi anapita kwenye muamba huku akimkimbiza Lebo. \"Ouch\" alipiga kelele. Bibi ameumia kwenye kiwiko cha mguu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Oh no! It looks like grandma might trip. She’s about to fall. I hope she will be okay.”"
msgstr "Sema, \" Oh hapana! Inaonekana bibi anaweza kujikwaa. Anakaribia kuanguka. Natumaini atakuwa sawa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She comes back from the doctor with a special boot and crutches. \"Gogo, come back to the city with us so that we can take care of you,\" says Lebo’s mom. \"I won’t leave my farm. I will manage on my own,\" Gogo replies, stubbornly."
msgstr "Amerudi kutoka kwa daktari akiwa na buti na gongo maalumu. \"Bibi, rudi na sisi jijini ini tuweze kukuangalia,\" anasema mama yake Lebo. \"Sitaliacha\" shamba langu. Nitaweza kujiangalia mimi mwenyewe,\" Bibi alijibu, kwa ukali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Help the child to learn new words by pointing at the picture and naming the things you see. Say, “This is a special boot” and “These are crutches.” Then explain: “The doctor gave these to grandma because her leg is hurt.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How do you think grandma feels? What makes you say that?”"
msgstr "Msaidie mtoto kujifunza maneno mapya kwa kuonyesha kwenye picha na kutaja majina ya vitu unavyoviona. Sema, \"Hili ni buti maalum\" na * Haya ni magongo.\" Halafu elezea: \"Daktari alimpa haya bibi kwasababu mguu wake umeumia?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Gogo, you must come. We will have so much fun!\" Lebo says, excitedly."
msgstr "\"Bibi, ni lazima uje, tutakuwa na vingi vya kufurahisha!\" Lebo anasema, kwa furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, the girl is giving her grandma a hug, how kind! Would you like to give me a hug too?” (When the child hugs you, respond warmly with) “Mmm, that feels so nice. Thank you for the lovely hug!”"
msgstr "Sema, \"Tazama, msichana anamkumbatia bibi yake, ni mwema kweli! Ungependa kunikumbatia pia?\" (Mtoto anapokukumbatia, pokea kwa uchangamfu) \"Mmm, najiskia vizuri sana. Asante kwa kunikumbatia kwa upendo\"!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "During the drive, Lebo bounces on her seat. She thinks of all the wild adventures she and Gogo will have in the city."
msgstr "Wakati gari inaendeshwa, Lebo alirukaruka kwenye siti. Anafikiria mambo yote mazuri ambayo yeye na bibi watakuwa nayo jijini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Now, let’s look and talk together!” Point to the picture and ask your child, “How many houses can you see? How many cars are there? How many animals can you find? What color is the car? What color are the roofs of the houses? Can you tell me the color that both animals have?"
msgstr "Sema, \"Sasa, hebu tuangalie na tuzungumze pamoja!\" Onyesha kwenye picha na muulize mtoto wako, \"Unaweza kuona nyumba ngapi?\" Kuna magari mangapi pale? Ni wanyama wangapi unaweza kupata? Gari hilo ni la rangi gani? Paa za nyumba ni za rangi gani? Unaweza kuniambia rangi za hao wanyama wote?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When they arrive at the house, Gogo rests on the sofa."
msgstr "Walipofika kwenye nyumba, Bibi alipumzika kwenye sofa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Help your child learn new words by pointing to things in the picture and saying their names. Ask your child to repeat after you. For example, you can say: ‘This is a lamp. These are crochet hooks. This is wool. This is a remote control.”"
msgstr "Msaidie mtoto wako kujifunza maneno mapya ukionyesha kwa kuelekezea vitu kwenye picha na kutaja majina yake. Muombe mtoto wako arudie baada yako. Kwa mfano, unaweza kusema: ‘Hii ni taa. Hizi ni sindano za kufumia. Hii ni pamba. Hii ni rimoti.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lebo dashes into the lounge. \"Gogo, Gogo, I know what we can do today! We can go to the mall. There are lots of shops with nice toys and ice cream!\" \"I’m afraid I can’t. The mall is too big, and I will get so tired.\""
msgstr "Lebo anaingia kwenye chumba cha kupumzika. \"Bibi, bibi, najua tunawezafanya nini leo! Tunaweza kwenda kwenye jengo kubwa la kuuza vitu. Kuna maduka mengi yenye vitu vizuri vya kuchezea na ashklim!\" \"Naogopa siwezi. Jengo hilo ni kubwa sana, na nitachoka sana.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “look at the thought bubble above the girl’s head, could she be thinking of going to the shopping mall” \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Have you ever been to the shopping mall?” If yes, “how was it? What did you do? Who did you go with?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"tazama kwenye ishara ya mawazo juu ya kichwa cha msichana;, anaweza kuwa anafikiria kwenda kwenye maduka makubwa\" \n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Je, umewahi kwenda kwenye maduka makubwa?\" Kama ndiyo, \"ilikuwaje? Ulifanya nini? Ulienda na nani?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Gogo, Gogo, I know what we can do today! We can go to the park!\" \"I’m afraid that won’t work. The dogs in the park will run around and could make me fall again.\""
msgstr "\"Bibi, Bibi, Najua tunawezafanya nini leo! Tunaweza kwenda sehemu ya michezo!\" \"Naogopa haitasaidia. Mbwa wa pale watanikimbiza na nitaweza kuanguka tena.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the thought bubble above the girl's head and say, “Now, let's look into the girl’s thought bubble again, what do you think she is thinking?"
msgstr "Onyesha kwa kuelekezea kwenye ishara ya kuwaza iliyo juu ya kichwa cha msichana na sema, “Sasa hebu tuangalie tena kwenye ishara ya mawazo ya msichana, unafikiri anawaza nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A second later, Lebo’s eyes are wide with excitement. \"Gogo, Gogo, I know what else we can do today. Let’s go to the beach.\" \"I’m sorry, Lebo. I’m afraid my crutches will sink into the soft sand.\""
msgstr "Sekunde moja baadae, Macho ya lebo yalitanuka kwa furaha. \"Bibi, bibi, Najua nini kingine tunawezafanya leo. Twende ufukweni.\" \"Samahani Lebo, Ninaogopa magongo yangu yatazama kwenye mchanga.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the thought bubble again and say, “Wow, the girl is now thinking of something else, i wonder what could be going on in her mind.”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha tena kwa kuelekezea kwenye ishara ya lindi la mawazo na sema, “Waooo, msichana anafikiria kitu kingine, sijui nini kitakuwa kinaendelea akilini mwake.”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lebo is quiet while Gogo knits. Suddenly she has an idea!"
msgstr "Lebo amekaa kimya wakati Gogo anafunga. Mara alikuwa na wazo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point to the girl and say: \"Look at her, she looks like she’s really thinking about something.\"Then ask the child: \"Can you show me what you look like when you're thinking really hard?\""
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwa msichana na usema, “Mtazame, anaonekana anafikiri kweli kuhusu kitu flani.” Halafu muulize mtoto: Unaweza kunionyesha unaonekanaje wakati unapokuwa unafikiria sana?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Gogo, Gogo, I know what we can do today! Let’s have a tea party. Gogo, you can sit here. I will bring everything to you because you are hurt.\""
msgstr "\"Bibi, Bibi, Najua nini tunawezafanya leo! Na tufanye tafrija ya chai. Bibi, unawezakaa hapa. Nitakuletea kila kitu kwasababu umeumia\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look! Maybe the girl is thinking about having a tea party. She brought many cups and a kettle, even though it's just her and grandma. Can you see her face? She looks very, very happy!”\n"
"Then say, “This is how I look when I’m happy. Now, can you show me your happy face?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! labda msichana anafikiria kuhusu kufanya tafrija ya chai. Alileta vikombe vingi na birika, Ingawa wapo yeye tu na bibi. Unaweza kuona uso wake? Anaonekana anafuraha sana sana.!”\n"
"Halafu sema, “Hivi ndivyo ninavyoonekana ninapokuwa na furaha. Sasa, unaweza kunionyesha uso wako wa furaha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Finally, everyone is having a tea party! Even Teddy is joining in with tea and biscuits. How fun is that?\"\n"
"Then ask: \"How do you think everyone feels?\" \"What do you think about the story? Did you like it? Why or why not?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Hatimaye, kila mmoja amefanya tafrija ya chai! Hata mdoli anajumuika kwenye chai na biskuti. Ni furaha iliyoje?”\n"
"Alafu muulize, “Unafikiri kila mmoja anajiskiaje?” ”Unafikiri nini kuhusu hii hadithi? Umeipenda? Kwanini umeipenda au kwanini hujaipenda?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lesedi’s Sandbox"
msgstr "Lesedi na kisanduku cha mchanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lesedi dreams of going to the beach. He wants to feel the sand between his toes and build a sandcastle. So his parents come up with a plan…"
msgstr "Lesedi aliota ndoto ya kwenda ufukweni. Anataka kushika mchanga kupata hisia kuhusu mchanga katikati ya vidole vyake na kujenga ngome ya mchanga. Hivyo wazazi wake walikuja na mpango…"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s the holidays and I’d love to go to the beach, but we have never been. I wonder what it feels like to play in the sea sand."
msgstr "Ni wakati wa likizo na ningependa kwenda ufukweni ila hatujawahi kwenda. Nawaza itakuwaje tukichezea mchanga wa bahari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe what you see, or ask your child to tell you what they see. Ask: where do you think this boy wants to go?"
msgstr "Elezea unachokiona au muulize mtoto wako akwambie anaona nini. Uliza: unafikiri huyu mvulana anataka kwenda wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Surprise! \"Look what we made you. A sandbox,\" exclaims Lesedi’s dad. Dad says he used some of his old tyres. Mom painted them with all my favourite colours: blue, red and yellow."
msgstr "Kwa mshangao! \"Angalia tulichokutengenezea. Kisanduku cha mchanga!\" Baba anasema alitumia magurudumu yake ya zamani, Mama akapaka rangi ninazozipenda, blue, nyekundu na njano."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point to boy and ask: “How do you think he is feeling? What do you think he is going to do next?”"
msgstr "Mnyooshee kidole mvulana na umuulize: Unafikiri anajiskiaje? Unafikiri anaenda kufanya nini baadae?’"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I can’t wait to get inside. I climb into my sandbox and my feet feel so warm and squishy."
msgstr "Nina hamu ya kuingia. Nikipanda kwenye kisanduku cha mchanga miguu yangu itahisi joto na kulowa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic actions from the pictures or story. Pretend to put your feet in the sand and wiggle your toes."
msgstr "Igiza Vitendo vya kwenye picha au hadithi. Jifanye unaweka miguu yako kwenye michanga na utikise vidole vyako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look! I’m at the beach. That looks like a good spot to spread my blanket. I set up my umbrella, but the wind blows it away."
msgstr "Angalia! Niko ufukweni. Pale panaonekana kama ni sehemu nzuri ya kutandika blanketi langu. Nimeweka mwamvuli wangu, lakini upepo unaupeperusha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic the sound of the wind and the umbrella blowing away. Demonstrate surprise and ask your child how they would feel if that happened to them."
msgstr "Iga sauti ya upepo na mwavuli unaopeperukia mbali. Onyesha mshangao na muulize mtoto wako angejiskiaje ikiwa hilo lingetokea kwake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The ocean makes a roaring sound. I run on the beach, daring the waves to catch me as I make footprints in the sand."
msgstr "Bahari ina mvumo wa kutisha. Nakimbia kwenye ufukwe, nikitishia mawimbi yanikamate, huku nikiacha alama za miguu yangu kwenye mchanga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic the sound of the ocean or the movement of the waves. Point to the footprints in the sand and explain what this is."
msgstr "Iga sauti ya bahari au mvumo wa mawimbi. Onyesha alama za nyayo za kwenye mchanga na uelezee hiki ni nini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Using my bucket and spade, I dig for shells. They come in many shapes and sizes."
msgstr "Kwa kutumia ndoo yangu na chepeo, Nachimba kupata magamba. Yanakuja katika maumbo na ukubwa mbalimbali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: How many shells can you see? What colours are they? Are they all the same shape? Which shells are big? Which shells are small?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Ni magamba mangapi unayaona? Yana rangi gani? Je yote yana maumbo sawa? Magamba yapi makubwa? Magamba yapi madogo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let me build a sandcastle. Wow, that’s huge!"
msgstr "Ngoja nitengeneze kasri ya mchanga. Jamani ni kubwa hiyo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture to your child or ask them what they see. Ask: do you like to play in the sand? Why or why not?"
msgstr "Ielezee picha kwa mtoto wako au muulize anachokiona. Muulize unapenda kucheza kwenye mchanga na kwanini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s lunchtime! Maybe I should have a strawberry jam sandwich. Mmm, my favourite."
msgstr "Ni muda wa chakula cha mchana! Labda nile mkate wenye jam ya stroberi. Mmm naipenda sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: where is he sitting? What is he eating?  What would you like to eat if you went to the beach?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako amekaa wapi? anakula nini, Je ungependa kula nini ukienda ufukweni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "For dessert, Mom brings me some chocolate ice cream."
msgstr "Kwa kiburudisho, Mama huniletea chokoleti na ashkilimu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: what is she holding in her hand? Who is she giving it to?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Ameshika nini mkononi mwake? Ni nani amempa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I lie on my blanket enjoying my ice cream and gaze at the sky turning pink."
msgstr "Nalala kwenye blanketi langu, nikiifurahia ashkilimu yangu na kuangalia paa la anga likibadilika kuwa la pinki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use descriptive words and explanations to talk about the pictures. This helps your child learn new words. The big, round orange sun. The pink and blue sky with clouds. The boy relaxing on his blanket, enjoying his delicious ice cream."
msgstr "Tumia maneno ya maelezo kuzungumzia picha. Hii inamsaidia mtoto wako kujifunza maneno mapya. Jua kubwa la duara la rangi ya chungwa Anga ya pinki na bluu yenye mawingu. Mvulana amepumzika kwenye blanketi lake, anaifurahia aishkilimu yake tamu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lesedi’s mom and dad watch him, their eyes beaming with pleasure. \"I’m so happy we could make his dream come true right here at home,\" Lesedi’s mom says."
msgstr "Baba na mama yake Lesedi wanamwangalia, macho yao yamejaa furaha. \"Nina furaha sana tunaweza kufanya ndoto zake kweli zikatimia hapa nyumbani,\" mama yake Lesedi anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about what the characters might be thinking or feeling. Ask: how does the boy feel? Why do you think he feels that way? Why are the parents smiling?"
msgstr "Zungumza kuhusu kile ambacho wahusika wanaweza kuwa wanafikiria au kujiskia. Muulize: Mvulana anajiskiaje ni kwanini anajiskia hivyo? Kwanini wazazi wanatabasamu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you, Mom and Dad. Today was the happiest day of my life!"
msgstr "Asanteni, Mama na Baba. Leo ilikuwa ni siku ya furaha kwenye maisha yangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: Is his clothes and hands dirty or clean? Why? What do you think he should do next?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Je nguo na mikono yake ni michafu au misafi? Kwanini? unafikiri anapaswa kufanya nini baadae?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: what did you think about the story? You could also pretend to have your own beach adventure with your child."
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Ulifikiria nini kuhusu hadithi hii? Unaweza kuigiza kuwa na safari yako ya ufukweni na mtoto wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover. Ask your child: What do you see? What is the woman pointing to?"
msgstr "Jadili jalada la kitabu. muulize mtoto wako: Unaona nini? Unafikiri mwanamke anaonyesha nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Little Shoots"
msgstr "Maswali ya mtoto"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Layo can’t wait to grow. But just like the bamboo seeds he and grandma plant, it might take a little longer than he wants!"
msgstr "Layo anatamani kukua. Lakini kama mbegu ya muanzi waliyopanda yeye na bibi yake, Inaweza kuchukua muda kidogo kuliko alivyotaka!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"When will I grow?\" asks Layo."
msgstr "\"Nitakua lini? anauliza Layo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what is the boy holding in his hand? What can you see in the photo?"
msgstr "Uliza: mvulana ameshika nini mkononi kwake? Unaweza kuona nini kwenye picha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I don’t know,\" replies Baba. \"Soon,\" says Mama."
msgstr "\"Sijui,\" alijibu Baba. \"Hivi punde\" anasema Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"When you are ready,\" says Grandma."
msgstr "\"Utakapokuwa tayari,\" anasema Bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: how many people are sitting down? Who is standing? What is she carrying? Where is the cat? Can you see any other animals?"
msgstr "Uliza: ni watu wangapi wamekaa chini? Nani amesimama? Kwanini analia? Paka yuko wapi? Unaweza kuona wanyama wengine?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grandma takes Layo to the farm. \"Let us plant some seeds.\""
msgstr "Bibi anaenda na Layo shambani.\"Tupande baadhi ya mbegu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where are they going? What are they looking at? How many orange animals can you see? Which birds are flying? Where is the mouse?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wanakwenda wapi? Wanaangalia nini? Unaweza kuona wanyama wangapi wenye rangi ya machungwa? Ni ndege wangapi wanaruka? Panya yuko wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "In one field they plant corn, and in another, melon."
msgstr "Kwenye eneo moja walipanda mahindi ya bisi, na kwenye lingine matikiti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What are these?\" asks Layo. \"Bamboo seeds,\" replies Grandma."
msgstr "\"Ni nini hivi?\" anauliza Layo. \"mbegu za Muanzi,\" anajibu Bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use the pictures to help your child practice counting. You can ask your child to count, or count out loud for your child. Ask: How many yellow seeds are there? How many black seeds? How many seeds does she have in her left hand? And how many seeds does she have in her right hand? How many seeds are there altogether?"
msgstr "Tumia picha kumsaidia mtoto wako ahesabu kwa vitendo. Unaweza kumwambia mtoto wako ahesabu, au hesabu kwa sauti kwaajili ya mtoto wako. Uliza: Kuna mbegu za njano ngapi pale? Kuna mbegu ngapi nyeusi? Ana mbegu ngapi kwenye mkono wake wa kushoto? Na ana mbegu ngapi kwenye mkono wake wa kulia? Kuna mbegu ngapi jumla kwa pamoja zote?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask questions to help your child understand what is happening. Ask: What is the boy looking at? What can you see outside the window?"
msgstr "Uliza maswali kumsaidia mtoto wako kufahamu nini kinatokea. Uliza: Mvulana anatazama nini? Unaweza kuona nini nje ya dirisha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"The corn and melon have grown well,\" says Grandma. \"What about the bamboo?\" asks Layo."
msgstr "\"Mahindi ya bisi na mattkiti yamekua vizuri,\" anasema Bibi. \" Vipi kuhusu Muanzi?\" anauliza Layo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"They will grow when they are ready.\""
msgstr "\"Vitakuwa vitakapokuwa tayari\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe and explain the pictures. Say: Look, the seeds they planted have grown. Some of the seeds have grown into tall corn plants. Other seeds have grown into big, round watermelons. What other plants can you see?"
msgstr "Fafanua na elezea picha. Sema: Tazama, mbegu walizopanda zimekua. Baadhi ya mbegu zimekua mimea ya mahindi marefu. Mbegu zingine zimekua matikiti maji makubwa, ya mviringo. Mimea gani mingine unaweza kuiona?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where is the boy standing? What is growing next to him? What is he looking at?"
msgstr "Uliza: Mvulana amesimama wapi? Nini kimeota karibu yake? Anatazama nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Everything grows in its own time,\" says Grandma."
msgstr "\"Kila kitu kinakua kwa wakati wake,\" anasema Bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make links between the pictures and your child’s world. Ask: What colour are their curtains? What colour curtains do we have at home? What do you see on their table? What do we have on our table?"
msgstr "Tengeneza muunganiko kati ya hizo picha na dunia ya mtoto wako. Uliza: Mapazia yao yana rangi gani? Mapazia tuliyo nayo nyumbani yana rangi gani? Unaona nini juu ya meza yao? Tuna nini kwenye meza yetu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"They have grown well,\" says Grandma."
msgstr "\"Vimekua vizuri,\"anasema Bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What are they looking at? How do you think they are feeling? Why?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wanatazama nini? Unafikiri wanajiskiaje? kwanini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe and explain the pictures. Say: Look, the three boys from the photo are now older."
msgstr "Elezea na dadavua picha. Sema: Tazama, wavulana watatu wa kwenye picha sasa ni wakubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“You have grown well.”"
msgstr "\"Umekua vizuri.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what looks different in this picture? What has changed?"
msgstr "Uliza: Nini kinaonekana tofauti katika picha hii? Nini kimebadilika?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Reflect on the story with your child. Ask: What happened in this story? What was the story about? What did you think of the story?"
msgstr "Tafakari na mtoto wako juu ya hadithi. Uliza: Nini kilitokea kwenye hadithi hii? Hadithi ilikuwa inahusu nini? Ulikuwa unafikiria nini kuhusu hadithi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look out, Luthando!"
msgstr "Angalia nje Lusajo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Luthando is very good at listening and very good at smelling, but he’s not so good at looking where he is going. He walks into puddles and bumps his head. What could be the problem?"
msgstr "Lusajo ni mzuri sana katika kusikiliza na mzuri sana katika kunusa, lakini sio mzuri wa kutazama kule anakokwenda. Anaingia kwenye madimbwi na anajigonga kichwa chake. Tatizo linaweza kuwa ni nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Listen!\" says Luthando. \"What do you hear?\" asks Sonto. \"Saturday.\" \"What does Saturday sound like?\" \"It’s quieter than Friday,\" says Luthando. \"Everyone’s still sleeping.\""
msgstr "\"Sikiliza\" anasema Lusajo. \"Unasikia nini?\" anauliza Saidi. \"Jumamosi\" \"Jumamosi inasikika kama nini?\" \"Iko kimya kuliko ijumaa,\" anasema Lusajo. \" Kila mmoja amelala\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I must fix Gogo’s gate today,\" Daddy says."
msgstr "\"Ni lazima nitengeneze geti la Bibi leo,\" Baba anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"An ice cream for anyone who helps me carry the shopping home,\" Mama says. \"We’ll help you, Mama,\" say the children."
msgstr "\"Nitampa asklimu yeyote atakayenisaidia kubeba vitu nyumbani kutoka dukani,\"anasema Mama. \"Tutakusaidia, Mama,\" wanasema watoto."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look out, Luthando!\" \"Hawu!\" \"You’re so funny,\" Sonto laughs."
msgstr "\"Tazama nje, Lusajo!\" \" Hawu!\": Unachekesha sana,\" Saidi anacheka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I hear a motorbike,\" says Luthando."
msgstr "\"Nasikia pikipiki,\" anasema Lusajo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"There’s no motorbike,\" says Sonto, looking all around."
msgstr "\"Hakuna pikipiki,\" anasema Saidi, akiangalia kila mahali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A motorbike zooms past. \"You’re very good at hearing, Luthando.\""
msgstr "Pikipiki imepita,''Una uwezo mkubwa wa kusikia, Lusajo''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look out, Luthando!\" \"Hawu!\" says Luthando as he steps into a puddle."
msgstr "\"Tazama nje, Lusajo\" \"Hawu!\" anasema Lusajo kadili anavyokanyaga dimbwi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look how wet you are,\" says Mama."
msgstr "\"Tazama ulivyolowa,\" anasema Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Daddy’s home.\" \"How do you know, Luthando?\" asks Sonto."
msgstr "\"Baba yupo nyumbani.\" \"Umejuaje, Lusajo?\" anauliza Saidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I can smell his cooking,\" says Luthando sniffing the air. \"You’re also good at smelling,\" Mama says."
msgstr "\"Nawezajua harufu ya mapishi yake,\" anasema Lusajo akinusa hewa. \" Wewe ni mzuri wa kutambua harufu,\" anasema Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look out, Luthando!\" \"Ouch!\" \"Watch where you’re walking,\" Mama says. \"Luthando’s not so good at looking,\" says Sonto."
msgstr "\"Tazama nje, Lusajo\" \"Angalia unapotembea,\" Mama anasema. \"Lusajo si mzuri sana, katika kuangalia\" anasema Saidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What do you see, Luthando?\" asks the friendly woman. Luthando squeezes his eyes together. He sees black squiggles on the wall."
msgstr "\"Unaona nini, Lusajo?\" Rafiki yake mama anauliza. Lusajo anafinya macho yake pamoja. Anaona michoro ya rangi nyeusi ukutani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He looks through a pair of glasses. \"I see letters,\" he says. \"Excellent!\""
msgstr "Alitazama kupitia jozi ya miwani. \" Naona herufi,\" anasema. \"Safi sana\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look, Gogo!\" \"You have glasses,\" says Gogo, clapping her hands. \"How wonderful. Tell me what you see.\""
msgstr "''Angalia, Bibi!'' Una miwani,''anasema Bibi, anapiga makofi.'' Ni vizuri sana. Niambie unaona nini.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I see bugs and ants and spiders and bees. I see EVERYTHING now.\""
msgstr "'' Ninaona Mende na Mchwa na buibui na Nyuki. Ninaona kila kitu sasa.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Gogo, your face has cracks,\" says Luthando, touching Gogo’s face. \"Hayi...Luthando! Those aren’t cracks. They’re lines on my face from getting old and laughing at all the funny things you say.\""
msgstr "''Bibi, uso wako una nyufa,'' anasema Lusajo, anashika uso wa bibi. ''Hayi...Lusajo! Hizo sio nyufa. Ni mistari usoni mwangu inayotokana na kuzeeka na vyote vya kuchekesha ulivyosema.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Don’t...\""
msgstr "''Hapana'...''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Look, a puddle!\" says Luthando. Too late!"
msgstr "''Angalia, dimbwi!'' anasema lusajo. Umechelewa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My inside weather"
msgstr "Hali ya hewa ndani yangu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes our feelings are hard to talk about, but everyone knows how to talk about the weather."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine ni ngumu kuzungumza kuhusu hisia zetu, lakini mmoja anajua kuzungumza kuhusu hali ya hewa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s easy to talk about the weather outside, even if it changes all the time."
msgstr "Ni rahisi kuzungumzia hali ya hewa ya nje hata kama hubadilika muda wowote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture and say, “Look up! The sun is out and the sky is mostly blue, with just a few fluffy grey things floating around. That means it's going to be a super fun day to play outside!”"
msgstr "Elezea picha na useme, “Tazama juu? Jua limetoka na anga ina rangi ya bluu sana, kukiwa na vitu vichache vyenye rangi ya kijivu vinavyoelea. Hiyo inamaanisha itakuwa ni siku ya kufurahisha sana kucheza nje.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But it’s hard to talk about the weather inside me. Sometimes it feels like people don’t understand."
msgstr "Lakini ni vigumu kuzungumzia hali ya hewa ya ndani mwangu. Wakati mwingine inahisiwa kama watu hawaelewi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the thought bubbles around the girl and say, “Look at this girl, could she be thinking about the weather? \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Point at the thought that shows rain, point at the one that shows cloudy weather and point at the one that shows sunny weather. Now tell me, which one is your favourite? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kwa msichana kwa kuelekezea kwenye alama inayoonyesha kufikiria jambo na useme, “Tazama huyu msichana, anaweza kuwa anafikiria hali ya hewa?\n"
"\n"
"Mwambie, “Onyesha kwa kuelekezea kwenye ishara ya mawazo yanayoonyesha hali ya hewa ya wingu na onyesha kwa kuelekeza ile inayoonyesha hali ya jua. Sasa niambie ni lipi unalolipenda zaidi? Kama ndio kwa nini na kama siyo kwanini?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do you feel like that too?"
msgstr "Na wewe unahisi hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Now look at the mother and the girl having a conversation, maybe they are discussing the weather.”"
msgstr "Sema,” Sasa mwangalie mama na msichana wanazungumza. Labda wanazungumza kuhusu hali ya hewa.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Some days my mind is full of sunshine and rainbows. I feel like I can do anything."
msgstr "Siku nyingine jua na upinde vina nikaa sana akilini. Najihisi kama naweza kufanya jambo lolote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, “Let’s have a look at the girl’s thought bubble again.’\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “What are the two things in her thought bubble that she is maybe thinking about? What colors are they?”"
msgstr ""
"Elekezea kwenye picha na useme, “Hembu tuangalie tena anachofikiria msichana.’\n"
"\n"
"Muulize. Ni vitu gani viwili vilivyo kwenye mawazo yake ambavyo anaweza akawa anafikiria? Vina rangi gani?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On other days my head is full of fog and clouds. It’s hard to listen to what people are saying or to remember things."
msgstr "Siku zingine kichwa kinawaza ukungu na mawingu. Inakuna vigumu kusikiliza kipi watu wanasema au kukumbuka vitu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the girl and say, “Let's look at the girl again, It looks like she is now thinking about the clouds.”"
msgstr "Onyesha kwa kuelekezea kwa msichana na useme, “Hebu tumtazame msichana huyo tena, Inaonekana kana kwamba sasa anafikiria juu ya mawingu.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I sometimes wake up feeling like it’s windy and wild in my head. I feel tired and grumpy."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine naamka nikihisi kama kuna upepo na dhoruba kichwani mwangu. Najihisi kama kichwa kimejaa na kina uchovu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oh no! She seems really frustrated. Perhaps the weather is really confusing her.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Now tell me, how do you act when you are frustrated or confused.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"La hapana! Anaonekana kuchanganyikiwa sana. Labda hali ya hewa inamchanganya sana.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Sasa niambie, unafanyaje wakati umekata tamaa au kuchanganyikiwa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And sometimes it feels like it’s raining inside me. It can be a drizzle making me feel sad, or a storm making me feel angry."
msgstr "Na wakati mwingine nahisi kama kunyeshewa ndani mwangu. Inaweza kuwa manyunyu yanayonifanya nijihisi kuwa na huzuni au dhoruba inayonifanya niwe na hasira."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Help the child learn new words by pointing and naming different things and say, “Let's learn new words! See this light rain? We call it \"drizzling.\" Can you say \"drizzling\"? Now, look at that big, loud rain with thunder and lightning! That's a \"storm.\" Can you say \"storm\"? Drizzling is soft rain, and a storm is big and loud rain!"
msgstr ""
"Msaidie mtoto kujifunza maneno mapya kwa kuonyesha ukielekezea na kutaja vitu mbalimbali na kusema, \"Hebu tujifunze maneno mapya! Ona mvua hii nyepesi? Tunaiita \"manyunyu.\" Je, unaweza kusema \"manyunyu\"? Sasa, angalia mvua hiyo kubwa, kubwa yenye ngurumo na radi! Hiyo ni \"dhoruba.\" Je, unaweza kusema \"dhoruba\"? Manyunyu ni mvua za rasharasha, na radi kubwa ni mvua kubwa!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes the weather inside me doesn’t match the weather outside."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine hali ya hewa ndani mwangu hailingani na hali ya hewa ya nje."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and say, “Let's look at the dress the girl is wearing, what color is the dress? What color are the dots on the dress? How many dots on the dress can you see?"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, “Hebu angalia nguo aliyovaa msichana, nguo hiyo ni ya rangi gani, doti za  kwenye vazi ni za rangi gani, unaweza kuona doti ngapi kwenye nguo hiyo?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes my inside weather doesn’t match how I want to feel or how I think I should feel."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine hali ya hewa ya ndani hailingani na namna ninavyotaka au ninavyofikiria ingekuwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and ask again, “Let's peek outside! What do you see? Look at the big, bright sun! What color is it? Now, count the pretty flowers outside. One, two, three... How many flowers are there? What colors are the flowers? Are they yellow? Maybe some purple? And what about the green stuff all over the ground? That's the grass! What color is the grass?”"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na umuulize tena, \"Hebu tuchunguze nje! Unaona nini? Angalia jua kubwa, linang’aa! Ni rangi gani? Sasa, hesabu maua mazuri nje. Moja, mbili, tatu... Kuna maua mangapi? Maua ni ya rangi gani? Je, ni ya njano? Labda ni rangi ya zambarau? Na vipi kuhusu vitu vya kijani vilivyo juu ya ardhi? Hizo ni nyasi! Nyasi ni rangi gani?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Is that okay? Yes, of course it is."
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa? Ndiyo, ni sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look at the mother and the girl looking at each other as they engage in a conversation.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Now tell me, how many eyes does the girl and the mother have? `how many eyes do you have? How many hands does the mother have? How many hands do you have?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama mama na msichana wakitazamana wanapozungumza.”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Sasa niambie, msichana na mama wana macho mangapi? una macho mangapi? Mama ana mikono mingapi? Una mikono mingapi?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The best thing to do when we feel like our inside weather is strange is to tell someone we love, and talk about it."
msgstr "Kitu sahihi cha kufanya tunapohisi kama hali ya hewa ya ndani ni ngeni, nikumwambia mtu unayempenda na kulijadili."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the couch and say, “Okay, now let's count legs! First, look at this couch. Count how many legs it has. One, two, maybe more? How many? Now, let's count your legs! How many legs do you have? Are the number of legs the same on the couch and on you?"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye kochi na useme, \"Sawa, sasa tuhesabu miguu! Kwanza, tazama hili kochi. Hesabu lina miguu mingapi. Moja, miwili, labda na zaidi? Ngapi? Sasa hebu hesabu miguu yako! Una miguu mingapi? Je, idadi ya miguu ni sawa na ya kwenye kochi na ya kwako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They’ve got inside weather too, and they’ll understand."
msgstr "Nao pia wanapata hali ya hewa, wataelewa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “What are your thoughts about this story? Do you like it? Why or why not?"
msgstr ""
"Muulize. “Una mawazo gani kuhusu hadithi hii? Umeipenda? Kama umeipenda kwanini na kama hujaipenda kwanini?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bring your child’s attention to the book’s cover. Ask: What are they doing? What do you think this story could be about?"
msgstr "Fanya mtoto wako awe makini kwenye jalada la kitabu. Uliza: wanafanya nini? Je unafikiri hadithi hii inahusu nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The Things That Really Matter"
msgstr "Vitu ambavyo ni muhimu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What are the most important things to take with you on a trip? Join Zuki, Tando, Mama and Papa on their eventful journey to find out."
msgstr "Ni vitu gani muhimu zaidi kubeba safarini? Ungana na Zuki, Thando, Mama na Baba kwenye safari yao kujua ni nini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We are going on a trip. I ask Mama what to pack. She says, \"The things that really matter.\""
msgstr "Tunakwenda safarini. Namuuliza mama nini nifungashe. Mama anasema, \"Vitu ambavyo ni muhimu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe what you see, or ask your child to tell you what they see. Ask: what are they doing? Where do you think they could be going?"
msgstr "Elezea unachokiona, au muulize mtoto wako akwambie anachokiona. Uliza wanafanya nini? Unafikiri wanaweza kuwa wanaenda wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We stop at the windmill for breakfast. The jungle gym is so much fun. I forget my toy."
msgstr "Tulisimama kwa ajili ya kifungua kinywa kwenye kinu cha upepo. Mazoezi ya msituni ni mazuri. Nilisahau mdori wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss what the characters are doing. Ask: what are the children doing? Who is waving? Why are they waving?"
msgstr "Jadili kile wanachofanya wahusika. Uliza: watoto wanafanya nini? nani anapunga mkono? Kwanini wamekaa wanapunga mkono?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sad in the car, but Tando is happy. \"Hooray! Now you can play with me!\" he says."
msgstr "Nina huzuni ndani ya gari, lakini Tando anafuraha. Alisema \"Huree! Unaweza kucheza na mimi sasa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use descriptive words to talk about the pictures. Say: Look, they are wearing their seatbelts because they are in the car. Why do you think they are wearing seatbelts?"
msgstr "Tumia maelezo ya maneno kuzungumza kuhusu picha. Sema: Tazama, amefunga mkanda sababu wako ndani ya gari. Unafikiri kwanini wamejifunga mikanda?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We stop at a farm to see some animals. Tando is searching so hard for a springbok, a monkey gets away with his headphones."
msgstr "Tulisimama kwenye shamba la ufugaji kuona baadhi ya wanyama. Tando anatafuta kwa juhudi ili amuone Paa, nyani aliondoka na spika za masikioni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child to count the animals, or count them for your child. Ask questions to help your child understand what is happening. Ask: what is the monkey doing? Does the boy know what is happening?"
msgstr "Mwambie mtoto wako ahesabu wanyama au mhesabie mtoto wako. Uliza maswali ili kumsaidia mtoto wako kuelewa kinachotokea. Uliza: Ngedere anafanya nini? Mvulana anajua kinachoendelea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He is sad in the car, but I am happy. \"Hooray! Now you can sing with me!\" I say."
msgstr "Anahuzuni kwenye gari, lakini mimi nina furaha. \"Huree! Nasema sasa unaweza kuimba na mimi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about what the characters might be thinking or feeling. Ask: how does the boy feel? Why do you think he feels that way?"
msgstr "Zungumza kuhusu nini wahusika wanaweza kuwa wanafikiria au kujiskia. Uliza: Huyu mvulana anajiskiaje? Kwanini unafikiri anajiskia hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We stop at a roaring waterfall. We are so excited, we are pushing and pulling."
msgstr "Tulisimama sehemu ya maporomoko ya maji. Tunafuraha sana, tunavuta na kuvutwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Papa falls in the water, and so does his map."
msgstr "Baba alianguka kwenye maji, na ramani yake pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what are they looking at? Say: oh no! Someone fell over! You can mimic the actions, like taking a picture, or falling down."
msgstr "Uliza: Wanaangalia nini? Sema: Oh hapana! Mtu alianguka! Unaweza kuiga vitendo, kama vile kupiga picha, au kuanguka chini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He is sad in the car, but Mama is happy. \"Hooray! Now I can help you find our way!\" she says."
msgstr "Ana huzuni ndani gari, lakini mama anafuraha, \"Huree! Sasa naweza kukusaidia kupata ufumbuzi,\" mama anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: how does the father feel? Why do you think he feels that way? Why is he wet?"
msgstr "Uliza: Baba anajiskiaje? Kwanini unafikiri anajiskia hivyo? Kwanini ameloana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We stop at the roadside vendor to buy some mielies."
msgstr "Tulisimama kwa mchuuzi pembezoni mwa barabara kununua mahindi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama bends over to pick the best ones, and her glasses fall and  break."
msgstr "Mama aliinama kuchagua yaliyo bora na miwani yake ikadondoka na kuvunjika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Why did they get out of the car? What is the man in the hat selling? What happened to the women’s glasses? Why did that happen?"
msgstr "Uliza: Kwanini walitoka nje ya gari? Mwanaume aliyevaa kofia anauza nini? Nini kimetokea kwenye miwani ya huyo mama? Kwanini ilitokea vile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama is sad in the car, but Papa is happy. \"Hooray! Now we can find our way together!\" Papa says."
msgstr "Mama ana huzuni kwenye gari, lakini baba anafuraha. Baba alisema, \"Huree! Sasa tunaweza kutafuta ufumbuzi kwa pamoja.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: how many people are in the car? How many are sitting at the front? And how many are sitting at the back?"
msgstr "Uliza: Ni watu wangapi wako kwenye gari? Ni wangapi wamekaa mbele? Na wangapi wamekaa nyuma?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We stop on an ancient hill to get a view of the valley. Papa is making silly jokes for us to smile for the picture, but..."
msgstr "Tulisimama kwenye kilima kizuri kupata mandhari ya bonde. Baba anafanya utani ili tutabasamu kwa ajili ya kupiga picha lakini..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help your child understand, explain what is happening. Say: Look, there is smoke coming out of the car. Do you think there might be something wrong with the car?"
msgstr "Ili kumsaidia mtoto wako kuelewa, eleza kinachotokea. Sema: Tazama. Kuna moshi unatokea kwenye gari: Je unafikiri kunaweza kuwa na tatizo kwenye gari?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When we get back to the car, it won’t start. Everyone stops laughing. \"Don’t worry...\" says Mama. \"We can still have a good time. We are the things that really matter.\""
msgstr "Tutakaporudi kwenye gari, halitawaka. kila mmoja anaacha kucheka. ''Usijali....'' anasema Mama. ''Bado tunaweza kuwa na wakati mzuri. Sisi ndio muhimu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Demonstrate the emotions from the story with your voice and face. Say: Look, they are all feeling sad. Why do you think they are feeling that way?"
msgstr "Onyesha hisia kutoka kwenye hadithi. hisia zionekane kwa kupitia uso na sauti: Sema: Tazama, wote wanajiskia huzuni. Unafikiri kwanini wanajiskia? hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And so, we do have a good time. By playing and singing and finding our way together, while enjoying the best mielies."
msgstr "Na hivyo, tuna muda wa kutosha. Wa kuimba na kucheza na kutafuta ufumbuzi, wakati tunafurahia mahindi matamu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where are they sitting? What are they doing? How do you think they are feeling now?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wamekaa wapi? Wanafanya nini? Unafikiri wanajiskiaje sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover. Ask your child: What do you see? Where do you think they might be going?"
msgstr "Jadili jalada la kitabu. Muulize mtoto wako: Unaona nini? Unafikiri wanaweza kuwa wanaenda wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To The Top!"
msgstr "Kileleni!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Climb the mountain with us! Look out for many tiny creatures… and BIG views. If we help each other, we can get to the top!"
msgstr "Panda mlima na sisi! Angalia nje kuna viumbe vidogo... na maoni makubwa. Kama tutasaidiana, tunaweza kufika kileleni!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the pictures, or ask your child to tell you what they see. Where are they? Where are they going? Respond with interest and enthusiasm."
msgstr "Elezea picha, au muulize mtoto wako akwambie anachokiona. Wako wapi? Wanaenda wapi? Jibu kwa kuonyesha umevutiwa na kwa shauku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe and explain the pictures. Look, here is a bird with a sharp beak and a long tail. The flowers are big and colourful. The father is holding a long stick that helps him to climb the mountain."
msgstr "Elezea picha. Tazama, huyu ni ndege ana mdomo uliochongoka na ana mkia mrefu. Maua ni makubwa na yenye rangi. Baba ameshika fimbo ndefu inayomsaidia kupanda mlima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child to point and name the animals. How many bees are flying? Where are the ants walking? Can we count them? Where is the frog hiding?"
msgstr "Mwambie mtoto wako akuonyeshe na kutaja wanyama. Ni nyuki wangapi wanaruka? Sisimizi wanaelekea wapi? Je tunaweza kuwahesabu? Je chura amejificha wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask your child: What is the father pointing at? What animal does the rock look like?\n"
"What is the girl doing?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Baba anaonesha nini? Mwamba unafanana na mnyama gani. Msichana anafanya nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: What are they doing? Why are they stopping? What can you see around them?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Wanafanya nini? Kwanini wameacha? Unaweza kuona nini karibu yao?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Discuss what the characters are doing. \n"
"Why are they sitting down? What are they eating? What would you like to eat if you were there?"
msgstr ""
"Jadili kile wahusika wanachofanya.\n"
"Kwanini wamekaa chini? Wanakula nini? Ungependa kula nini kama ungekuwa pale?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic the sound of the wind and the hat blowing away. Ask: What happened to her hat? Why did that happen?"
msgstr "Igiza sauti ya upepo na kofia ikipeperuka. Uliza: Nini kilitokea kwa kofia yake? Kwanini lilitokea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Who found the hat? How does the girl feel now that her hat has been found?"
msgstr "Uliza: Nani aliipata kofia? Msichana anajiskije sasa kofia yake imepatikana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is the girl feeling? Why is she feeling that way? What can her father do to help?"
msgstr "Uliza: Msichana anajiskia nini? Kwanini anajisikia vile? Baba yake anaweza kufanya nini kumsaidia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: Why is she sitting on her father’s shoulders? How is she feeling now?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Kwanini amekaa kwenye mabega ya baba yake? Anajisikiaje sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: Where is the frog sitting? What is the bird doing? Who is sitting at the top of the hill?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Chura amekaa wapi? Ndege anafanya nini? Nani amekaa juu ya kilima?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: why are they sitting down? What are they looking at? How would you feel after climbing such a big mountain?"
msgstr "Uliza: Kwanini wamekaa chini? Wanatazama nini? Ungejisikiaje baada ya kupanda mlima mkubwa namna hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Act out events from the book at a later stage. Go for a walk with your child and see what animals and birds you can spot as you walk. Or, collect different hats around your house and make a game out of hiding them and trying to find them."
msgstr "Igiza matukio kutoka kwenye kitabu kwa hatua za baadae. Katembee na mtoto wako na muone wanyama na ndege mnaoweza kuwaona kadili mtakavyokuwa mnatembea. Au, kusanya kofia mbalimbali karibu na nyumba yenu na mtengeneze mchezo wa kuzificha na kujaribu kuzitafuta."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where is Lulu?"
msgstr "Lulu yupo wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where is Lulu and why is she hiding?"
msgstr "Lulu yupo wapi na kwanini anajificha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh, no!\""
msgstr "\"Oh, Hapana!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Lulu! It’s time to go,\" calls Ma."
msgstr "\"Lulu! Ni wakati wakurudi Nyumbani!\" Mama anaita."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where is Lulu? Is she under the sofa? Is she behind the curtain?"
msgstr "Lulu yupo wapi? Je yupo chini ya kochi? Je yupo nyuma ya pazia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where is Lulu? Is she next to the stove? Is she in the cupboard?"
msgstr "Lulu yupo wapi? Je yupo mbele ya jiko? Je yupo ndani ya kabati?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Lulu! It’s time to go. Where are you?\" calls Ma."
msgstr "\"Lulu! Ni wakati wa kurudi nyumbani upo wapi?\" Mama anaita."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"There you are!\" \"I don’t want to gooo!\""
msgstr "\"Hapo ulipo!\" \"Sitaki kuondoka!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"We have to go,\" says Ma. \"But I really like this one!\""
msgstr "\"Tunatakiwa kuondoka,\" Mama anasema. \"Lakini kiukweli napenda hiki.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I really like this one!\""
msgstr "\"Kiukweli napenda hiki!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"And this one.\" \"And this one.\" \"And this one.\""
msgstr "\"Na hiki.\" \"Na hiki.\" \"Na hiki.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"See? You return books and borrow more.\" \"YAY!\""
msgstr "\"Ona? Umerudisha vitabu na unaazima zaidi.\" \"NDIO!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where is Lulu now?"
msgstr "Lulu yupo wapi sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ouma’s\n"
"Amazing Flowers"
msgstr "Maua mazuri ya Jane"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ouma has amazing flowers! Robyn wants to pick them all …"
msgstr "Ouma ana maua mazuri ya ajabu! Robyn anataka kuyachukua yote …"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ouma has a window box full of amazing flowers. Robyn wants to pick them all!"
msgstr "Jane ana boksi la dirishani lililojaa maua mazuri. Robby anataka kuyachukua yote!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Please don’t pick the flowers, Robyn! Ouma loves to see them when she opens her curtains."
msgstr "Tafadhali usichume maua, Robyn! Jane anapenda kuyaona anapofungua mapazia yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Butterflies dance around the petals. It’s so lovely to have these visitors."
msgstr "Vipepeo wanacheza kuzunguka maua. Inapendeza sana kuwa na wageni hawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The bees use the flowers to make delicious honey."
msgstr "Nyuki wanatumia maua kutengeneza asali tamu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The flowers bring joy to everyone who walks past Ouma’s house."
msgstr "Maua yanaleta furaha kwa kila mtu ambaye alipita nyumbani kwa Jane."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The neighbour likes to smell them when he visits for tea."
msgstr "Majirani wanapenda harufu yake anapowatembelea kwa ajili ya chai."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes, sunbirds drink the sweet nectar from the flowers."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine, ndege hunywa majimaji matamu ya kwenye ua."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look, a tiny beetle! It shines in the sun. And there’s a fat caterpillar!"
msgstr "Tazama mende mdogo, anang'aa juani, na kuna kiwavi mnene!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Please don’t pick Ouma’s flowers, Robyn! They won’t stay fresh very long."
msgstr "Tafadhari usichume maua ya Jane, Robyn! Hayatakuwa mazuri kwa muda mrefu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I won’t pick them, Ouma,\" says Robyn, even though she really wants to. She feels a little bit sad!"
msgstr "''Sintayachuma Jane,'' anasema Robyn, hata kama anataka sana. Anajisikia huzuni kidogo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ouma doesn’t want Robyn to be sad. \"Okay, Robyn,\" says Ouma. \"You can pick your favourite flower.\""
msgstr "Jane hataki Robyn awe na huzuni,''Sawa Robyn,'' anasema Jane. ''unaweza kuchuma ua unalolipenda,''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"And I have an idea ... Let’s plant more flowers together!\""
msgstr "''Nina wazo... Ngoja tupande maua pamoja!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Baby’s First Family Photo"
msgstr "Picha ya kwanza ya mtoto akiwa na familia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Baby’s family is excited about their first family photo. What will Mama, Papa, Big Sister, Baby and Gogo wear?"
msgstr "Familia ya mtoto mdogo inafurahishwa na picha yao ya kwanza ya kifamilia. Ni nini atavaa Mama, Baba, dada mkubwa, mtoto na Bibi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whose bright orange wrapper is this? It is Mama’s."
msgstr "Hiki kilemba cha rangi ya chungwa ni cha nani? Ni cha Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child questions about the pictures. Ask: What is she wearing on her head? What colour is it?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako maswali kuhusu picha. Uliza: Amevaa nini kichwani kwake? ina rangi gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whose blue shirt is this? It is Papa's."
msgstr "Hili shati la bluu ni la nani? Ni la Baba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the pictures to your child. Say: Look, he is wearing a shirt with blue patterns and a blue tie. His glasses are also blue."
msgstr "Muelezee mtoto wako picha. Sema: Tazama. amevaa shati la michoro ya bluu na tai ya bluu. Miwani yake pia ni ya bluu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whose yellow head wrap is this? It is Gogo's."
msgstr "Hiki kitambaa cha kichwani cha rangi ya njano ni cha nani? Ni cha Bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Who can you see? What is she wearing? Why do you think she is wearing glasses? Do you know someone who wears glasses?"
msgstr "Uliza: Unaweza kumuona nani? Amevaa nini? Kwanini unafikiri amevaa miwani? Unamfahamu yeyote anayevaa miwani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whose pretty red dress is this? It is Big Sister’s."
msgstr "Gauni hii nzuri nyekundu ni ya nani? Ni ya dada mkubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the pictures to help your child learn words. Say: Look, she has tied her hair with big green and red bows. The patterns on the bows are the same pattern as her dress."
msgstr "Elezea picha kumsaidia mtoto wako kujifunza maneno. Sema: Tazama, amebana nywele zake na vibanio vikubwa vya kijani na pindo nyekundu. Miundo kwenye pinde ni kama miundo kwenye gauni yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whose green and yellow flowery dress is this? It is mine!"
msgstr "Gauni hili lenye maua ya kijani na njano ni la nani? Ni langu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make links between the pictures and your child’s world. Ask: What is she wearing? What are you wearing today? What colours are your clothes today? And what colours are my clothes?"
msgstr "Tengeneza muunganiko kati ya picha na dunia ya mtoto wako. Uliza: Amevaa nini? Unavaa nini leo? Nguo zako ni za rangi gani leo? N nguo zangu ni za rangi gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I love my orange wrapper.\" Mama twirls."
msgstr "\"Nakipenda kitenge changu chenye rangi ya chungwa.\" Mama alizunguka kwa kucheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is she doing? Why do you think she is doing that?"
msgstr "Uliza: Anafanya nini? Unafikiri kwanini anafanya vile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I love my blue shirt.\" Papa bows."
msgstr "\"Nalipenda shati langu la bluu.\" Baba aliinama kwa heshima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is he doing? Let’s try to do the same move as him."
msgstr "Uliza: Anafanya nini? Hebu tujaribu kufanya vilevile kama yeye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I love my yellow head wrap.\" Gogo jiggles."
msgstr "\"Nakipenda kitambaa changu cha kichwani cha njano.\" Bibi alijizungusha kwa kucheza kwa furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use the pictures to teach your child about different shapes. Say: How many circles or round shapes can you see? What colours are they? Look, her clothes are covered in a yellow diamond pattern."
msgstr "Tumia picha kumfundisha mtoto wako maumbo tofauti. Sema: Kuna miduara mingapi au maumbo ya duara unayoweza kuona? Zile ni rangi gani? Tazama, nguo zake zimefunikwa kwenye miundo ya almasi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I love my pretty red dress.\" Big Sister jumps up and down."
msgstr "\"Nalipenda gauni langu zuri jekundu.\" Dada mkubwa aliruka juu na chini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What colours are on her dress? What colour shoes is she wearing? What is she doing?"
msgstr "Uliza: Kuna rangi gani kwenye gauni yake? Amevaa viatu vya rangi gani? Anafanya nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I love my green flowery dress.\" I clap my hands."
msgstr "\"Nalipenda gauni langu lenye maua ya kijani.\" Napiga makofi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic actions from the story, like clapping hands. Ask: why do you think she is clapping her hands? How is she feeling?"
msgstr "Igiza matendo kutoka kwenye hadithi, kama kupiga makofi, Uliza: Unafikiri kwanini anapiga makofi mikono yake? Anajisikiaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We are ready."
msgstr "Tupo tayari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SNAP!"
msgstr "Picha!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What are they going to do now? Why do you say that? How many people are there?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wanaenda kufanya nini sasa? Kwanini unasema hivyo? Kuna watu wangapi pale?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make links between the pictures and your child’s world. Do we have a family photo? Who is in it? Or, should we take a family photo later when we are all together? What do you want to do for our family photo?"
msgstr "Tengeneza kiungo kati ya picha na dunia ya mtoto wako. Tuna picha ya familia? Nani yuko humo? Tupige picha ya familia baadae tutakapokuwa sote pamoja? Unataka kufanya nini kwenye picha yetu ya familia/?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Brave Bora"
msgstr "Bora Shujaa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Going to the doctor can be scary! Can Bora overcome his fears, with a little help from Baba and Jojo?"
msgstr "Kwenda kwa daktari inaweza kuogopesha! Bora anaweza kuushinda uoga wake. kwa msaada kidogo kutoka kwa Baba na Jojo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bora is sitting at the clinic with Baba. Jojo, his stuffed monkey, came too. Jojo is sleeping in Bora’s bag."
msgstr "Bora amekaa kliniki na Baba. Ngedere wake aitwaye Jojo alikuja pia. Jojo amelala kwenye begi la Bora."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I don’t like needles. They hurt!\" says Bora."
msgstr "''Sipendi sindano. Zinaumiza!''anasema Bora."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"An injection helps make you healthy. It’s okay to be scared, Bora. Baba will be right here with you. And Jojo too.\""
msgstr "''Sindano zinasaidia kukufanya uwe na afya njema. Ni sawa kuwa na hofu, Bora. Baba atakuwa hapa pamoja na wewe. Na Jojo pia.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Bora Baraka!\" a loud voice calls. \"Let’s go Bora, \" says Baba. \"It’s your turn.\""
msgstr "'' Bora Baraka!'' kwa sauti kubwa,'' Twende Bora,''anasema Baba. ''Ni zamu yako''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Let’s come back tomorrow Baba!\" says Bora."
msgstr "''Turudi kesho Baba!''anasema Bora."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Remember what Baba said you will get for being brave enough to get your injection?\" asks Baba. \"A red  lollipop! Okay, I’m coming,\" says Bora."
msgstr "''Kumbuka baba alichosema, ukiwa jasiri ukachoma sindano? Baba anauliza. \" pipii ya kijiti nyekundu!\" Sawa, nakuja,\" Bora anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The doctor smiles at Bora. \"Is this your  monkey? Can we examine him too?\" she asks."
msgstr "Daktari alitabasamu kwa Bora. ''Huyu ni Ngedere wako? Tunaweza kumchunguza pia? anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bora looks at Baba, then at Jojo, and nods."
msgstr "Bora anamwangalia Baba, pia Jojo na kutikisa kichwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Now, it’s your turn,\" she says. \"Will you help me give your monkey a small injection so he feels better?\" asks the doctor."
msgstr "''Sasa, ni zamu yako.''anasema''Unaweza kunisaidia kumchoma Ngedere wako sindano ndogo, ili ajisikie vizuri?''anauliza daktari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"TOOP!\" says the doctor as she gives Jojo the monkey an injection."
msgstr "''TOOP!''anasema daktari wakati akimchoma sindano Jojo Ngedere."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Now, it’s your turn. Is that a superhero on your T-shirt?\" she asks."
msgstr "''Sasa,''ni zamu yako. Je huyo ni shujaa kwenye flana yako?''anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"TOOP!\" She says as she gives Bora the injection."
msgstr "''TOOP!''Anasema huku akimpatia Bora sindano."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Ouch!\" shouts Bora. \"Hey, that wasn’t so bad!\""
msgstr "''Ouch'' anapiga kelele Bora. Hey, Haikuwa mbaya sana!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I know it stings a little, but we’re done and you have been very brave!\" says the doctor."
msgstr "''Najua inauma kidogo, ila tumemaliza na umekuwa shujaa sana!''anasema daktari."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"One red lollipop for our brave Bora!\""
msgstr "''Pipi moja nyekundu ya kijiti kwa ajili ya shujaa wetu!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Also!"
msgstr "Na Pia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo’s make-believe world has no room for his little sister, Keitu. But she has other ideas!"
msgstr "Uigizaji wa Thabo unaamini kuwa dunia haina nafasi kwa dada yake mdogo, keitu, lakini ana mawazo mengine!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo pretends that his bed is a raft on the sea!"
msgstr "John anaigiza kuwa kitanda chake ni chelezo ya kwenye Bahari!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "His little sister Keitu says, \"Yes ! And also! There are sharks.\""
msgstr "Dada yake mdogo John anayeitwa Kabula , anasema \"Ndiyo! Na pia! Kuna papa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"No!\" says Thabo."
msgstr "\"Hapana\" John anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo pretends that their taxi is a spaceship!"
msgstr "John anajifanya kuwa taksi yake ni meli inayoelea angani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "His little sister Keitu says, \"Yes! And also! Watch out for shooting stars!\""
msgstr "Dada yake mdogo John anayeitwa Kabula, anasema \"Ndiyo! Na pia! Kuwa muangalifu na nyota zinazotoa risasi!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo pretends the playground is a jungle!"
msgstr "John anajifanya eneo lake la kuchezea ni msitu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "His little sister Keitu says, \"Yes! And also! We are lions.\""
msgstr "Dada yake mdogo John anayeitwa Kabula anasema \"Ndiyo! Na pia! Sisi ni simba.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"No,\" says Thabo."
msgstr "John anasema, \"Hapana!\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Oh!\" says Thabo, \"Wait! Wow! Yes! That’s a great idea!\""
msgstr "\"Oh!\" John anasema, \"Subiri! Waoo! Ndiyo! Hilo ni wazo zuri!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I know!\" says Keitu."
msgstr "\"Najua!\" Kabula anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo pretends to be a lion! Keitu also pretends to be a lion!"
msgstr "John anajifanya kuwa simba! Kabula pia anajifanya kuwa simba!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo pretends the other kids are a river of crocodiles!"
msgstr "John anajifanya kuwa watoto wengine wote mamba wa kwenye mto!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keitu says, \"Yes! And also! We can jump on this log to float away.\""
msgstr "Kabula anasema \"Ndiyo! Na pia! Tunaweza kuruka kwenye hili gogo na kuondoka kwa kuelea.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Yes! And also!\" Thabo says, \"We can slide down the rainbow!\""
msgstr "\"Ndiyo. Na pia!\" John anasema, \" Tunaweza kuteleza kwenye upinde wa mvua!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keitu says, \"Yes! And also! Watch out for the dinosaurs!\""
msgstr "Kabula anasema \"Ndiyo! Na pia! Kuwa muangalifu na Dino!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo says, \"I had the best day playing pretend with you.\""
msgstr "'John anasema, 'Nilikuwa na siku nzuri nimecheza nikiigiza niko na wewe.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keitu says, \"And also! We should play again tomorrow!\""
msgstr "Kabula anasema, \"Na pia! Kesho tucheze tena!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry Akku"
msgstr "Akku mwenye hasira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Akku is having an awful day and it’s making her very, VERY angry. Read this book to find out how Akku's anger melts away, and get ideas on what to do when YOU are very, VERY angry."
msgstr "Akku ana siku mbaya na imemkasirisha sana. Soma kitabu hiki ujue namna hasira za Akku zilivyoyeyeka na upate ushauri unavyohitaji kufanya ukiwa umekasirika"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When the last school bell rang, all the children laughed and screamed with joy. All, except Akku. Akku was ANGRY!"
msgstr "Kengele ya mwisho shuleni ilipopigwa kila mtoto alicheka na kupiga kelele kwa furaha. wote, ispokuwa Akku. Akku alikuwa amekasirika!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe and point at the children in the picture and say, “Hmmm.. It looks like all the children are happy and dancing except for this one. She looks really sad, I wonder what could be wrong.”"
msgstr ""
"Elezea na onyesha kuelekezea kwa watoto kwenye picha na useme, \"Hmmm.. Inaonekana watoto wote wana furaha na wanacheza isipokuwa huyu mmoja. Anaonekana mwenye huzuni sana, nashangaa nini kinaweza kuwa tatizo.\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Akku! Akku! Look at the pretty sunflowers!\" said Appa, as they rode through a field. \"GRRMPH! They’re TOO YELLOW! They’re making my eyes hurt!\" said Akku."
msgstr "\"Akku! Akku! Angalia yale maua ya kupendeza!\" alisema Baba, walipoendesha kupitia uwanjani. \"GRRMPH! Ni ya njano sana, yanasabisha macho yangu kuuma!\" alisema Akku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Help the child to learn new words by pointing at different items in the picture and say, “Look at this picture. I'm going to point to things, and you say the words after me, okay?”\n"
"Then say, \"These are sunflowers. Can you say 'sunflowers'? That is a bicycle. Can you say 'bicycle'? Those are palm trees. Can you say 'palm trees'? And that is a huge tree trunk. Can you say 'tree trunk'?\""
msgstr ""
"Msaidie mtoto kujifunza maneno mapya kwa kuonyesha kuelekezea vitu tofauti kwenye picha na useme, \"Tazama picha hii. Nitaonyesha kuelekezea vitu, na wewe usema maneno baada yangu, sawa?\"\n"
"Kisha useme, \"Hizi ni alizeti. Unaweza kusema 'alizeti'? Hiyo ni baiskeli. Unaweza kusema 'baiskeli'? Hiyo ni mitende. Unaweza kusema 'mitende'? Na hilo ni shina kubwa la mti. Unaweza kusema 'shina la mti'?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Akku! Akku! Look! Look at all the monkeys!\" said Appa, pointing at the roof of their house. \"CHEEE!\" said Akku. \"SHOOO! Go AWAY!  SHOOO!\""
msgstr "\"Akku! Akku! Waone hawa Ngedere!\" alisema Baba huku akionesha paa la nyumba. \"CHEE!\" alisema Akku. \"Shooo! Ondoka! Shoo!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point in the picture and say, “What is that on the roof? Is that what I think it is?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Ni nini hicho juu ya paa? Je! ninavyofikiria ndio hivyo?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oooh, are those monkeys on the roof?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How many monkeys do you see? How many monkeys have tails? How many monkeys have big grey beards?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Oooh, je, hao ni nyani juu ya paa?”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unaona nyani wangapi? Ni nyani wangapi wana mikia? Ni nyani wangapi wana ndevu kubwa za kijivu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Here, drink some buttermilk,\" said Appa. \"It’ll cool you  down.\" \"HRRRM!\" said Akku. \"I DON’T WANT ANY!\" \"Try a sip, at least?\" \"OKAY! FINE!\" said Akku, and tried a sip. It wasn’t all that bad. She had another sip. And another. In no time, the glass was empty."
msgstr "\"Hapa, kunywa maziwa kidogo,\" alisema Baba. \"Itakutuliza.\" \"Sihitaji!\" \"Jaribu kuonja kidogo.\" \"Sawa basi!\" Akku alisema, na akajaribu kuonja. Haikuwa mbaya hivyo. Alionja tena. Na tena. Muda si muda, kikombe kilibaki tupu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Imagine you're this girl, and there are monkeys around! Would you feel a little bit scared? Maybe!”\n"
"Ask, “If you felt scared, what could you do to feel better? Could you take a deep breath? Maybe close your eyes for a second? Or maybe you'd want to hold someone's hand? What do you think would help you feel calm?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Fikiria wewe ni huyo msichana, na kuna nyani karibu! Je, unahisi unaweza kuogopa kidogo? Labda!\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize,\"Ikiwa ulijiskia kuwa na wasiwasi, ungefanyaje ili kujisikia vizuri? Je, unaweza kuvuta pumzi ndefu? Labda kufunga macho yako kwa sekunde moja? Au labda ungetaka kumshika mtu mkono? Unafikiri nini kingekusaidia kujisikia utulivu?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Would you like a vada?\" asked Appa. \"FFEHH!\" said Akku. \"Just one little bite?\" \"Okay, FINE!\" said Akku, and took a bite. It was quite good. She took another bite. And another. In no time, the plate was empty."
msgstr "\"Utahitaji kalimati?\" aliuliza Baba. \"Hamna!\"alisema Akku. \"Kidogo tu ya kuonja.\" \"Sawa, safi!\" alisema Akku, na akang'ata. Ilikuwa tamu kabisa. Aling'ata tena. Na tena. Muda si muda sahani lilikuwa tupu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Now look at the girl again. It looks like the father gave her something nice to eat. Perhaps to get her smile, but still, she doesn't look happy. I wonder what could have upset her.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Sasa mtazame msichana huyo tena. Inaonekana baba alimpa chakula kizuri. Labda ili kumfanya tabasamu, lakini bado, haonekani kuwa na furaha. Nashangaa ni nini kilikuwa kimemkera.\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Good girl,\" said Appa. \"Now will you tell me why you’re so angry?\" \"NO!\" said Akku. \"Was it something I did?\" \"NO!\" \"Was it something Amma did?\" \"NO!\" \"Did something bad happen in school today?\" \"MAYBE!\" \"Oho.\""
msgstr "\"Safi binti,\" alisema Baba. \"Sasa utaniambia ni nini kinakukasirisha?\" \"Hapana!\" alisema Akku. \"Kuna kitu nilifanya?\" \"Hapana!\" \"Kuna jambo Mama alikufanyia?\" \"Hapana!\" \"Kuna chochote kibaya kilichotokea shuleni leo?\" \"Labda!\" \"Naam\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “If you were this girl, and something had upset you, how would you react?”"
msgstr "Muulize, “Kama ungekuwa huyu msichana, na jambo fulani likakukera, ungefanyaje?”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Would you like to draw it?\" asked Appa. \"Here’s a nice sheet of paper and some crayons.\" \"Okay, FINE!\" said Akku."
msgstr "\"Ungependa kukichora?\" aliuliza Baba. \"Hiki hapa kipande kizuri cha karatasi.\" \"Sawa basi!\" alisema Akku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Now tell me, how many crayons do you see in this picture? How many papers do you see? What do you think the girl is going to do with the paper and crayons?"
msgstr ""
"Muulize, \"Sasa niambie, unaona kalamu ngapi kwenye picha hii? Unaona karatasi ngapi? Unafikiri msichana atazifanyia nini karatasi na kalamu za rangi?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Akku drew a brick... \"This is the STUPID BRICK that I tripped over this morning,\" said Akku. \"You’re right. That IS a VERY STUPID brick!\" said Appa."
msgstr "Akku alichora tofari... \"Hili ni lile tofali jinga lililonikwaa asubuhi,\" alisema Akku. \"Umegonga ndipo, hilo ni tofari jinga sana!\" alisema Baba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “What color is the girl using to draw on a paper? What shape is the drawing? Can you guess what he is drawing?"
msgstr "Muulize, \"Msichana anatumia rangi gani kuchora kwenye karatasi? Mchoro ni wa sura gani? unaweza kukisia anachora nini?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Akku drew a boy... \"This is Bikku, a VERY BAD BOY! He laughed when I fell down!\" said Akku. \"You’re right,\" said Appa. \"He shouldn’t have laughed at you.\""
msgstr "Akku alichora kijana... \"Huyu ni Bikku. Kijana mbaya sana! Alicheka nilipoanguka!\" alisema Akku. \"Umesema sawa sawa,\" alisema Baba. \"Hakutakiwa kukucheka.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Hmmm! there is another drawing, i wonder who this could be. Who do you think this is?"
msgstr "Sema, \"Hmmm! kuna mchoro mwingine, sijui huyu anaweza kuwa nani. Unafikiri huyu ni nani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Akku drew an idli... \"This is my idli,\" said Akku. \"It fell out of my lunch box when I tripped over the STUPID BRICK!\""
msgstr "Na Akku alichora idli... \"Hii ni Biskuti yangu.\" Akku alisema \"Ilianguka nje ya mkebe wangu wa chakula nilipotegwa na tofali na kuanguka!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and say, “That looks like something to eat. What color is it? What shape is it? How many dots are inside the drawing?”"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Hicho kinaonekana kama kitu cha kula. Ni rangi gani? Ina umbo gani? Ndani ya mchoro kuna nukta ngapi?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Akku drew a crow... \"This is the VERY BAD CROW that flew off with my idli,\" said Akku. \"The crow must have been very hungry,\" said Appa."
msgstr ""
"Na Akku akachora Kunguru... \"Huyu ni kunguru mbaya sana aliyechukua \n"
"chapati yangu,\" Akku alisema. \"Huenda kunguru alisikia njaa sana,\" Baba alisema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture making a sad sound and say, “Oh no, a bird flew away with a biscuit, what will the girl eat?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Now show me how a bird flies. Do you think you can catch it?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha inayotoa sauti ya huzuni na useme, \"La hapana, ndege aliruka na biskuti, msichana atakula nini?\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Sasa nionyeshe jinsi ndege anavyoruka. Je, unafikiri unaweza kumkamata?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Akku drew her teacher... \"This is my teacher, Amala Miss,\" said Akku. \"She helped me up when I fell down. And then she hugged me.\" \"That’s nice of her,\" said Appa \"And then she pinched my cheeks. I DON’T LIKE IT when my cheeks are pinched.\" \"Oho! That must have HURT, no?\" \"A little bit. But I’m okay now.\" \"That’s good.\""
msgstr "Na Akku alimchora mwalimu wake... \"Huyu ni mwalimu wangu, Bi. Amala,\" Akku alisema. \"Alinisaidia nilipoanguka kisha akanikumbatia.\" \"Huo ndio uzuri wake,\" alisema Baba. \"Kisha alifinyaa mashavu yangu. Sipendi kufinywa mashavu.\" \"Salale! Hio iliumiza sana, hapana?\" \"Kiasi tu. Ila niko sawa.\" \"Hiyo ni sawa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, “There is another drawing.” \n"
"\n"
"Connect what is in the book with the child’s experience by pointing at the hand in the picture and saying, “How many fingers can you see? How many fingers do you have? What color is the hand? What color is your hand?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Kuna mchoro mwingine.\" \n"
"\n"
"Unganisha kile kilicho kwenye kitabu na uzoefu wa mtoto kwa kuonyesha kuelekezea kwenye mkono kwenye picha na kusema, \"Je! unaweza kuona vidole vingapi? Una vidole vingapi? Mkono ni rangi gani? Mkono wako una rangi gani?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"See how well you draw, Akku?\" said Appa. \"You’re a real artist! Will you draw something for Amma too?\" \"OH-kay!\" said Akku, and started drawing some more. \"This is a little white mouse... and this is a boat... and this is a coconut tree...\""
msgstr "\"Angalia namna unavyochora vizuri Akku?\" Alisema Baba. \"Wewe ni msanii wa kweli! Utachora kitu cha Amma, pia?\" \"Sawa!\" Akku alisema, na akaanza kuchora zingine zaidi. \"Hii ni panya ndogo... na hii ni meli... na huu ni mnazi...\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the feet and say, “Now look at the fathers feet. How many feet does he have? How many feet do you have? How many toes does he have? How many toes do you have?"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye miguu na useme, “Sasa tazama miguu ya baba, ana miguu mingapi, ana vidole vingapi? una vidole vingapi?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"And this is a sun flower... and this is your cycle, Appa... and this is a dog... and this is a frog...\" In no time, Akku had forgotten all about the STUPID BRICK that made her trip and fall. And about the BAD BOY who laughed at her. And about the IDLI- STEALING CROW. And Akku even forgot about being ANGRY."
msgstr "''''Na hii ni alizeti.... na hii ni baiskeli yako Baba.... na huyu ni mbwa.... na huyu ni chura....''''Kwa kipindi kifupi, Akku alikuwa amesahau na lile tofali lililomuangusha. Na kuhusu yule kijana mkorofi aliyemcheka. Na kuhusu BISKUTI.... Kunguru aliyeiba. Na Akku akasahau alikuwa amekasirika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Reflect on the girl's drawings and say, “Wow, she made so many pictures.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How do you think she feels now after drawing all of them? Maybe drawing made her feel better and calmer?”\n"
"Then say, “When I feel mad, sometimes I go for a walk, or sing a little song, or read a fun book, or listen to music. These things help me feel calm again. Now it's your turn! When you feel angry, what do you do to feel calm? Tell me!”"
msgstr ""
"Tafakari juu ya michoro ya msichana huyo na useme, “Wow, alitengeneza picha nyingi sana.”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri anajisikiaje sasa baada ya kuchora zote? Labda kuchora kumemfanya ajisikie vizuri na kutulia?\"\n"
"Kisha sema, \"Ninapohisi kuchanganyikiwa, nyakati fulani naenda matembezini, au kuimba nyimbo, au kusoma kitabu cha kufurahisha, au kusikiliza muziki. Mambo haya hunisaidia kuhisi utulivu tena. Sasa ni zamu yako! Unapohisi hasira, unafanya nini ili kujisikia utulivu? Niambie!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"10 Things to Do If You Feel ANGRY like Akku:\n"
"1. Laugh loudly and jump around with your arms in the air!\n"
"2. Slowly – very, very slowly – breathe in, and breathe out!\n"
"3. Drink some water! Or buttermilk! \n"
"4. Eat a piece of fruit! Or a vada!\n"
"5. Tell a grown-up about how you’re feeling!\n"
"6. Write about how you’re feeling!\n"
"7. Draw it out! Paint it!\n"
"8. Play with a pile of clay!\n"
"9. Make up a song about your anger! Sing it aloud!\n"
"10. Dance like a monkey!"
msgstr ""
"Vitu kumi vya kufanya ukikasirika kama Akku;\n"
"1. Cheka kwa sauti na urukeruke huku mikono yako ikiwa hewani!\n"
"2. Polepole tu vuta pumzi ndani tena nje.!\n"
"3. Kunywa maji kidogo au maziwa!\n"
"4. Kula kipande cha tunda au chakula!\n"
"5. Mwambie mkubwa unavyojisikia!\n"
"6. Andika unavyojisikia!\n"
"7. Chora! paka rangi!\n"
"8. Cheza na mchanga!\n"
"9. Tunga wimbo kuhusu hasira zako na uuimbe!\n"
"10. Cheza kama Ngedere!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Can you tell me what you think about the story? Did you like it? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize, \"Je, unaweza kuniambia nini unafikiri kuhusu hadithi? Je, uliipenda? Kwanini uliipenda au kwa nini hukuipenda?\" \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Beloved Daughter"
msgstr "Binti mpendwa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Natabo has run away from her home! Do you know why?"
msgstr "Natabo amekimbia nyumbani! Unajua ni kwanini?"

