#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This is Natabo. She has six brothers."
msgstr "Huyu ni Natabo. Ana kaka sita."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her parents give her a small pot. She loves it."
msgstr "Wazazi wake walimpa chungu kidogo. Anakipenda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One day her brothers break the pot."
msgstr "Siku moja kaka zake walikivunja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Natabo cannot find her pot. She cries and cries."
msgstr "Natabo haoni chungu chake. Analia na kulia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Natabo runs away. She climbs a tall tree."
msgstr "Natabo anakimbia. Anapanda mti mrefu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her parents find her. \"Please come down,\" they ask."
msgstr "Wazazi wake wakamkuta. \"Tafadhali shuka chini,\" walimuomba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her brothers sing, \"Please come down.\""
msgstr "Kaka zake wanaimba, \"Tafadhali shuka chini\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Natabo makes fun of their song."
msgstr "Natabo anaufanyia mzaha wimbo wao."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Then Natabo's friend comes. \"Please come down,\" she sings."
msgstr "Halafu rafiki wa Natabo anakuja. \"Tafadhali njoo chini,\" anaimba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Natabo's friend sings until she comes down from the tree."
msgstr "Rafiki wa Natabo anaimba mpaka anakuja chini kutoka kwenye mti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The friends walk home together."
msgstr "Marafiki walitembea pamoja kwenda nyumbani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Everyone celebrates that Natabo is home. Natabo gets a new pot!"
msgstr "Kila mmoja anasherehekea kuwa Natabo yupo nyumbani. Natabo anapata sufuria mpya!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Big Blue Bus"
msgstr "Basi kubwa la bluu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei and his mother are waiting for the big blue bus. Where is it?"
msgstr "Ebei na Mama yake wanasubiri basi kubwa la bluu. Liko wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "There was only one bus in Ebei's village. It was big and blue. It was very noisy."
msgstr "Kulikuwa na basi moja tu katika kijiji cha Ebei. Lilikuwa basi kubwa lenye rangi ya bluu. Lilinguruma sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Describe the picture and say, “Look, there is a big blue bus. It is the only bus in this village and people love it a lot.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Have you seen a bus in your village? If yes, what color is it?"
msgstr ""
"Elezea picha na useme, \"Angalia, kuna basi kubwa la bluu. Ndiyo basi pekee katika kijiji hiki na watu wanalipenda sana.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Je, umeona basi katika kijiji chako? Kama ndiyo, ni la rangi gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Tomorrow we will go to town,\" said Ebei's mother. \"We will buy your school uniform.\""
msgstr "Siku moja mama yake Ebei alisema, \"Kesho tutaenda mjini kununua sare yako ya shule.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look at this little cloud above their heads! That's a thought bubble. It shows what they might be saying to each other.\"\n"
"Ask, \"Hmm... what do you think the mommy and her son are talking about in their thought bubbles?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Angalia wingu hili dogo juu ya vichwa vyao! Hiyo ishara ya kuwaza kitu. Inaonyesha kile wanachoweza kuambiana.\"\n"
"Muulize, \"Hmm... unafikiri mama na mwanae wanazungumza nini katika ishara ya mawazo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei was very excited. They would travel in the big blue bus. He could not sleep that night."
msgstr "Ebei alifurahi sana. Kumbe atasafiri katika lile basi kubwa la bluu! Usiku huo hakuweza kulala vizuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, \"Hmm... look at the boy. He's in bed, but he's not sleeping! He's still thinking about what his mommy said. Maybe she told him something super fun and exciting!\""
msgstr "Sema, \"Hmm... mwangalie mvulana. Yuko kitandani, lakini hajalala! Bado anafikiria kile ambacho mama yake alisema. Labda alimwambia jambo la kufurahisha na la kusisimua!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When his mother came to wake him, Ebei was already dressed."
msgstr "Mamake alipoenda kumuamsha, Ebei alikuwa tayari amevaa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Wow, the boy is up and ready, I wonder where he might be going?”"
msgstr "Sema, “Waooo, mvulana ameamka na yuko tayari, sijui anaweza kuwa anaenda wapi?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei and his mother walked to the bus stop. They waited for the big blue bus. But the bus did not come."
msgstr "Ebei na mamake walienda kwenye kituo cha basi. Walisubiri lile basi kubwa la bluu. Basi halikufika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, \"Look at the boy and his mommy! What color is his shirt? What color are his pants? And what color are his shoes? Now, what color is Mommy's dress? What color are her shoes? And what color is her bag?”\n"
"Now point at the different items and ask, “Wow! Look at Mommy's dress! Can you count how many round circles are on it? Let's look at the trees! Can you count how many trees you can see in the picture?\"\n"
"Then point to the road sign and say, \"Hmm, that's a sign next to the boy. Can you guess what that sign might \n"
"mean? Maybe it tells the bus to stop, or maybe it shows where to go!\""
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kwa kuelekezea picha na useme, \"Angalia mvulana na mama yake! Shati lake ni la rangi gani? Kaptula yake ni ya rangi gani? Na viatu vyake ni vya rangi gani? Sasa mavazi ya Mama ni ya rangi gani? Viatu vyake vina rangi gani? Na begi lake ni la rangi gani?\"\n"
"Sasa onyesha kuelekezea kwenye vitu mbalimbali na umuulize, \"Lo! Angalia nguo ya Mama! Je, unaweza kuhesabu ni miduara mingapi iliyo juu yake? Hebu tuangalie miti! Je, unaweza kuhesabu ni miti mingapi unaweza kuona kwenye picha?\"\n"
"Kisha onyesha kuelekezea kwenye alama ya barabarani na useme, \"Hmm, hiyo ni alama karibu na mvulana. Je, unaweza kuhisi alama hiyo ina maanisha nini? labda inaelezea gari lisimame au labda inaonyesha wapi pa kwenda\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Other people arrived at the bus stop. They complained because the bus was late. \"Where is the bus?\" they asked."
msgstr "Watu wengine walifika kwenye kituo cha basi. Wote walilalamika kuwa basi lilichelewa. Mmoja aliuliza, \"Basi limetuacha?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look! More people came to the bus stop! They're all waiting for the bus. Hmm, maybe the bus is taking a little while. Oh no!\" \n"
"Ask, \"Now, count all the people waiting for the bus. How many are there now? Have you ever ridden on a bus before?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! Watu zaidi walikuja kituo cha basi! Wote wanasubiri basi. Hmm, Labda basi litachukua muda kidogo, Oh hapana!”\n"
"\n"
"Uliza, “Sasa, hesabu watu wote wanaosubiri basi. Wapo wangapi sasa? Umewahi kupanda basi hapo awali?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei was worried. \"We will not be able to go to town,\" he thought. \"I will not be able to get my uniform.\""
msgstr "Ebei alikuwa na wasiwasi. \"Tusipokwenda mjini, sitapata sare yangu ya shule,\" aliwaza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look at the boy! He's waiting and waiting for the bus, and now he looks a little bit worried because it's getting late. Sometimes, when I'm worried, I get a little bit grumpy, like this...\" (make a slightly worried or grumpy face).”\n"
"Ask, \"Now, can you show me what your face looks like when you feel worried?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Mtazame mvulana! Anasubiri na kusubiri basi, na sasa anaonekana kuwa na wasiwasi kidogo kwasababu inazidi kuchelewa. Wakati mwingine, nikiwa na wasiwasi, napata huzuni kidogo, kama hii…”(onyesha wasiwasi kidogo au sura ya wasiwasi).” \n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Sasa, unaweza kunioyesha uso wako unavyokuwa unapokuwa unajiskia wasiwasi?”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Some people gave up and went home. Ebei cried. He did not want to go. \"We will wait a bit longer,\" said his mother."
msgstr "Baadhi yao walikata tamaa wakarudi nyumbani. Lakini Ebei alilia akakataa kurudi. \"Tutasubiri zaidi,\" mama yake alimtuliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, \"Look! Some people are going away from the bus stop, but some are still waiting. Look at that boy over there... oh no! He looks like he is crying.\"\n"
"Ask, \"How do you think that boy might be feeling? Why do you think he feels that way? What do you do when you feel sad?\""
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Angalia! Watu wengine wanaenda mbali na kituo cha basi, lakini wengine bado wanasubiri. Mwangalie mvulana yule pale... la, hapana! Anaonekana kama analia.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri mvulana huyo anaweza kuwa anajisikiaje? Unafikiri kwa nini anajiskia hivyo? Unafanyaje unapojiskia huzuni?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Suddenly, they heard a noise. They saw dust in the air. The bus was coming!"
msgstr "Ghafla, walisikia mngurumo. Wakaona vumbi hewani. Basi lilikuwa linakuja kwa kasi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look! Everyone's looking that way! Their faces look like something’s happening! Maybe... is that the bus coming?\"\n"
"Ask, \"How do you think the people are feeling now? Are they excited? Maybe a little bit tired of waiting? What do you think?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Angalia! Kila mtu anaangalia hivyo! Nyuso zao zinaonekana kama kitu kinatokea! Labda... je, basi hilo linakuja?\"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri watu wanajisikiaje sasa? Je, wamefurahia? Labda wamechoka kidogo kusubiri? Unafikiria nini?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But this bus was not blue. It was not big. It was red and small. The people did not want to get in this bus."
msgstr "Basi halikuwa la bluu wala halikuwa kubwa. Basi lile lilikuwa dogo na jekundu. Waliosubiri waliliangalia tu na hawakuingia ndani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Act surprised and say, \"Oops! That's not the blue bus! Okay, look closely at this bus.”\n"
"Ask, “What color is it?\""
msgstr ""
"fanya kwa mshangao na kusema, \"Lo! Hilo si basi la bluu! Sawa, angalia basi hili kwa makini.\"\n"
"Muulize, \"Lina rangi gani?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Get in! Get in!\" shouted the driver. \"We are very late today,\" he called."
msgstr "Dereva aliwaita, \"Ingieni! Ingieni! Tumechelewa sana leo.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Help the child to learn new words. Point at the different items in the picture and say, “Okay, let's learn some new words! Look at this picture...\"Say purse.\" (Wait for the child to repeat). Point to the briefcase, \"Say briefcase.\" (Wait for the child to repeat). Point to the steering wheel, \"Say steering wheel.\" (Wait for the child to repeat). Point to the rondavel, \"Say rondavel.\" (Wait for the child to repeat)"
msgstr "Msaidie mtoto kujifunza maneno mapya. Onyesha ukielekezea vitu tofauti kwenye picha na useme, “Sawa, tujifunze maneno mapya! Angalia picha hii...\"Sema mfuko wa fedha.\" (Subiri mtoto arudie). Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye mkoba, \"Sema mkoba.\" (Subiri mtoto arudie). onyesha kuelekezea usukani, \"Sema usukani.\" (Subiri mtoto arudie). Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye mzunguko, “Sema mzunguko”, (Subiri mtoto arudie)\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei and his mother got in first. Soon everyone else got in the small red bus."
msgstr "Ebei na mamake walikuwa wa kwanza kuingia. Mara wote waliingia ndani ya basi lile dogo jekundu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, \"Yay! Look! They're on the bus now! That means it's time to go! Hooray!\""
msgstr "Sema, \"La! Tazama! Wako kwenye basi sasa! Hiyo inamaanisha ni muda wa kwenda! Hureeee!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei looked out the window. He saw more people at the bus stop."
msgstr "Ebei alichungulia dirishani. Aliwaona watu wengi zaidi wakiingia ndani ya basi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at each of the different people in the picture and say, \"Look at all these people! See their shirts? Everyone has a different color on their top!\n"
"Ask, \"What color is this shirt? What about this one? Tell me the color of this top! And what color is this one right here?. \n"
"Say, let's now look at what you are wearing. Then ask, “what color is your clothes? What about mine?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kwa kuelekezea watu tofauti kwenye picha and sema, “Tazama watu wote hawa! “Ona mashati yao? Kila mmoja nguo yake ya juu ina rangi tofauti!\n"
"Uliza, “Shati hili ni la rangi gani? Vipi kuhusu hili? Niambie rangi ya nguo hii ya juu! Na hii hapa ni rangi gani?\n"
"Sema, hembu sasa tuangalie umevaa nini. Halafu uliza, “Nguo zako ni za rangi gani? Vipi kuhusu yangu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Even more people were running to catch the bus. But they were too late. The red bus was full. It left for town."
msgstr "Mara basi likaondoka. Ebei aliwaona watu wengine wakikimbia kulifikia basi. Walikuwa tayari wamechelewa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Uh oh! Look! The bus drove away, and some people missed it! They're running super fast to try and catch it! One person looks a little stuck.”\n"
"Ask, “What would you do if the bus left you behind? Would you run after it too? Can you show me how you would run?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, \" ah oh! Tazama! Basi liliondoka, na watu wengine walilikosa! Wanakimbia haraka sana kujaribu kulikamata! Mtu mmoja anaonekana kukwama kidogo.\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Ungefanya nini ikiwa basi lingekuacha? Je, ungelikimbiza pia? Unaweza kunionyesha ungekimbia namna gani?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Ungefanya nini ikiwa basi lingekuacha? Je, ungelikimbiza pia? Unaweza kunionyesha ungekimbia namna gani\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Where is the big blue bus?\" asked Ebei's mother. \"It broke down,\" replied the driver. \"We are fixing it. It will come tomorrow.\""
msgstr "Mamake Ebei alimuuliza dereva, \"Liko wapi basi kubwa la bluu?\" Dereva alimjibu, \"Samahani mama, basi la bluu liliharibika. Linatengenezwa Kesho litakuja.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, \"Look at the little cloud above their heads! That's like a thought bubble. I think the mother is asking the bus driver about the blue bus. Hmm... where could it have gone?\""
msgstr "Sema, “Tazama wingu dogo juu ya vichwa vyao! Hiyo ni kama ishara ya kufikiria jambo. Nafikiri mama anamuuliza dereva wa basi kuhusu basi la bluu. Hmm…litakuwa limeenda wapi?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ebei did not care about the colour of the bus. He did not care about the size. This bus was going to town!"
msgstr "Ebei hakujali rangi wala ukubwa wa basi. Alifurahi kuwa basi lile lilikuwa linawapeleka mjini. Hatimaye, atanunuliwa sare ya shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask the child to share their thoughts about the story and say, “Now tell me, what do you think about the story? What did you like the most about it?”"
msgstr "Muombe mtoto akushirikishe mawazo yake kuhusu hadithi na useme, \"Sasa niambie, una maoni gani kuhusu hadithi hiyo? Ulipenda nini zaidi kwenye hadithi?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Decision"
msgstr "Uamuzi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A village takes a decision together to change their lives for the better."
msgstr "Kijiji kilichukua uamuzi wa pamoja kubadilisha maisha yao yawe mazuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© African Storybook Initiative, 2015. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "African Storybook Initiative, 2015. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My village had many problems. We made a long line to fetch water from one tap."
msgstr "Kijiji changu kilikuwa na matatizo mengi. Tulipanga foleni ndefu kuchota maji kutoka kwenye bomba moja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Describe the picture and say, “Look at this picture! Wow, lots and lots of people are waiting by the tap. They all want to get some water. Hmm, why are they all lined up like that? Maybe the water is coming out super slow?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “What do you think?”"
msgstr "Elezea picha na useme, \"Angalia picha hii! Lo, watu wengi wanasubiri karibu na bomba. Wote wanataka kuchota maji. Mmh, kwa nini wote wamejipanga hivyo? Labda maji yanatoka polepole sana?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We waited for food donated by others."
msgstr "Tulisubiri chakula cha msaada kilichotolewa na wengine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture again and say, “Look at another queue, could the people be queuing for something else?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Let's look at the people who are wearing red, how many are they? How about those wearing green?”\n"
"\n"
"Then say, “Now let's look at the clothes you are wearing, what colors are they?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha tena na useme, “Angalia foleni nyingine, je watu wanaweza kuwa kwenye foleni kutafuta kitu kingine?”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Hebu tuangalie watu waliovaa nyekundu, ni wangapi? Vipi kuhusu wale waliovaa kijani?\"\n"
"\n"
"Kisha sema, “Sasa hebu tuangalie nguo ulizovaa, ni za rangi gani?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We locked our houses early because of thieves."
msgstr "Tulifunga nyumba zetu mapema kwasababu ya wezi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, “Look at this picture! See the mother? She's closing the door with a key, click, click! And look, the window is also closed tight.”\n"
"Ask, “Hmm, why do you think mommy is locking the door? What do you think?"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Angalia picha hii! unamuona mama? Anafunga mlango kwa ufunguo, kwichi kwichi! Na tazama, dirisha pia limefungwa vizuri.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Hmm, unafikiri kwa nini mama anafunga mlango? Unaonaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Many children dropped out of school."
msgstr "Watoto wengi waliacha shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Can you tell me what is happening in this picture?”"
msgstr "Muulize, “Unaweza kuniambia nini kinatokea kwenye picha??"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Young girls worked as maids in other villages."
msgstr "Wasichana wadogo walifanya kazi kama wasaidizi wa nyumbani kwenye vijiji vingine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, “Look, those are young girls. They are supposed to be in school but it looks like they are working as maids.”\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Do you think it's important for children to go to school? Why do you think so?"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwenye picha na useme, \"Tazama, hao ni wasichana wadogo. Walitakiwa wawe shuleni lakini -inaonekana wanafanya kazi kama vijakazi.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Je, unafikiri ni muhimu kwa watoto kwenda shule? Kwa nini unafikiri hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Young boys roamed around the village while others worked on people's farms."
msgstr "Mvulana mmoja mdogo alizungukazunguka kijijini wakati wengine walifanya kazi kwenye mashamba ya watu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the picture and say, “There seems to be many boys moving around the village. I wonder what they could be doing?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Now tell me, how many boys do you see in this picture?"
msgstr ""
"Elekeza kwenye picha na useme, \"Inaonekana kuna wavulana wengi wanaozunguka kijijini. Nashangaa wanaweza kuwa wanafanya nini?\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Sasa niambie, unaona wavulana wangapi kwenye picha hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When the wind blew, waste paper hung on trees and fences."
msgstr "Upepo ulipovuma takataka za karatasi zilining\"inia kwenye miti na uzio."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look at this picture! Whoa, the wind is super strong! See how everything is flying around? Even the papers are stuck on the tree!\n"
"Now, look at the man. The wind is taking his hat! How do you think he feels right now? Is he happy? Sad? Silly? Tell me what you think!"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Tazama picha hii! Lo, upepo una nguvu sana! Tazama jinsi kila kitu kinavyozunguka? Hata karatasi zimekwama kwenye mti!\n"
"\n"
"Sasa, mwangalie mwanaume. Upepo unachukua kofia yake! Unafikiri anajisikiaje sasa hivi? Je, ana furaha? anasikitika? anajiskia mzembe? Niambie unafikiri nini!!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People were cut by broken glass that was thrown carelessly."
msgstr "Watu walikatwa na chupa zilizovunjika na kutupwatupwa kwa uzembe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Oh no! Look at the boy's foot. Is that blood? Uh oh! What happened? There are so many broken things on the floor. Did he maybe step on them? It's a good idea to wear your shoes so your feet don't get hurt!"
msgstr "Sema, La! Angalia mguu wa mvulana. Hiyo ni damu? Lo! Nini kilitokea? Kuna vitu vingi vilivyovunjika kwenye sakafu. Je, labda alivikanyaga? Ni wazo zuri kuvaa viatu vyako ili miguu yako isiumie!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Then one day, the tap dried up and our containers were empty."
msgstr "Halafu siku moja, maji yalikatika bombani na vyombo vyetu havikuwa na maji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Describe the characters emotions and say, “Okay, imagine everyone in the village is feeling a little bit sad and worried. The water tap is empty! That means no water to drink, no water to wash our hands, and maybe even no water for the plants.”\n"
"Ask, \"Why do we need water? What do you use water for?\" Tell me what you think!”"
msgstr ""
"Elezea hisia za wahusika na useme, \"Sawa, fikiria kila mtu kijijini ana huzuni na wasiwasi kiasi. Bomba la maji ni tupu! Hiyo inamaanisha hakuna maji ya kunywa, hakuna maji ya kunawa mikono, na labda hata hakuna maji ya kumwagilia mimea.\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Kwa nini tunahitaji maji? Unatumia maji kufanyia nini?\" Niambie unafikiri nini!”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My father walked from house to house asking people to attend a village meeting."
msgstr "Baba yangu alitembea nyumba hadi nyumba kuomba watu wahudhurie mkutano wa kijiji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Let's count the people in this picture! One, two, three... how many are there? Now, who is super tall? Can you point to the tallest person? And who is tiny? Point to the shortest person!”"
msgstr "Sema, \"Hebu tuhesabu watu katika picha hii! Moja, mbili, tatu... wako wangapi? Sasa, nani ni mrefu sana? Je, unaweza kuonyesha kuelekezea kwa mtu mrefu zaidi? Na ni nani mdogo? Onyesha mtu mfupi zaidi!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People gathered under a big tree and listened."
msgstr "Watu walikusanyika chini ya mti mkubwa na walisikiliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture and say, “Look! See all those people sitting under the big tree? They're talking about things that are making them sad in their village. Like, there's no water to drink, yucky trash all over the place, and broken stuff everywhere. Maybe they're talking together to try and make things better!”"
msgstr "Elezea picha na useme, \"Tazama! Unawaona watu hao wote wameketi chini ya mti mkubwa? Wanazungumza kuhusu mambo ambayo yanawahuzunisha katika kijiji chao. Kama vile, kukosa maji ya kunywa, takataka nyingi kila mahali, na vitu vilivyovunjika kila mahali. Labda wanazungumza pamoja ili kujaribu kufanya mambo kuwa mazuri!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My father stood up and said, \"We need to work together to solve our problems.\""
msgstr "Baba yangu alisimama na alisema.,\"Tunahitaji kufanya kazi pamoja kutatua matatizo yetu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Do you think it's a good idea for them to talk and help each other fix these problems? Why do you think that?”"
msgstr "Muulize, \"Je, unafikiri ni wazo zuri kwao kuzungumza na kusaidiana kurekebisha matatizo haya? Kwanini Unafikiria hivyo?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Eight-year-old Juma, sitting on a tree trunk shouted, \"I can help with cleaning up.\""
msgstr "Juma mwenye umri wa miaka nane amekaa kwenye tawi kubwa la mti alisema kwa sauti, \" Naweza kusaidia kufanya usafi.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Wow! Even kids helped fix problems in their town! That's super cool, right?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Imagine if your friends had a problem, and you had a problem too. Would you help your friends think of ways to solve their problem?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Waoo! Hata watoto walisaidia kutatua matatizo katika mji wao! Hiyo ni nzuri sana, sivyo?\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Hebu fikiria ikiwa marafiki zako walikuwa na tatizo, na wewe pia una tatizo. Je, ungewasaidia marafiki zako kufikiria njia za kutatua tatizo lao?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "One woman said, \"The women can join me to grow food.\""
msgstr "Mwanamke mmoja alisema, \"Wanaweka wanaweza kuungana na mimi kulima mazao ya chakula.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the women in the picture and say, “Look at the ladies in the picture. See that bubbly cloud over their heads? That's their thinking bubble!”\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “What do you think is going on inside their heads? What do you think they are saying to each other? Tell me your ideas!”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea wanawake kwenye picha na useme, \"Watazame wanawake kwenye picha. Ona wingu hilo lenye mvuto lililo juu ya vichwa vyao? Hiyo ni ishara ya wao kufikiria jambo!\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri nini kinaendelea ndani ya vichwa vyao? Unafikiri wanaambiana nini? Niambie mawazo yako!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Another man stood up and said, \"The men will dig a well.\""
msgstr "Mwanaume mwingine alisimama na alisema, \" Wanaume watachimba kisima.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the men in the picture, “Now let's look at these two men. See that bubbly cloud over their heads? That's their thinking bubble!”\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “What do you think is going on inside their heads? What do you think they are saying to each other? Tell me your ideas!”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwa mwanaume kwenye picha, Sasa tuangalie wanaume hawa wawili. Angalia hilo wingu lenye mvuto juu ya vichwa vyao? Hiyo ni ishara ya wao kufikiria jamboi!”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri nini kinaendelea ndani ya vichwa vyao? Unafikiri wanaambiana nini? Niambie mawazo yako!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We all shouted with one voice, \"We must change our lives.\" From that day we worked together to solve our problems."
msgstr "Sote tulipiga kelele kwa sauti, \"Ni lazima tubadilishe maisha yetu.\" Toka siku ile tulifanya kazi pamoja kutatua matatizo yetu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the people in the picture and say, “Look! Everyone is helping to fix their problem together. See all those happy faces? Even the little girl looks like she's dancing because they figured it out! Yay for them! They solved it! Isn't that super great?”"
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea watu kwenye picha na useme, \"Tazama! Kila mtu anasaidia kutatua matatizo yao pamoja. Ona nyuso hizo zote zenye furaha? Hata msichana mdogo anaonekana kama anacheza kwa sababu walisuluhisha pamoja! Je! hiyo si ni nzuri sana?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Emotions Come and Go"
msgstr "Hisia huja na kwenda"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look out for the emotions you feel and why!"
msgstr "Angalia hisia unazojiskia na kwanini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© African Storybook Initiative, 2019. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© African Storybook Initiative, 2019. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ada is chuckling because she heard a funny story. She is smiling. What is Ada feeling?"
msgstr "Ada anacheka kwa sababu alisikia hadithi ya kuchekesha. Anatabasamu. Ada anahisi nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gisa is feeling grumpy. He has a scowl on his face. Why is he irritated?"
msgstr "James anahisi hasira. Ana mkunjo kwenye paji la uso. Kwa nini amekasirika?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yuadoo is scared of the dark. Everyone feels fear sometimes. But Yuadoo can ask for help."
msgstr "Adela anaogopa giza. Kila mtu huhisi hofu wakati mwingine. Lakini Adela anaweza kuomba msaada."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Chidubem is worried about his school work. He can tell his teacher. He can ask for help."
msgstr "Chidu ana wasiwasi juu ya kazi yake ya shule. Anaweza kumwambia mwalimu wake. Anaweza kuomba msaada."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lushan is playing around! It's okay to be silly sometimes."
msgstr "Nathan anacheza cheza! Ni sawa kufanya mchezo wakati mwingine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Eruro is feeling sad. It's okay to cry. Emotions come and go."
msgstr "Ethan anajisikia mwenye huzuni. Ni sawa kulia. Hisia huja na kuondoka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ayator is bursting with happiness. He is joyful. Emotions come and go."
msgstr "Zawadi amejawa na furaha. Yeye amefurahi. Hisia huja na kuondoka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hadiza is bored. She needs to find something to do."
msgstr "Hadija anahisi kuchoka. Anahitaji kupata kitu cha kufanya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ayo is angry. He is frustrated. Anger is a difficult feeling."
msgstr "Ayo amekasirika. Amechanganyikiwa. Hasira ni hisia ngumu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Labake is excited. What's the cause of her excitement? Mother made her favourite food."
msgstr "Lizi amefurahishwa. Je! Ni nini sababu ya kufurahi kwake? Mama alitayarisha chakula akipendacho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zege felt sleepy. He was very tired. \"But wait, is 'sleepy' an emotion?\" asks Efe."
msgstr "Zakayo alihisi usingizi. Alikuwa amechoka sana. \"Lakini, 'kuhisi usingizi' ni hisia?\" Sefu anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Efe is confused! Can you answer his question?"
msgstr "Sefu amechanganyikiwa! Je! Unaweza kujibu swali lake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tega is feeling surprise and shock. He heard some gossip. Is it true?"
msgstr "Tumaini anahisi mshangao na mshtuko. Alisikia uvumi fulani. Ni ukweli?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yebo is sick. She feels miserable. She needs some medicine and rest to feel better."
msgstr "Aisha ni mgonjwa. Anahisi huzuni. Anahitaji dawa na kupumzika ili ajisikie vizuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sekyen is feeling content. She has finished her chores. Now she can play."
msgstr "Selina anahisi kutosheka. Amemaliza kazi zake za nyumbani. Sasa anaweza kucheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Vandefan does not have chores today. He shows two thumbs up to Sekyen. \"Good job, now let's play!\" he says."
msgstr "Victor hana kazi leo. Anamwonyesha Selina vidole viwili. \"Kazi nzuri, sasa hebu tucheze!\" anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu Loves Football"
msgstr "Jasu na Mpira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu loves football. She loves kicking the ball, hard! But she doesn't have her own ball. Jasu comes up with a plan."
msgstr "Jasu ni msichana aliyependa kucheza mpira. Lakini hakukuwa na mpira. Jasu alitafuta mbinu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Room to Read, 2016. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Room to Read, 2016. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu liked to play football."
msgstr "Alitamani sana kucheza mpira."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “On ho, the girl lost her ball. How will she play football” Ask, “Do you play football? Why or why not?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Oh hapana, msichana amepoteza mpira wake. Atachezaje mpira” Muulize: “Unacheza mpira wa miguu? kama ndio kwanini au kama hapana kwanini??"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But she lost her ball!"
msgstr "Lakini alipoteza mpira wake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look, a boy is playing with a ball, could that be the girl's ball?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How would you feel if you were the girl?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Tazama, mvulana anacheza mpira, inaweza kuwa ni mpira wa msichana?”\n"
"Muulize: “Ungejiskiaje kama ungekuwa ni yule msichana?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She looked for old socks, scrap paper, and thread."
msgstr "Jasu alitafuta soksi, karatasi na kamba. "

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the following items and ask the child to name them. Point at each item and ask, “what is this?. \n"
"\n"
"Ask: “What do you think the girl is doing?”"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kwa kuelekezea vitu vifuatavyo na mwambie mtoto avitaje. Onyesha kwa kuelekezea kwenye kila kitu na muulize: “Hiki ni nini?.\n"
"\n"
"Muulize: “Unafikiri msichana anafanya nini?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She made a ball."
msgstr "Alitengeneza mpira."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Wow, is that a ball in a girl's hands? Could that mean she was making a ball?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Can tell me the colors you see on the ball.? What colors are the girls' shoes, dress and top. What colors are the mothers dress and top?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Waoo, Huo ni mpira mikononi mwa msichana? Hiyo inamaanisha kuwa alikuwa anatengeneza mpira?”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize’ “Unaweza kuniambia rangi unazoziona kwenye mpira? Viatu, gauni, blauzi vya msichana vina rangi gani. Gauni na blauzi ya mama yake vina rangi gani?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu kicked her ball everywhere she went."
msgstr "Kila alipokwenda Jasu aliupiga mpira."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “look, the girl is kicking her ball.” \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “do you know how to kick a ball? Can you show me how you kick a ball?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “ Tazama, msichana anapiga mpira wake.” \n"
"Muulize,” Je unajua kupiga mpira? Unaweza kunionyesha jinsi unavyopiga mpira?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu went to visit her grandpa. She kicked her ball into his mango tree. Some mangoes dropped."
msgstr "Alipokwenda kwa babu aliupiga mpira juu. Mpira ulidondosha maembe machanga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oh no, is that the girls ball on the tree?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How do you think the ball got there? How do you think the two mangoes on the ground got there?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema,” Oh hapana, je ule ni mpira wa msichana juu ya mti?”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Unafikiri mpira umefikaje hapo? Unafikiri maembe yaliyo chini yamefikaje?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grandpa wasn’t happy. He told Jasu to be careful. Jasu apologized."
msgstr "Babu hakufurahia. Alimwambia Jasu awe mwangalifu. Jasu alimwahidi babu kutorudia tena."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “There is grandpa talking to the girl. What could he be saying to her? Could the ball have hit the mangoes?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “What would you do if you were the girl and your ball caused grandpa’s mangoes to fall?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “ Kuna babu anaongea na msichana. Anaweza kuwa anamwambia nini? Mpira unaweza kuwa umepiga maembe?\n"
"\n"
"Uliza: “ Ungefanya nini kama ungekuwa ni yule msichana na mpira wako ndio ungekuwa umesababisha maembe ya babu kuanguka?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu went to the market with her mother."
msgstr "Jasu alikwenda sokoni na mama yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, a girls seems to be going somewhere with her mother, I wonder where they could be going.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema. “Tazama, msichana anaonekana anaenda sehemu flani na mama yake, Sijui wanaweza kuwa wanaenda wapi.”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She kicked her ball."
msgstr "Jasu aliupiga mpira."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Help your child learn new words. Say: “Look, there is a palm tree, a man riding a bicycle, a woman carrying a basket, mother running on sandals and a scuff flying off as the mother runs.” \n"
"\n"
"Then say: “ Show me a palm tree, show me a bicycle, show me a basket, show me a pair of sandals and show me a scuff”"
msgstr ""
"Msaidie mtoto wako ajifunze maneno mapya. Sema: “Tazama, kuna mtende, mtu anaendesha baiskeli, mwanamke amebeba kikapu, mama anakimbilia viatu na kilemba kinapeperuka kadili mama anavyokimbia.”\n"
"\n"
"Halafu sema: “Nionyeshe mtende, nionyeshe baiskeli, nionyeshe kikapu, nionyeshe viatu, na nionyeshe kilemba”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It landed in a basket of tomatoes. Tomatoes fell to the ground!"
msgstr "Mpira ukamwaga nyanya. "

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Oh no, tomatoes fell on the ground.” Ask, “How many tomatoes are on the ground? What color are they? Have you seen tomatoes before? Where have you seen them?” \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “How do you think the woman whose tomatoes fell off is feeling? How would you feel if your favourite food fell off?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Oh hapana, nyanya imeanguka chini. “Muulize, “ Kuna nyanya ngapi chini”? Ni za rangi gani? Umewahi kuona nyanya kabla? Uliziona wapi?“\n"
"\n"
"Muulize: “ Unafikiri mwanamke ambaye ndiye  mwenye nyanya zilizodondoka chini anajiskiaje? Ungejiskiaje kama chakula chako pendwa kingedondoka?”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama told Jasu not to play around. Jasu apologized again."
msgstr "Mama alimwambia Jasu asicheze sokoni. Jasu aliomba msamaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask the child to name the fruits and vegetables in the picture. Point at the different fruits and vegetables and say, “what do we call this fruit? What do we call these vegetables?” \n"
"\n"
"Then point at different fruits and vegetables in the picture and ask the child to name colors. Ask, “What color is this?”\n"
"\n"
"Then ask, “Which is your favourite fruit? Which is your favourite vegetable?”"
msgstr ""
"Mwambie mtoto ataje majina ya  matunda na mboga za majani za kwenye picha. Onyesha kwa kuelekezea matunda tofauti na mboga za majani na sema, “tunda hili tunaliitaje”? Mboga hizi za majani tunaziitaje?\n"
"Halafu onyesha matunda tofauti na mboga za majani kwenye picha na mwambie mtoto ataje majina ya rangi. Muulize: “Hii ni rangi gani”?\n"
"\n"
"Halafu muulize: “ Unapenda tunda gani? Unapenda mboga gani za majani?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu carried her ball all the way home."
msgstr "Jasu alihuzunika akaubeba mpira wake hadi nyumbani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look, the girl and the mother are walking home from the markert.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “what is the girl carrying in her hands? How many items are in the mothers basket? What colors are they?\n"
"\n"
"Say, “Look at the child and Mommy” and ask, \"Can you see anything that looks the same on the child and Mommy's clothes and shoes?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama, msichana na mama wanatembea kwenda nyumbani kutoka sokoni.”\n"
"Muulize,”msichana amebeba nini mikononi mwake? Kuna vitu vingapi kwenye kikapu cha mama? Ni vya rangi gani?\n"
"\n"
"Sema, “Watazame mtoto na mama’ na muulize, “Unaweza kuona kitu chochote kinachoonekana sawa kwenye nguo ya mtoto na za mama na viatu?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "At home, Jasu went to the playground with her friends. They played happily."
msgstr "Alipofika, aliwafuata marafiki zake wakacheze uwanjani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, the girl is now home with her friends and they are ready to play together.” Ask, “do you have friends that you play with? How many friends do you have? Are they boys or girls?"
msgstr "Sema, “Tazama, msichana sasa yuko nyumbani na rafiki zake na wapo tayari kucheza pamoja.” Muulize, “Una marafiki unaocheza nao? Una marafiki wangapi? Ni wavulana au wasichana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grandpa was happy that Jasu is playing in a safe place. He bought Jasu a nice new ball. Every evening, the neighborhood kids gathered to play at the playground."
msgstr "Babu alikuwa na furaha kwamba Jasu anacheza sehemu salama. Alimnunulia Jasu mpira mpya mzuri. Kila jioni, watoto wa majirani walikusanyika kucheza pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, there is grandpa, I think he is watching the girl and her friends as they play together. Ask, “how do you think the kids feel? How do you feel when you play with your friends?"
msgstr "Sema, “Tazama,  babu,  Nafikiri anamtazama msichana na marafiki zake wanavyocheza pamoja. Muulize, “Unafikiri watoto wanajiskiaje? Unajiskiaje unapocheza na rafiki zako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Jasu likes kicking the new ball with her friends..."
msgstr "Jasu anapenda kuchezea mpira mpya na rafiki zake..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Wow, I wonder if the playground is near their house? If it is, grandpa can watch them and they will be safe”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Do you also play with your friends close to your house too?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Waoo, Sijui uwanja wa michezo utakuwa karibu na nyumba yao? kama ndivyo, babu anaweza kuwaangalia na watakuwa salama”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Wewe pia unacheza na rafiki zako karibu na nyumbani? “Pia unacheza na rafiki zako wa karibu na nyumba yenu?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "...but Jasu still loves her old ball, too."
msgstr "...lakini Jasu bado anaupenda mpira wake wa zamani pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Now tell me, what do you think of this story? Do you like it? If not, why don't you like it?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “ Sasa niambie, unafikiriaje kuhusu hadithi hii? Umeipenda? Kama sivyo, kwanini hujaipenda?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover. Ask: What do you see? Where is the millipede shongololo sitting?"
msgstr "Jadili ganda la kitabu. Uliza: Unaona nini? Jongoo shongololo amekaa wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shongololo's Shoes"
msgstr "Viatu vya Shongololos"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shongololo has lost his shoes, and the other animals are NOT being very helpful. Will he ever find them?"
msgstr "Shogololo amepoteza viatu vyake, na wanyama wengine sio wa msaada sana. Je ataviona?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Book Dash, 2016. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Book Dash, 2002. Haki zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Where are all my shoes? I know I left them here!"
msgstr "Viatu vyangu viko wapi? Nafahamu niliviacha hapa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use descriptive words and explanations to talk about the pictures. The long millipede has many tiny little feet. I think he is looking for his shoes. I see some yellow boots scattered across the floor. Do you think those are his shoes?"
msgstr "Tumia maneno ya kujielezea na kudadavua kuzungumza kuhusu picha. Jongoo mrefu ana miguu mingi midogo. Nafikiri anatafuta viatu vyake. Naona buti za njano zimetawanyika kwenye sakafu. Unafikiri hivyo ni viatu vyake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I haven’t seen your shoes. Go ask Snail!"
msgstr "Sijaviona viatu vyako. Nenda umuulize konokono!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child questions to help them think about what is happening. Ask: What is he holding in his hand? Who do you think that belongs to?"
msgstr "Uliza mtoto wako maswali kumsaidia afikiri kuhusu nini kinaendelea. Uliza: Ameshika nini mkononi mwake.? Unafikiri ile ni ya nani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No shoes here. Go ask Giraffe."
msgstr "Hakuna viatu hapa. Nenda umuulize Twiga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help your child understand, explain what is happening. Say: Look, the snail is using one of the millipede’s shoes as a shell for his back. Ask: how do you think the shongololo feels about that?"
msgstr "Kumsaidia mtoto wako kuelewa, elezea nini kinatokea. Sema: Tazama, Konokono anatumia moja ya viatu kama gamba kwa mgongo wake. Uliza: unafiri Jongoo anajiskiaje kuhusu hilo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I’m in a hurry – go ask Frog."
msgstr "Mimi nina haraka. Nenda umuulize Chura."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What does the giraffe have on her head? What is she doing? Can you count all her spots?"
msgstr "Uliza: Twiga ana nini kichwani kwake? Anafanya nini? Unaweza kuhesabu madoa yake?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shoes? How many? Go ask Flamingo."
msgstr "Viatu? Vipo vingapi? Nenda umuulize Korongo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Where is the frog sitting? What colours can you see in this picture?"
msgstr "Uliza: Chura amekaa wapi? Unaweza kuona rangi gani kwenye hii picha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Seen your shoes? No, not me."
msgstr "Umeona viatu vyako? Hapana, siyo mimi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic actions from the story. Say: Look, the flamingo is standing on one leg. Can you stand on one leg like flamingo?"
msgstr "Igiza vitendo kutoka kwenye hadithi. Sema: Tazama, ndege flamingo amesimama kwa mguu mmoja. Unaweza kusimama kwa mguu mmoja kama ndege flamingo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Will I ever find my shoes?"
msgstr "Hivi, nitavipata viatu vyangu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about what the characters might be thinking or feeling. Ask: how does he feel? Why do you think he feels that way?"
msgstr "Ongea kuhusu kile ambacho wahusika wanaweza kufikiria au kujiskia. Uliza: Anajiskiaje? Unafikiri kwanini anajiskia hivyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shoes, eh? You should ask the Monkeys."
msgstr "Viatu, eeh? Ungewauliza Nyani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is the fox using the shoe for? What do you think is in the shoe? Would you drink something out of a shoe?"
msgstr "Uliza: Mbweha anatumia kiatu kwaajili ya nini? Unafikiri ndani ya kiatu kuna nini? Ungeweza kunywa kitu flani kutoka kwenye kiatu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hello hello? We’re busy. Go ask Owl, she knows everything!"
msgstr "Hallo, hallo? Tuna kazi nyingi. Nenda umuulize Bundi, anafahamu kila kitu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use a lively, playful voice, with different voices for different characters. Pretend to be the monkeys talking to each other in funny voices."
msgstr "Tumia sauti yenye uchangamfu, ya kucheza, yenye sauti tofauti kwa wahusika tofauti, Igiza kuwa kama Ngedere wanaoongea wao kwa wao kwa sauti za kufurahisha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hmm. I have an idea. Why don’t you ask Lion?"
msgstr "Hmm, nina wazo. Kwanini usimuulize Simba?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connect what is happening in the book with your child’s experiences. Say: Look, the owl is reading a book, just like us. What are some of your favourite books or stories?"
msgstr "Unganisha nini kinatokea kwenye kitabu na uzoefu wa mtoto wako. Sema: Tazama, bundi anasoma kitabu, kama sisi. Je ni vitabu gani au hadithi gani unazipenda zaidi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "These are yours? I’ll give them all back if you come to my party!"
msgstr "Hivi ni vya kwako? Nitavirudisha kama utakuja kwenye sherehe yangu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what does the lion have in his hair? How many shoes can you see? Which of all the animals has the most shoes?"
msgstr "Uliza: Simba ana nini kwenye nywele zake? Unaweza kuona viatu vingapi? Ni mnyama gani kati ya wanyama wote ana viatu vingi zaidi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use the pictures to help your child practice counting. You can ask your child to count, or count out loud for your child. Say: how many animals are there? And how many flags? Can you count all of Shongololo's yellow shoes?"
msgstr "Tumia picha kumsaidia mtoto wako kufanya mazoezi ya kuhesabu. Unaweza kumwambia mtoto wako kuhesabu. au mhesabie mtoto wako kwa sauti. Sema: Wanyama wangapi wako pale? Na bendera ngapi? unaweza kuhesabu viatu vyote vya njano vya Jongoo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Act out events from the book at a later stage. You can hide shoes around the house for your child to try and find. Think of funny or creative places to hide the shoes!"
msgstr "Igiza matukio ya hatua za mbele kutoka kwenye kitabu. Unaweza kuficha viatu karibu na nyumba ili mtoto wako ajaribu kuvitafuta. Fikiria sehemu ya kufurahisha au ya ubunifu ya kuficha viatu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What’s next?"
msgstr "Nini kinafata?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Once the school bell rings, the excitement begins. Grandpa picks Fatima up from school. What adventures will they have?"
msgstr "Mara kengele ya shule inapolia, furaha inaanza. Babu anamchukua Fatima kumpeleka shule Watakuwa na matukio gani ya kufurahisha?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."
msgstr "Kazi hii imepewa leseni chini ya Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fatima is always busy! She loves to run and play."
msgstr "Daima Fatima anakuwa bize (anakuwa na mambo mengi)! Anapenda kukimbia na kucheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her favourite part of the day is when Grandpa arrives. \"How should we spend our day, Fatima?\" asks Grandpa."
msgstr "Kitu anachokipenda zaidi katika siku ni pale Babu anafika. \"Fatima, Je tunapaswa kuitumiaje siku yetu?\" anauliza Babu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I know!\" says Fatima. \"Let’s go to the park.\""
msgstr "\"Najua!\" anasema Fatima. \"Twende kwenye Bustani.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I can see the whole world from up here,\" Fatima shouts."
msgstr "\"Kutokea hapa juu naweza kuiona sehemu kubwa sana.\" Fatima aliongea kwa sauti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"I have an idea!\" \"Let’s play superheroes and pick up the litter,\" says Fatima."
msgstr "\"Nina wazo!\" \"Tucheze mchezo wa mashujaa na tuokote takataka,\" alisema Fatima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Great stuff! Now you can see all the flowers.\" \"What’s next?\" asks Grandpa."
msgstr "\"Safi! Sasa unaweza kuona maua yote\" \"Nini kinafata?\" anauliza Babu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Weeeeeeeee!\" \"What a crazy cool kid you are!\" says Grandpa. \"What’s next?\""
msgstr "\"Weeeeeeeee!\" \"Wewe ni mtoto mzuri sana!\" anasema Babu. \"Nini kinafata?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"How about something cold and delicious?\" says Fatima."
msgstr "\"Unaonaje tupate kitu chochote cha baridi na kitamu?\" Anasema Fatima"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What’s next, kiddo?\" asks Grandpa. Fatima yawns. \"Let’s go home.\""
msgstr "\"Tufanye nini tena, Mtoto?” anasema Babu. Fatima anapiga miayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Hello, Fatima,\" says Mum. \"What did you and Grandpa do today?\""
msgstr "\"Mambo, Fatima,\" anasema Mama. \"Mlifanya nini pamoja na Babu leo?\" \"Sio sana\" wote walisema"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Not much!\" they both say."
msgstr "\"Sio sana\" wote walisema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"What should we do tomorrow?\" asks Fatima."
msgstr "\"Tufanye nini kesho?\" Anauliza Fatima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fatima hurries to bed. She is excited for her next adventure with her best friend, Grandpa."
msgstr "Fatima fanya haraka ukalale. Anafurahia matembezi yake yanayofuata na rafiki yake kipenzi Babu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHHHHH!"
msgstr "SHHHHH!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shh! Baby is asleep! Why is everyone making so much noise?"
msgstr "Shh! Mtoto amelala! Kwanini kila mtu anapiga kelele sana?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Baby is sleeping. zzzzzzzzzzzz"
msgstr "Mtoto amelala. zzzzzzzzzzzz"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DOOF DOOF! DOOF Shh, Sister! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "DOOF DOOF! DOOF Shh, dada! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "CLANG CLANG CLANG! Shh, Brother! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "KLANG KLANG KLANG! Shh, Kaka! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "WOOF WOOF WOOF! Shhh, dog! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "WOOF WOOF WOOF! Shhh, mbwa! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Beepity Beep! Beepity Beep! Shhh, phone! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "Triiiiii Triii! Triiiii Triii! Shhh, simu! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TOOT TOOT TEETOOT! Shhhh, radio! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "DUU DUU DUU! Shhh, Redio! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Brmmm Brmmm BRMMM! Shhhhh, truck! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "Bruummm Bruummm BRUUMMM! Shhhh, Lori! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "CLICKITY CLACK CLICKITY CLACK! Shhhhh, train! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "KLIKITII KLIKITII KLIKITII KLIKITII! Shhhhh, treni! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ba dubba dubba Dubba dubba! Shhhhhhhhh, helicopter! Baby is sleeping!"
msgstr "Toko toko toko toko chwiiiiiii! Shhhhhhh, helikopta! Mtoto amelala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Baby is awake!"
msgstr "Mtoto ameamka!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "DOOF CLANG WOOF BEEP TOOT BRMMM CLICKITY BADUBBA"
msgstr "DOOF CLANG WOOF BEEP TOOT BRMMM CLICKITY BADUBBA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Baby is noisy! CLANG WOOF BEEP BRMM CLICKITY TOOT CLICKITY DOOF BADUBBA! WOOF CLANG DOOF WOOF CLICKITY BAD CLANG DOOF WOOF BRMMM BEEP"
msgstr "Mtoto anapiga kelele! CLANG WOOF BEEP BRMM CLICKITY TOOT CLICKITY DOOF BADUBBA! WOOF CLANG DOOF WOOF CLICKITY BAD CLANG DOOF WOOF BRMMM BEEP"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lost Toy"
msgstr "Mdoli aliyopotea"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A child has lost their favorite toy. They are so sad. Will some kind strangers help?"
msgstr "Mtoto amepoteza mdoli wake anaoupenda. Anahuzuni sana. Kuna wasamaria watakaomsaidia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Describe what is happening in the picture and say, \"Look over here! See the boy? He's holding his toy really close, like he loves it a lot!\"\n"
"Ask, \"Do you have toys? Do you love your toys too?\""
msgstr ""
"Elezea kinachotokea kwenye picha na useme, \"Angalia pale! Unamwona mvulana? Ameshikilia mdoli wake kwa karibu, anampenda sana!\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Je! una midoli? Unaipenda midoli yako?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Oh no! It looks like the boy is crying. I wonder what could have happened. Perhaps he doesn't want to leave? Or maybe he forgot his toy? Hmmm…!"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"La hapana! inaonekana kama mvulana analia. Nashangaa ni nini kimemtokea. Labda hataki kuondoka? Au labda alisahau mdoli wake? Mmmmh...!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look at the boy! He looks really, really sad. See that big cloud above his head? That's a thought bubble, like what he's thinking inside.”\n"
"Ask, \"What do you think he's thinking about that makes him so sad? How can you tell he's feeling sad? What does your face look like when you are sad?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Mtazame mvulana huyo! Anaonekana mwenye huzuni sana. Unaona wingu hilo kubwa juu ya kichwa chake? Huo ni wingi wa  mawazo, kama vile kuna anachofikiria\"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Unafikiri anafikiria nini kinachomfanya awe na huzuni sana? Unaweza kuielezeaje huzuni anayojiskia? Uso wako huwa unaonekanaje ukiwa na huzuni?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture and say, “Oh no! The boy is really sad, he doesn't want to ride a taxi without his toy. Where could it have gone?”"
msgstr ""
"Elezea picha na useme, \"La! Mvulana ana huzuni sana, hataki kupanda teksi bila mdoli wake. Utakuwa umeenda wapi?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the toy in the picture and say, “Look, is that the boy’s toy in that bag?  I wonder how it got there."
msgstr "Onyesha kuelekezea mdoli kwenye picha na useme, \"Angalia, huo ni mdoli wa mvulana kwenye lile begi? Nashangaa ulifikaje kule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Wow, look what we have here. It is a market, they are selling so many things. Now let's explore them together.\n"
"\n"
"Point at the different items and ask the child to name them. Ask, “what is this?” \n"
"\n"
"Then help the child to count by saying, “Now tell me, how many taxis do you see? How many fish are they selling? How many bundles of bananas do they have? How many people are there?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Waoo, tazama tulicho nacho hapa, ni soko, wanauza vitu vingi sana. Sasa hembu tuvichunguze pamoja.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Onyesha kuelekezea vitu mbalimbali na umwombe mtoto avipe majina. Muulize, \"hii ni nini?\" \n"
"\n"
"Kisha msaidie mtoto kuhesabu kwa kusema, \"Sasa niambie, unaona teksi ngapi? Wanauza samaki wangapi? Wana kiasi gani cha ndizi? Kuna watu wangapi?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Act worried and sad then say, “Oh no, is the toy falling off the bag? Not again!”"
msgstr ""
"Igiza wasiwasi na huzuni kisha useme, \"La, je, mdoli anaanguka kutoka kwenye begi? hapana haanguki tena!\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look, there is a dog bucking at the toy”. Mimic the sound of a bucking dog, then say, “I wonder if it will be able to catch the toy from falling onto the ground.”\n"
"\n"
"Ask, “Do you have dogs at home or in your village? Do you like them? Why or why not?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Tazama, kuna mbwa anaubwekea mdoli\". Iga sauti ya mbwa anayebweka, kisha useme, \"Sijui kama ataweza kumnasa mdoli asianguke chini.\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, \"Je, una mbwa nyumbani au kijijini kwako? Unawapenda? kama ndiyo Kwanini au kama huwapendi ni kwanini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Wow, it looks like the dog was able to rescue the toy. What an amazing dog.”"
msgstr "Sema, \"Waoo, inaonekana kama mbwa aliweza kuokoa mdoli. Ni mbwa wa ajabu kama nini.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the items in the picture and say, “Now let's play a spotting game! Look at grandpa's clothes, this toy, and this dog. Can you find the same color on all of them?\n"
"Let's do it like this: \"Grandpa has a white shirt. Look! The dog is also white!\" Now you try! Find a color that's the same on grandpa, the toy, and the dog. What color did you find?"
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuelekezea vitu vilivyo kwenye picha na useme, “Sasa tucheze mchezo wa kuona! Angalia nguo za babu, mdoli huyu, na mbwa huyu. Je, unaweza kupata rangi sawa kwa wote?\n"
"\n"
"Hebu tufanye hivi: \"Babu ana shati nyeupe. Tazama! Mbwa pia ni mweupe!\" Sasa jaribu! Tafuta rangi inayofanana na babu, mdoli na mbwa. Umepata rangi gani?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “Look, is that grandpa with the toy. Did grandpa find the lost toy?”\n"
"\n"
"Point at the boy and say, “Look at the boy, I wonder how he might be feeling seeing his toy.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, \"Tazama, Huyo ni babu aliye na mdoli. Je, babu alipata mdoli aliyopotea?\"\n"
"\n"
"Onyesha kuelekezea kwa mvulana na kusema, \"Mtazame mvulana, nashangaa jinsi anavyojiskia anapoona mdoli wake.\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Now tell me, how do you think the boy feels now that he got his lost toy back? How would you feel if something you love got lost? Why?"
msgstr "Muulize, \"Sasa niambie, unafikiri mvulana anajiskiaje sasa baada ya kupata mdoli wake aliyekuwa amepotea? Ungejiskiaje ikiwa kitu unachokipenda kitapotea? Kwa nini?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What’s at the Park?"
msgstr "Kuna nini mbugani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zoey loves finding things in the park. One day, she gets a big surprise."
msgstr "Zoi anapenda kutafuta vitu mbugani. Siku moja, alistukizwa na jambo kubwa la furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Down the road from Zoey’s house, there is a big, green park."
msgstr "Barabarani kwa chini kutoka nyumba ya Zoi, kuna bustani kubwa ya kijani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zoey is quite shy, but she loves to play in the park. Every day after school, Zoey and Granny go there to play."
msgstr "Zoi ana aibu sana, Lakini anapenda kucheza bustanini. Kila siku baada ya kutoka shule, Zoi na Bibi wanaenda pale kucheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Granny needs glasses to see. But she can hear very well. Zoey is good at finding things. Even better than Granny!"
msgstr "Bibi huhitaji miwani kuona. Lakini anaweza kusikia vizuri sana. Zoi ni mzuri katika kupata vitu. Zaidi kuliko Bibi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She can find birds and bugs."
msgstr "Anaweza kupata ndege na mende."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She can find the prettiest flowers and the tallest trees."
msgstr "Anaweza kupata maua mazuri na miti mirefu zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And she’s very good at finding Granny’s secret sweets."
msgstr "Na ni mzuri sana katika kupata vitu vitamu vya siri vya bibi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s that noise behind the tree?” asks Granny. “Does it sound like a bird?” asks Zoey. “No,” says Granny. “It sounds much bigger than a bird. Can you see what it is?”"
msgstr "\"Hiyo ni sauti gani nyuma ya mti?\" bibi anauliza. \"Inaonesha ni kama sauti ya ndege?\" anauliza Zoi. \"Hapana,\" anasema bibi. \"Ni kama kubwa kuliko ya ndege. Unaweza kuona ni nini hicho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“It’s a dog!” says Zoey."
msgstr "\" Ni mbwa!\" Zoi anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Phew!” says Granny. “This dog is very smelly!”"
msgstr "\"Fyuuu!\" Bibi anasema. \"huyu mbwa ananuka sana!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The next day, Zoey comes home from school and packs her bag. “Are you ready to go to the park?” asks Granny. “Yes, please,” says Zoey. “Granny, look who’s outside!” says Zoey."
msgstr "Siku iliyofuata, Zoi alirudi nyumbani kutoka shule na aliandaa begi lake. \"Upo tayari kwenda mbugani?\" bibi anauliza. \"Ndio, tafadhali,\" anasema Zoi. \"Bibi, angalia nani yupo nje!\" Zoi anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“You found us!” says Zoey. “Now, let’s give you a bath.”"
msgstr "\"Umetupata!\" Zoi anasema. \" Sasa, ngoja tukuogeshe.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And from that day on, Zoey, Granny and their new friend played in the park every day."
msgstr "Na toka siku ile na kuendelea, Zoi, bibi na rafiki yao mpya walicheza mbugani kila siku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu and Zizo"
msgstr "Zibu na Zizo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu and Zizo are twin brothers. They are similar, but different. Being different is not bad, it’s great."
msgstr "Zibu na Zizo ni ndugu wa kiume mapacha. Wanafanana, lakini ni tofauti. Kuwa tofauti sio mbaya, ni nzuri."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu and Zizo are twin brothers. ‘They look the same,’ people always say."
msgstr "Zibu na Zizo ni ndugu wa kiume mapacha. \"Wanafanana,\" watu wanasema daima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Describe the picture and say, “look, these are twin brothers, they look almost the same, like two peas in a pod. \n"
"\n"
"Then say, \"But... hmm... look closely! Can you see anything that's a little bit different between them?\""
msgstr ""
"Elezea picha na sema,”Tazama hawa ni mapacha wa kiume, wanafanana sana, kama njegere zilivyo ndani ya ganda.\n"
"\n"
"Alafu useme, “lakini….hmm…..tazama kwa umakini! unaweza kuona chochote  ambacho ni tofauti kati yao?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama buys them the same clothes. They go to the same school."
msgstr "Mama huwanunulia nguo zilizo sawa. Wanasoma shule moja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “The two brothers are now going to school in their uniform.” \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “what is the color of their uniform?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Ndugu wawili wa kiume wanakwenda shule wakiwa wamevalia sare za shule.”\n"
"\n"
"Muulize, “Sare zao zina rangi gani?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu and Zizo both like banana bread."
msgstr "Zibu na Zizo wote wanapenda mkate wa ndizi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “can you tell me what is on the table? How many slices of bread do you see?"
msgstr ""
"Muulize. “ Unaweza kuniambia nini kipo juu ya meza? Unaviona vipande vingapi vya mkate?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes Zibu and Zizo say ... Hello!! ... at the same time."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine Zibu na Zizo husalimia kwa pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “look, one of them is waving his hand. Perhaps he is greeting someone” \n"
"\n"
"Ask, “show me how you greet people when you meet them.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema,  “tazama, mmoja wao anapunga mkono . Labda anasalimia mtu flani”\n"
"\n"
"Mwambie., “Nionyeshe jinsi unavyosalimia watu unapoonana nao,”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu likes soccer."
msgstr "Zibu hupenda soka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “Tell me, what do you think the boy in this picture is doing?”"
msgstr ""
"Uliza, “Niambie, unafikiri mvulana kwenye picha hii anafanya nini?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zizo likes drawing pictures."
msgstr "Zizo hupenda kuchora picha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask, “What about this one? What do you think he is doing?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask again, “can you tell me the number of pencils and brushes you can see on the floor.”"
msgstr ""
"Uliza, Vipi kuhusu hii? Unafikiri anafanya nini?”\n"
"\n"
"Uliza tena, “unaweza kuniambia idadi ya penseli na brashi unazoweza kuziona sakafuni.?."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu likes to talk to people."
msgstr "Zibu hupenda kuongea na watu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask, “Can you tell me what you think is happening in this picture.”\n"
"\n"
"Then ask, “how many children can you see? Point at the different children and ask, “what is the color of their clothes?”"
msgstr ""
"Uliza, “Unafikiri ni nini kinatokea kwenye picha hii.”\n"
"\n"
"Halafu uliza, “Unaweza kuona watoto wangapi? Onyesha kwa watoto fofauti kwa kuwaelekezea na uliza, “nguo zao ni za rangi gani?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zizo likes to keep to himself."
msgstr "Zizo hupenda kukaa mwenyewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, the boy is reading a book. I wonder what he could be reading about?”"
msgstr "Sema. “Tazama, mvulana anasoma kitabu. Sijui atakuwa anasoma kuhusu nini?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zibu likes counting numbers. He wants to be an accountant."
msgstr "Zibu hupenda kuhesabu namba. Anataka kuwa mhasibu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look! So many numbers! The boy looks like he's counting them.\"\n"
"Ask, \"Can you help me count the numbers? Let's see... how many numbers are red? Now, how many numbers are green? Let's now count the blue numbers. How many blue ones are there? Last one! Can you count how many numbers are yellow?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! kuna namba nyingi! Mvulana anaonekana kama anazihesabu.”\n"
"Uliza, “Unaweza kunisaidia kuhesabu namba? Hebu tuone…  Namba ngapi ni nyekundu? Sasa, namba ngapi ni za kijani? Hebu sasa tuhesabu namba za bluu. Za bluu zipo ngapi? Ya mwisho! Unaweza kuhesabu namba ngapi ni za njano?”\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Zizo likes learning new words. He wants to write books."
msgstr "Zizo hupenda kujifunza maneno mapya. Anataka kuandika vitabu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Look! A pink book! And guess what's on the cover? A kitty! Mimic the cat sound and say, \"Meow! Meow!\" \n"
"Then ask, \"Can you try to make a kitty sound?\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama! Kitabu cha pinki! Na kisia kuna nini kwenye jalada? Paka! Igiza sauti ya paka na sema, Nyaaau! nyaaau!\n"
"\n"
"Halafu uliza, “Unaweza kujaribu kuigiza sauti ya paka!\"?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "‘How come Zibu and Zizo look the same, but like different things?’ ask the children at school."
msgstr "Inakuwaje Zibu na Zizo wanafanana, lakini wanapenda vitu tofauti?\" watoto wanauliza shuleni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture and say, \"Look at these kids! They're looking at the twin brothers and thinking, 'Hmm, why do they like different things even though they look the same?'\""
msgstr ""
"Elezea picha na sema, “Tazama hawa watoto! Wanawaangalia mapacha wa kiume na wanafikiria  “Hmm, kwanini wanapenda vitu tofauti ingawa wanafanana?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We look the same, but we are different and like different things and that's okay.'"
msgstr "Tunaonekana sawa, lakini tuko tofauti na tunapenda vitu tofauti na hiyo ni sawa.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, \"Do you think it's okay for twin brothers to like different things, like maybe one likes cars and the other likes blocks? Why do you think that?\""
msgstr "Muulize “Unafikiri ni sawa kwa wale mapacha wa kiume kupenda vitu tofauti, kama vile labda mmoja hupenda magari na mwingine hupenda viboksi vya kuchezea? Kwanini unafikiria hivyo?” ?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes you can!"
msgstr "Ndio unaweza!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Join Teacher Langa’s class as they share what they want to be when they grow up. Let’s see what they say!"
msgstr "Jiunge na darasa la mwalimu Langa wanaposhirikisha kile wanachotaka kuwa watakapokua wakubwa. Na tuone wanasema nini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What do you want to be when you grow up?” asks Teacher Langa."
msgstr "\"Unataka kuwa nani utakapokuwa mkubwa? '' anauliza mwalimu Langa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Hmmm I can see lots of different children in this picture. They all look different and are doing different things. What do you see?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Hmmm Naweza kuona watoto wengi tofauti tofauti kwenye picha hii. Wote wako tofauti na wanafanya vitu tofauti tofauti. Unaona nini?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Khutso shouts, “I want to be a cook!”"
msgstr "Kuso anapiga kelele,'' Nataka kuwa mpishi!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What do you think is happening in this picture?” If the child is unable to explain the picture, help them to understand what is happening by saying, “the boy is thinking of becoming a chef when he grows up.”"
msgstr "Muulize: Unafikiri nini kinatokea katika picha hii? Kama mtoto anashindwa kuielezea picha, msaidie kufahamu nini kinatokea kwa kusema “mvulana anafikiria kuwa mpishi atakapokuwa mkubwa..”."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I love helping my mom bake and cook at home.” Nandi says, “No! That’s a girl’s job. My mom does all the cooking at home.” “Yes he can, Nandi. You can be anything you want to be,” says Teacher Langa. The class chants, “Yes you can!”"
msgstr "Napenda kumsaidia mama kuoka na kupika nyumbani.'' Anasema Nandi, ''Hapana! Hiyo ni kazi ya kike. Mama yangu ndiye anapika nyumbani.'' Ndio anaweza, Nandi. Unaweza kuwa chochote kile unataka kuwa,''anasema Mwalimu Langa. darasa linaimba,''Ndio unaweza!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is different between this picture and the previous one? Something is falling on someone’s head - can you spot who? How do they feel?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: Kuna tofauti gani kati ya picha hii na ile iliyopita? Kitu kinaanguka juu ya kichwa cha mtu - unaweza kumwona nani? Wanajisikiaje?”\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Milani says, “I want to build houses like my dad.”"
msgstr "Milani anasema,''Nataka kuwa mjenzi wa nyumba kama baba yangu.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What is she thinking of becoming one day?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Anafikiria kuwa nani siku moja?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“No you can’t, that’s dangerous!” yells Phathu. “Yes she can, Phathu, as long as she loves it,” replies Teacher Langa. The class chants, “Yes she can!”"
msgstr "''Hapana huwezi, Hiyo ni hatari!'' Patu anapiga kelele.'' Ndio anaweza, Patu, ilimradi anaipenda,'' anajibu mwalimu Langa. Darasa linaimba, ''Ndio unaweza!''!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many children are in this picture? And how many of them are on the ladder? And if two climbed off, how many would there be on the ladder then?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Ni watoto wangapi wapo kwenye picha hii? Na ni wangapi kati yao wako kwenye ngazi? Na ikiwa wawili walipanda, ni wangapi wangekuwa kwenye ngazi?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sthelo says, “I want to be a nurse.”"
msgstr "Selo anasema, ''Nataka kuwa muuguzi.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, the boy is thinking of becoming a nurse when he grows up.” Ask: “Would you like to become a nurse when you grow up? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Tazama, kijana anafikiria kuwa muuguzi atakapokuwa mtu mzima. muulize: \"Je, ungependa kuwa muuguzi utakapokuwa mtu mzima? Kwanini au kama sio, kwanini?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The class bursts out laughing. “What is so funny?” asks Teacher Langa. Nandi replies, “Nurses are girls.” “There are male nurses too,” says Teacher Langa. “So class, can Sthelo be a nurse? The class booms, “Yes he can!”"
msgstr "Darasa lilinaangua kicheko.'' Nini kinachekesha? anauliza mwalimu Langa. Nandi anajibu, ''Wauguzi ni wasichana,'' Kuna wauguzi wanaume pia,''anasema mwalimu Langa.'' kwahiyo darasa, Selo anaweza kuwa Muuguzi? Darasa linapiga kelele, ''!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Why do you think other kids are laughing? Point to the child hanging on the pole and say: “How do you think he is feeling? Why do you think he is feeling that way? Do you think it is because the other children are saying he can’t be a nurse because he is a boy? Did you know that men and women can be nurses, just like men and women can be doctors?”"
msgstr "Muulize: Unafikiri kwa nini watoto wengine wanacheka? Onyesha mtoto anayening'inia kwenye mti na useme: \"Unafikiri anahisije? Kwa nini unafikiri anajihisi hivyo? Unafikiri ni kwa sababu watoto wengine wanasema hawezi kuwa muuguzi kwa sababu yeye ni mvulana? Je, unajua kwamba wanaume na wanawake wanaweza kuwa wauguzi, kama vile wanaume na wanawake wanavyoweza kuwa madaktari?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“I want to be an artist and draw pretty pictures,’’ says Liyana."
msgstr "''Nataka kuwa msanii na kuchora picha nzuri,'' Liyana anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What do you think this child wants to be when she grows up? What is she painting? How do you think she feels? Why does the woman in the picture look worried?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Unafikiri mtoto huyu anataka kuwa nani akiwa mkubwa? Anachora nini? Unafikiri anajisikiaje? Kwa nini mwanamke aliye kwenye picha anaonekana kuwa na wasiwasi?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“That’s not a real job,” says Khutso and rolls his eyes. “That sounds lovely, Liyana!” replies teacher Langa. “Can Liyana be an artist?” “Yes she can!” shouts the class!"
msgstr "'' Hiyo sio kazi rahisi,''Kuso anasema na akiangaza macho.'' Hiyo ni nzuri Liyana!\"\" mwalimu Langa anajibu.''Je Liyana anaweza kuwa msanii?''Ndio anaweza!'' Darasa linapiga kelele!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe what the children are wearing, and compare the colours and clothes with what you and your child are wearing."
msgstr ""
"Eleza watoto wanavaa nini, na ulinganishe rangi na nguo na mavazi ambayo wewe na mtoto wako mmevaa.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“I want to be an alarm clock,” says Phathu."
msgstr "''Nataka kuwa mpiga kengele,'' Patu anasema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Hmmm, what does this child want to be? An alarm clock!? What do you think about that?”"
msgstr "Sema: \"Hmmm, mtoto huyu anataka kuwa nani? Saa ya kengele!? Una maoni gani kuhusu hilo?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Huh?” “What do you think, class?” asks Teacher Langa. The class booms, “Yes you can! Yes you can!”"
msgstr "''Huh?'' ''Darasa, mnafikiriaje?'' mwalimu Langa anauliza. Darasa linapiga kelele, ''Ndio unaweza! Ndio unaweza!''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Who has short hair in this picture? Who has long hair? And your hair? Is it short or long? And my hair?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Ni nani aliye na nywele fupi kwenye picha hii? Nani ana nywele ndefu? Na nywele zako? Je, ni fupi au ndefu? Na nywele zangu?\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nandi hasn’t shared what she wants to be when she grows up. What do you think she could be?"
msgstr "Nandi hajashirikisha kile anachotaka kuwa atakapokuwa mkubwa. Unafikiri anaweza kuwa nani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What did you think of the story? What did you like about it? Do you know that you can be anything you want? Then say, “Yes you can!”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Unafikiria nini juu ya hadithi? Ulipenda nini juu yake? Unajua kwamba unaweza kufanya kazi yoyote unayotaka? Kisha sema, \"Ndiyo unaweza!\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yellow Earth, Brown Earth"
msgstr "Dunia ya njano, Dunia ya kahawia (brown)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi is an explorer. A cloud-watcher, a seed-sorter and a puddle-splasher. Travel to Avi’s favourite place — the Earth — in this book about noticing and recognising patterns."
msgstr "Avi ni mpelelezi. mtazama mawingu, mpangaji wa mbegu, kinyunyizo cha majii, Safari ya kwenda sehemu anayoipenda Avi - Dunia - katika kitabu hiki inahusu kutambua na kujua mifumo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi wakes up early. It is a good day. Avi is visiting Yellow Earth today. Yellow flowers, dried-up flowers, tiny flowers. Yellow flowers—"
msgstr "Avi huamka mapema. Ni siku nzuri. Avi anatembelea dunia ya njano leo. Maua ya njano, maua ya njano yaliyokaushwa, maua madogo, maua ya njano-"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi makes bunches."
msgstr "Avi hutengeneza mashada."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and ask, “tell me, what do you see in this picture?”"
msgstr "Onyesha picha kwa kuilelekezea kwa kidole na uliza. “niambie, unaona nini kwenye picha hii?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi looks for the perfect stick to poke the earth with. Smooth stick bumpy stick. Smooth stick—"
msgstr "Avi hutafuta kijiti kinachofaa zaidi cha kutikisia dunia. Fimbo laini, fimbo yenye matuta, fimbo laini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi keeps looking for treasures."
msgstr "Avi anaendelea kutafuta hazina."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “what do you think the boy is doing?"
msgstr "Muulize,\"Unafikiri mvulana anafanya nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi collects seeds. Brown seeds, black seeds, red seeds, green seeds. Brown seeds, black seeds— Yellow Earth is a happy place."
msgstr "Avi hukusanya mbegu. Mbegu za rangi ya kahawia, mbegu nyeusi, mbegu nyekundu, mbegu za kijani, mbegu za kahawia, mbegu nyekundu - Dunia ya njano ni mahali pa furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, “look, the boy collected seeds.”\n"
"Ask, “how many groups of seeds do you see? What colours are they? Which group has more seeds?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Tazama, mvulana alikusanya mbegu,” Muulize, “unaona makundi mangapi ya mbegu? Ni ya rangi gani? Kundi gani lina mbegu zaidi?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi is visiting Grey Earth today."
msgstr "Avi anatembelea Dunia ya rangi ya kijivu leo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Big puddle, small puddle, no puddle. Big puddle, small puddle—"
msgstr "Dimbwi kubwa, dimbwi dogo, hakuna dimbwi, dimbwi kubwa, dimbwi dogo ---"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point at the picture and say, “there is a bird flying over the grey earth.” then mimic the action of flying and ask the child to do the same."
msgstr ""
"Onyesha kuielekezea picha na sema, “kuna ndege anapaa kwenye dunia ya kijivu. “halafu igiza kitendo cha kupaa na mwambie mtoto afanye hivyo hivyo.\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Drip! Drop! Plish! Drip—"
msgstr "Drip,! Drop! Pish! Drip---"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grey Earth is a wet place."
msgstr "Dunia ya rangi ya kijivu ni mahali penye ubichi/unyevunyevu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say, \"Listen! It's so wet outside! It's been raining, and I can hear the raindrops going... drip, drop, drip, drop!\" (Mimic the \"drip, drop\" sounds. you can also tap your finger like raindrops).”\n"
"Ask, \"Can you say drip, drop like this? Drip, drop!\""
msgstr ""
"Sema, “Sikilliza! nje kumelowa sana! Imekuwa inanyesha, na naweza kusikia matone ya mvua yanadondoka ndo, ndo, ndo, ndo!” (Igiza sauti za “ndo, ndo”. Pia unaweza kugonga kidole chako kama matone ya mvua).”\n"
"Uliza, “Unaweza kusema ndo, ndo kama hivi? Ndo! ndo!”!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi is visiting Brown Earth today. CRUNCH crunch CRUNCH crunch—"
msgstr "Avi anatembelea dunia ya kahawia leo. kwachu kwachu kwachu kwachu---"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi stomps on the dry ground."
msgstr "Avi hukanyaga ardhi iliyokauka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Look, the child is playing.” Ask, “how do you think the child feels? How do you feel when you play?"
msgstr ""
"Sema, “ Tazama, mtoto anacheza”, Muulize , “Unafikiri mtoto anajiskiaje? Unajiskiaje unapocheza?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi smiles at the bright sun. Long cloud, round cloud, thin cloud. Long cloud— Brown Earth is a joyful place."
msgstr "Avi hutabasamu kwenye jua kali. Wingu refu, wingu la mzunguko, wingu refu--- Dunia ya rangi ya kahawia ni mahali pa furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture by pointing at it and make a real life comparison by saying, \"Look up! See the clouds? Wow! Some clouds are long like a wiggly worm, some are round like a ball, and some are super thin, like a tiny little string!"
msgstr "Elezea picha kwa kuonyesha ukiielekezea na ufananishe na maisha halisi kwa kusema, “ Tazama! Ona mawingu? Waoo! Baadhi ya mawingu ni marefu kama mnyoo, baadhi ni ya nviringo kama mpira, na baadhi ni membamba sana, kama kamba ndogo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi watches the Earth change every year. Yellow Earth, Grey Earth, Brown Earth—"
msgstr "Avi huangalia mabadiliko ya dunia kila mwaka. Dunia ya njano, dunia ya kijivu, dunia ya kahawia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point at the trees in the picture and say, “\"Look! Wow! The trees are so pretty and yellow!” \n"
"\n"
"Then point at the grass and say, “And look at the grass! Some of it is yellow, and some of it is brown.\""
msgstr ""
"Onyesha miti kwa kuilekezea kwenye picha na sema, “”Tazama! Waoo! Miti ni mizuri sana na ya njano!”\n"
"\n"
"Halafu onyesha kwenye nyasi na sema, “Na tazama kwenye nyasi! Baadhi yake ni njano, na baadhi yake ni kahawia.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi is looking for a stick."
msgstr "Avi anatafuta fimbo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Off to Yellow Earth again!"
msgstr "Nenda tena kwa dunia ya njano!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask, “what do you think the boy wants to do?”"
msgstr "Muulize,\"Unafikiri mvulana anafanya nini?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Patterns Are All Around Us The day, the week, the month and the year — all have patterns that repeat. The seasons change every year and come back the same way. Every year, winter is followed by summer, which is followed by the monsoon. Look around you and try to spot these patterns. Go back to the beginning of the book and look for patterns you might have missed."
msgstr "Miundo ipo imetuzunguka. Siku, wiki, mwenzi na mwaka-- vyote vina miundo inayojirudia. Ni kwasababu majira hubadilika kila mwaka na inajirudia kwa jinsi hiyo hiyo. Kila mwaka, majira ya baridi yanafuatiwa na majira ya joto, ambayo yanafuatiwa na upepo wa msimu. Angalia pande zote na jaribu kuangalia miundo hii. Nenda nyuma mwanzo wa kitabu na tafuta miundo ambayo pengine uliikosa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say, “Now tell me, what do you think of this story? What did you like or not like?”"
msgstr "Muulize: Sasa niambie, ulifikiria nini kuhusu hadithi hii? Ulijifunza nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is Nita Upside Down"
msgstr "Kwanini Nita yupo juu chini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nita’s hanging upside down. Can she turn the right way round?"
msgstr "Nita ananing'inia juu chini. Anaweza kuzunguka kurudi kwenye mkao wa kawaida?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nita’s hanging upside down, her long hair tickling at the ground. The trees, the grass, the everything is all the wrong way round."
msgstr "Nita ananing\"inia juu chini, nywele zake zinagusa ardhini. Miti, nyasi, kila kitu kimekaa kwa jinsi isiyo sahihi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Her feet, they poke into the sky. Little Navi’s walking by. He says ‘I’ve seen you here before. You’re upside down again! What for?’"
msgstr "Miguu yake, inapiga angani. Navi mdogo anatembea. Anasema '' Nimeshawahi kukuona hapa hapo nyuma\" Upo juu chini tena! Kwaajili ya nini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "His feet swim lightly in the air. She tries to hide behind her hair. ‘It’s h-h-h-hard to t-t-talk’, she says to him. ‘I’m not the same. I don’t fit in.’"
msgstr "Miguu yake inaogelea kidogo hewani. Anajaribu kujificha nyuma ya nywele zake, 'Ni ngu-ngu-ngu-ngumu ku-ku-ku-kuongea,' anamwambia, siko sawa. sitoshei.'"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Navi takes her by the hand. He wants to help her understand. They climb to Navi’s look-out spot. From up here they can see a lot. They perch and have a quiet stare at children playing here and there."
msgstr "Navi anamshika mkono. Anataka kumsaidia aelewe. Wanapanda hadi eneo kutokea Navi anapotazama. Kutokea pale juu wanaweza kuona vingi. Wanakaa na kuwatazama kwa utulivu watoto wanaocheza hapa na pale."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Those kids are not tthe same at all. Abe’s round."
msgstr "Wale watoto hawafanani /sio wale wale kabisa. Zamu ya Abe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Chi’s freckled,"
msgstr "Madoa ya Chi,"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lala’s extra tall."
msgstr "Lala ni mrefu zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bambam’s wild and must be free,"
msgstr "Mwitu ya Bambam ni lazima iwe huru"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "while Lulu’s reading quietly."
msgstr "huku Lili akisoma kimya kimya."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look at Freya's crazy hair."
msgstr "Angalia nywele za Freya zinachekesha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And Sid wears glasses everywhere."
msgstr "Na Sid huvaa miwani kila mahali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And me, I am just skin and bone. And you are you. You’re not alone. Each human’s sort of strange, you see. That makes you just the same, like me. This world is really one big game. To play, we can’t all be the same."
msgstr "Mimi ni ngozi tu na mifupa. Na wewe ni wewe. Hauko peke yako. Kila aina ya binadamu ni ya ajabu, unaona. Hii inawafanya mfanane, kama mimi. Kweli dunia hii ni mchezo mmoja mkubwa. Katika kucheza hatuwezi kufanana wote."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nita feels the right way round, thanks to the new friend she’s found. Upside down was never fun. Now she plays with everyone."
msgstr "Nita anaona njia sahihi, shukrani kwa fafiki mpya, amepatikana. Juu chini haikuwa furaha kamwe. Sasa hucheza na kila mmoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover. Ask: What do you see? What do you think this story is about?"
msgstr "Jadili ganda la kitabu. Uliza: Unaona nini? Unafikiri hadithi hii inahusu nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up"
msgstr "Nitakapo kuwa mkubwa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I don’t know what I want to be when I grow up. Can you help me choose?"
msgstr "Sijui nataka kuwa nani nitakapo kuwa mkubwa. Unaweza kunisaidia kuchagua?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can say: Look, the girl is holding a big sunflower. What colour is the flower’s petals? And what colour is the stem? Have you ever seen such a big flower in real life?”"
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kusema: Tazama, msichana ameshikilia ua kubwa  la alizeti. Ua lina rangi gani?  Na shina lina rangi gani? Umewahi kuona ua kubwa namna hii katika maisha yako?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What do I want to be when I grow up?"
msgstr "Ninataka kuwa nani nitakapokuwa mkubwa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What is that? (mimic barking sounds). Ask your child to think about dogs they know: where have they seen them? What are they like?"
msgstr "Muulize: “ Hicho ni nini? (igiza sauti ya kubweka). Mwambie mtoto wako afikirie kuhusu mbwa anayewajua: Aliwaona wapi? wanafanana na nini? ?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Wow, the girl is dancing.” Ask: How do you think the girl feels? Do you love to dance? How do you feel when you dance?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: Waoo, msichana anacheza.”\n"
"Muulize: Unafikiri msichana anajiskiaje? Unapenda kucheza? Unajiskiaje wakati unapocheza??"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a dancer and dance on a stage."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. Nataka kuwa msanii wa kucheza na nicheze kwenye jukwaa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many ballet shoes can you see? What colors are they?”"
msgstr "Muulize:” Unaviona viatu vingapi vya kamba? Ni vya rangi gani?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe the picture and say: “Look, there is a puppy with a Firefighter. The firefighter is holding a fire hose. He uses it to put out big fires.”"
msgstr "Elezea picha na useme: “Tazama, kuna mbwa mdogo na mzimamoto. Mzima moto anashikilia bomba la kuzimia moto. analitumia kuzima moto mkubwa”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a firefighter and put out big fires."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. Nataka kufanya kazi katika jeshi la Ukoaji kitengo cha zimamoto na kuzima moto mkubwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Would you like to be a firefighter? Why or Why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: “ Unapenda kuwa mzimamoto?  kama unapenda ni kwanini na kama haupendi ni kwanini?”\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a nurse and make sick people better."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. Nataka kuwa muuguzi na kuwafanya wagonjwa wajiskie nafuu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look now she is a nurse”. Ask: Have you seen a nurse before? Where did you see a nurse? Would you like to be a nurse or a doctor? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Tazama yeye ni muuguzi sasa”. \n"
"Muulize:  Umewahi kumuona muuguzi kabla? Ulimuona wapi Muuguzi? Je unapenda kuwa muuguzi au daktari? kama unapenda ni kwanini na kama haupendi ni kwanini?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Wow, there is a teddy with a nurse. I wonder how he is feeling.” Ask: “How do you think a teddy is feeling? Why do you think he is feeling that way?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Waoo, Mdoli yuko na muuguzi. Nashangaa anajiskiaje?\n"
"Muulize:” unafikiri mdoli anajiskiaje? unafikiri kwa nini anajiskia hivyo?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a musician and play in a band."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. nataka kuwa mwanamuziki na kucheza kwenye bendi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Ohhh, the girl is holding a guitar. I think she is a musician.” Ask: “Do you love music? What songs do you like?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Ohhh, Msichana ameshikilia gitaa. Nafikiri yeye ni mwanamuziki.” Muulize: Je unapenda muziki? unapenda nyimbo gani?’’?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Describe and explain what you see in the picture. Point to the spanner and say: “this is a spanner. A spanner is used to grip, tighten or loosen screws and nails.” (mimic the action of using a spanner). This will help a child to learn new words “grip”, “tighten” and “loosen”."
msgstr "Elezea na dadavua unachokiona kwenye picha. Elekezea kwenye spana na useme: “hii ni spana. Hii ni spana inatumika kushika, kukaza, au kulegeza skrubu na misumali.” (Igiza kitendo kwa kutumia spana). Hii itamfanya mtoto ajifunze maneno mapya “Kushika”, “kukaza” na “kulegeza”."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a mechanic and fix cars and tractors."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. nataka kuwa fundi magari na kurekebisha magari na matrekta."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Spanners are used by mechanics to fix cars and other vehicles.” Ask: “Where on this car do you think we can use a spanner?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Spana hutumiwa na mafundi kutengeneza magari na vyombo vingine vya usafiri”, \n"
"Muulize: “ Unafikiri kwenye gari hii ni sehemu gani tunaweza kutumia spana?\"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say: “Look, she is writing down letters from the alphabet on the board”. Ask: Can you recognise any of these letters? Say: “Let’s sing the alphabet song together - A, B, C, D, E, F, G….”  \n"
"\n"
"You can also point to the different letters and name different words that start with that letter."
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Tazama, anaandika herufi kutoka kwenye alfabeti za kwenye ubao”. Muulize: Unaweza kuzitambua herufi hizi? Sema: “Ngoja tuimbe wimbo wa Alfabeti pamoja- A,B,C,D,E,F,G…..”\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza pia kuonyesha herufi tofauti na kutaja maneno tofauti yanayoanza na herufi hizo.\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a teacher and teach children to read and write."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. Nataka kuwa mwalimu na kufundisha watoto kusoma na kuandika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Does your teacher also write on the board at school? What do you like most about school? And what don’t you like?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: “Je mwalimu wako pia huwa anaandika kwenye ubao shuleni? Unapenda nini zaidi kuhusu shule? Na nini hupendi?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look - now she is wearing a soccer outfit.” Ask: “What colour are her pants? What colours are her socks? And What colours are her shoes?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema:  “Tazama-sasa amevaa nguo za kuchezea mpira wa miguu”,  “Kaptura ina rangi gani? soksi zake zina rangi gani? Na viatu vyake vina rangi gani?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a soccer player and score the winning goal."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa. Nataka kuwa mchezaji wa mpira na kufunga goli la ushindi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Here is a soccer ball.” Ask: “What colours are the ball? What shape is the ball? What can you see here at home that is the same shape?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Huu ni mpira wa miguu”, Muulize: “Mpira una rangi gani? Mpira una umbo gani? Unaona kitu gani hapa nyumbani chenye umbo sawa na mpira?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be an astronaut and fly to the moon."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa, Nataka kuwa mwana anga na kuruka hadi mwezini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Look, there is the moon, and here are more planets! Do you know how to get to the moon? You have to be an astronaut.”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Tazama, kuna mwezi, na hapa ni nyota nyingi!  Je unajua jinsi ya kufika mwezini? Lazima uwe mwana anga.”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say: “What is an astronaut? An astronaut is a person who is trained to travel to space. They travel to space in a spacecraft. A spacecraft is a vehicle that is designed to fly and operate in outer space. How cool is that?”\n"
"\n"
"Ask: “Would you like to go to space? Why or why not?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Mwana anga ni nini?’ Mwana anga ni mtu ambaye amefundishwa kusafiri angani. Anasafiri na chombo cha angani. Chombo cha angani ni chombo cha usafiri kilichobuniwa kupaa na kufanya kazi katika eneo la anga. Ni nzuri kwa namna gani?” \n"
"\n"
"Muulize: “Ungependa kwenda angani?\n"
"Kwanini ungependa na kwa nini usingependa?”?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Say: “Now she is a chef. She cooks delicious food for everyone.”\n"
"\n"
"Make links between the pictures and your child’s world. Ask: “Who cooks for you at home? Do you like making food, or helping to prepare our meals?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Sasa binti ni mpishi. Hupika chakula kitamu kwa kila mmoja.”\n"
"\n"
"Unganisha kati ya picha na dunia ya mtoto wako. Muulize: Nani huwa anakupikia nyumbani? Unapenda kutengeneza chakula, au kusaidia kuandaa vyakula vyetu?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I want to be a chef and make food for my family and friends."
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa, Nataka kuwa mpishi na kuandaa chakula cha familia yangu na marafiki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Hmmmm. Those biscuits look delicious” (and mimic smelling the biscuits or making eating sounds). Ask: “Do you love biscuits? Can you count the number of biscuits in the picture? What colors and shapes are these biscuits?”"
msgstr ""
"Sema: “Hmmmm. Hizo biskuti zinaonekana ni tamu” ( na igiza kunusa harufu ya biskuti au tengeneza sauti za kula).\n"
"Muulize: “ Unapenda biskuti? Unaweza kuhesabu idadi ya biskuti za kwenye picha? Biskuti hizi zina rangi na maumbo gani?\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask or say: “What is the girl thinking about? Perhaps she is thinking about what she wants to be when she grows up.”\n"
"\n"
"Say (while pointing to each thought): “perhaps she is deciding whether she wants to be a dancer…or an astronaut…., or a teacher one day?”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: “ Msichana anawaza kuhusu nini? Labda anawaza kuhusu anataka kuwa nani atakapokuwa mkubwa.”\n"
"\n"
"Sema: ( huku ukielekezea kidole kwa kila wazo)”labda anaamua ikiwa anataka kuwa mchezaji  au mwana anga… au  Mwalimu siku moja?”\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When I grow up, I can choose whatever I want to be!"
msgstr "Nitakapokuwa mkubwa, Naweza kuchagua niwe nani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What do you want to be when you grow up?"
msgstr "Unataka kuwa nani utakapokuwa mkubwa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “What would you want to be when you grow up? Why?”"
msgstr "Muulize: \"Ungependa kuwa nani ukiwa mtu mzima? Kwa nini?\"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: Which of these items have you seen at home, outside, or in our community? Which one is your favourite and why?”"
msgstr "Muulize: Ni kipi kati ya hivi vitu umeviona nyumbani, nje, au katika jamii zetu? Ni kipi umekipenda zaidi na kwanini?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask: “What do you think about this story?”\n"
"\n"
"Then say: “Do you know that there are many different things that you can be when you grow up? How exciting!”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: \"Una maoni gani kuhusu hadithi hii?\"\n"
"\n"
"Kisha sema: “Je, unajua kwamba kuna mambo mengi tofauti-tofauti ambayo unaweza kuwa nayo unapokuwa mtu mzima?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What's In The Pot?"
msgstr "Kuna nini kwenye Chungu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sam can’t wait for supper. What’s in the pot? Wait and see."
msgstr "Sam hawezi kusubiri chakula cha usiku. Kuna nini kwenye Chungu? subiri uone."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s for supper?” asked Sam. “It’s a surprise”, said Mama, putting a big pot on the stove."
msgstr "''Tunakula chakula gani usiku?'' anauliza Sam. '' Ni cha kufurahisha na kushangaza','' alisema Mama. Anatenga sufuria kubwa jikoni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She added a jug of water. Sam was worried. “Are we having water for supper?” he wailed. “It’s a surprise. Wait and see.” replied Mama."
msgstr "Aliongeza jagi la maji. Sam alikuwa na wasiwasi. ''Chakula cha usiku?''alihuzunika. Ni mshangao. Subiri uone. alijibu Mama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Can I help?” asked Sam. “I could stir.”"
msgstr "''Naweza kusaidia?'' aliuliza Sam. ''Ningeweza kuchochea.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“You are still a bit short,” said Mama. “The pot might fall over. But you can help me by fetching things.”"
msgstr "''Bado ni mfupi,'' Mama anasema ''Chungu kinaweza kudondoka. ila unaweza kunisaidia kwa kubea vitu','"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"Can you bring me an onoin, please.\" \"This doesn't smell very nice.\""
msgstr "'' Tafadhali unaweza kuniletea kitunguu, Hii haina harufu nzuri sana.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "\"They will taste nice once they are cooked.\""
msgstr "''Zitakuwa na ladha nzuri zikiwa zimepikwa,''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Now I need some tomatoes. No, that is an apple. The tomatoes are also round and red, but you will find them in the fridge.”"
msgstr "''Sasa nahitaji nyanya. Hapana, hiyo ni apple/tufaa. Nyanya pia ni za mduara na nyekundu. lakini utazikuta kwenye friji.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Can you bring me potatoes. They are round and brown.”"
msgstr "''Unaweza kuniletea viazi. Ni vya mviringo na vina rangi ya kahawia.''."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Is supper ready yet?”"
msgstr "''Je chakula cha usiku kiko tayari?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“If you are hungry you can eat the apple while you wait.” “What about these?” “No, we won’t need biscuits. We can save those for after supper.”"
msgstr "\"Kama una njaa unaweza kula epo/tofaa wakati ukisubiri.\" \" Vipi kuhusu hizi?\" \" Hapana, hatuhitaji biskuti. Tunaweza kutunza hizo kwaajili ya chakula cha jioni.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s in the pot?”"
msgstr "''Kuna nini kwenye sufuria?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“It’s a surprise. Wait and see.”"
msgstr "''Cha kufurahisha na kushangaza. Subiri uone.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What about this?” “That is a watermelon. It will be too big for the pot.” “See if you can find some spinach. It is also green.”"
msgstr "''Vipi kuhusu hili?'' ''Hilo ni tikiti maji. litakuwa kubwa sana kwenye sufuria,''Angalia kama unaweza kupata mchicha. Pia ni wa kijani.''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Please get some bread. No, it won’t go into the pot but on the table.”"
msgstr "''Tafadhari chukua mkate. Hapana hauwezi kuingia kwenye sufuria labda juu ya meza,''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama carried the pot to the table and started to dish up. “What’s in the pot?” asked Sam."
msgstr "Mama alibeba sufuria juu ya meza na akaanza kuonja. Kuna nini kwenye sufuria? aliuliza Sam."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Soup!” My favourite!"
msgstr "''Supu'' Ndio nachokipenda zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego's Tea Party"
msgstr "Tafrija ya chai ya Tito"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego is hosting a tea party! But something strange keeps happening while he is setting the table."
msgstr "Tito anaandaa tafrija ya chai! Lakini kuna jambo la ajabu linatokea mara kwa mara wakati akiwa anaendelea kuandaa meza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego is hosting a tea party for the WHOLE family. “How many people are coming for tea, Koko?” “You, me, Mama, and Papa. And your little sister, Tshiamo.”"
msgstr "Tito anaandaa tafrija ya chai kwaajili ya familia nzima. \" Ni watu wangapi wanakuja kwaajili ya chai, Bibi?\" \"Wewe, mimi, Mama, na Baba na dada yako mdogo Shani\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego counts the teacups as he takes them from the kitchen. “One, two, three, four, and one for Koko!”"
msgstr "Tito anahesabu vikombe vya chai kadili anavyovichukua kutoka jikoni. \"Moja, mbili, tatu na moja kwaajili ya Bibi\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego goes to the stoep and places the teacups down on the table. “One, two, three, four, and ... ?” “I only see four cups,” says Koko, “but we are five people.” “When I was in the kitchen before, there were five cups!” Tlotlego exclaims."
msgstr "Tito anaenda barazani na anaweka vikombe chini mezani. \"Moja, mbili tatu, nne na ...?\" \" Naona vikombe vinne tu.\" anasema Bibi, \" lakini tupo watu watano.\" \" Nilipokuwa jikoni kabla, vilikuwa vitano!\" Tito anashangaa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego counts the pretty little plates as he takes them from the cupboard. “One, two, three, four, and five! There’s a plate for each of us.”"
msgstr "Tito anahesabu sahani nzuri ndogondogo kadili anavyozichukua toka kabatini, \"Moja, mbili, tatu, nne na tano! Sahani zipo za kila mmoja wetu.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego goes to the stoep and places the plates next to the teacups.“One, two, three, four, and ... ?” “I only see four plates,” says Koko, “but we are five people.”"
msgstr "Tito anaenda kwenye eneo aliloandaa na anaweka sahani karibu na vikombe vya chai. \" Moja, mbili, tatu, nne na ...?\" \" Naona sahani nne tu,\" Bibi anasema, \"lakini tuko watu watano.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego counts the biscuits as he takes them from the jar. “One, two, three, four, and five!”"
msgstr "Tito anahesabu biskuti kadili anavyozitoa kutoka kwenye mtungi. \"Moja, mbili, tatu, nne na tano!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego goes to the stoep and places the biscuits on the plates."
msgstr "Tito anaenda kwenye sehemu ya mwinuko katika mazingira ya nyumbani kwao na anaweka biskuti kwenye sahani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“One, two, three, four, and ... ?” “I only see four biscuits,” says Koko, “but we are five people.”"
msgstr "\"Moja, mbili, tatu, nne, na ...?\" \" Naona biskuti nne tu,\" anasema Bibi, \"lakini tupo watu watano.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego is very confused. He knows he has been counting correctly. Before he had five biscuits, and now there are only four. HOW did the biscuits become less?"
msgstr "Tito amechanganyikiwa sana. Anajua alihesabu kwa usahihi. Kabla alikuwa na biskuti tano, na sasa kuna nne tu. Biskuti zimekuwaje pungufu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego counts the sugar cubes as he takes them from the jar. “One, two, three, four, and five!”"
msgstr "Tito anahesabu pakiti za sukari kadili anavyozichukua kutoka kwenye mtungi. \"Moja, mbili, tatu, nne, na tano!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego goes to the stoep and places the sugar cubes on the table. This time, he is sure he hears a giggle. “One, two, three, four, and ... ?” “Five!” shouts a voice from under the table."
msgstr "Tito anaenda kwenye sehemu ya mwinuko katika mazingira ya nyumbani kwao na anaweka pakiti za sukari mezani. Safari hii, ana hakika amesikia kicheko. \" Moja, mbili, tatu, nne, na ...??\" \"Tano!: sauti ya juu ilitokea chini ya meza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tlotlego bends down to look under the table. To his shock, he sees a complete tea set laid out under the table! There are the missing teacup, plate, biscuit, and sugar cube. FIVE!"
msgstr "Tito anainama chini kuangalia chini ya meza. kwa mshtuko, anaona seti ya chai iliyokamilika imewekwa chini ya meza! Hizo ni vikombe, sahani, biskuti na sukari zilizokuwa zimekosekana. TANO!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When Mama and Papa come home from work, they all have tea on the stoep. One, two, three of them having tea at the table, and two of them having tea below!"
msgstr "Baba na mama watakapokuja nyumbani kutoka kazini, wote watapata chai kwenye sehemu ya mwinuko kwenye mazingira ya pale nyumbani kwao. Mmoja, wawili, watatu wao kupata chai mezani, na wawili wao kupata chai chini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The one on the middle"
msgstr "Yule aliye katikati"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Khanyiswa is not the first born. She’s not the last born. She’s the one in the MIDDLE!"
msgstr "Khanyiswa sio mtoto wa kwanza. Yeye sio mtoto wa mwisho. Yeye ni wa katikati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am the middle one. Not the first born. Not the last born. The one in the middle!"
msgstr "Mimi ni wa katikati. Sio mtoto wa kwanza. Sio mtoto wa mwisho. Ni yule wa katikati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The one in the middle can be easy to forget."
msgstr "Yule wa katikati ni rahisi kusahau."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And easy to leave out."
msgstr "Na rahisi kutoka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But that’s okay because I am also the one with IDEAS!"
msgstr "Lakini hiyo ni sawa kwasababu mimi pia nina mawazo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look what I can make from just this cardboard box! A BEAUTIFUL house... with real doors and windows."
msgstr "Angalia ninachoweza kutengeneza kutoka kwenye hili boksi! Nyumba nzuri... yenye milango na madirisha ya uhakika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My house has an extra special bed, and a MAGIC SLIDE."
msgstr "Nyumba yangu ina kitanda cha ziada na bembea ya maajabu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Some days my house is also a shop."
msgstr "Kuna wakati nyumba yangu pia inakuwa duka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And on other days it’s a VERY FANTASTIC show."
msgstr "Na kwa siku zingine inakuwa onyesho zuri la kushangaza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes my house is just for me!"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine nyumba yangu ni kwa ajili yangu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And that’s the best place for me."
msgstr "Na hapo ndipo mahali pazuri zaidi kwangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And sometimes it’s a house for three! I am the middle one. Not the first born. Not the last born. The one in the middle!"
msgstr "Na wakati mwingine ni nyumba yetu watatu! Mimi ni wa katikati. Siyo mtoto wa kwanza. Siyo mtoto wa mwisho. Ni yule wa katikati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The best thing ever"
msgstr "Jambo bora ambalo halikuwahi kutokea"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Muzi loves to build with his toys. But when he leaves them behind to travel to uGogo’s house, he discovers something very special about the world. And he learns something new about himself."
msgstr "Muzi anapenda kujenga na midoli yake. Lakini anawaacha ili kusafiri kwenda nyumbani kwa bibi yake, anagundua kitu cha pekee sana kuhusu Dunia na anajifunza kitu kipya kuhusu yeye mwenyewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Muzi loves to build things. He dreams of building the best thing ever."
msgstr "Muzi anapenda kujenga vitu. Ana ndoto ya kujenga kitu ambacho hakijawahi kutokea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Once he built a shelter for his toys. But it wasn’t the best thing ever."
msgstr "Aliwahi kujenga makazi ya midoli yake. Lakini hayakuwa bora kuliko."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yesterday he built a bridge for his animals. It was a good thing. But not the best..."
msgstr "Jana alijenga daraja kwaajili ya wanyama wake. Ilikuwa kitu kizuri. Lakini si bora..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today Muzi is going to visit uGogo. He is sad. Without his toys, how can he build the best thing ever?"
msgstr "Leo Muzi anaenda kumtembelea bibi. Ana huzuni. Bila hii midoli, anawezaje kujenga kitu bora kuliko\"?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "At the bus stop, Muzi is amazed. He sees red things and blue things. Small things and big things. New things and old things."
msgstr "Kwenye kituo cha basi. Muzi anashangaa. Anaona vitu vyekundu na vitu vya bluu. Vitu vidogo na vitu vikubwa. Vitu vipya na vitu vya zamani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Muzi has a new idea for building the best thing ever."
msgstr "Muzi ana wazo jipya la kujenga kitu ambacho hakijawahi kutokea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On the road to uGogo’s, Muzi finds many things. Long things and short things. Round things and square things."
msgstr "Njiani kuelekea kwa Bibi, Muzi alipata vitu vingi. Vitu virefu na vitu vifupi. Vitu vya mviringo na vitu vilivyokuwa katika umbo la pembe nne."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "By the riverside, Muzi finds more things. Soft things and pointy things. Green things and brown things."
msgstr "Pembeni ya mto, Muzi alipata vitu zaidi. Vitu vya kawaida na vitu vya maana. Vitu vya kijani na vitu vya kahawia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look, Muzi! We are here."
msgstr "Angalia, Muzi! Tupo hapa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "While uGogo bakes for the hungry travellers... Muzi builds."
msgstr "Wakati Bibi huoka kwaajili ya wasafiri wenye njaa... Muzi hujenga."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Gogo, Gogo! says Muzi. The world is full of toys. Look what I can build."
msgstr "Bibi, Bibi! anasema Muzi. Dunia imejaa midoli. Tazama naweza kujenga nini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh, Muzi, laughs Gogo. A new house for me. This is the best thing ever!"
msgstr "Oh, Muzi, anamcheka bibi. Nyumba mpya kwaajili yangu. Hili ni jambo bora haijawahi tokea!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teju's Shadow"
msgstr "Kivuli cha Teju"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teju is worried. Something keeps following him! What could it be?"
msgstr "Teju ana wasiwasi. Kitu flani kinaendelea kumfuatilia! Kinaweza kuwa nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Book Dash, 2019. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Book Dash, 2002. Haki zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s that?”"
msgstr "\"Ni nini hicho?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Teju hides. “It won’t find me here!”"
msgstr "Teju anajificha. \"Hakitanipata hapa!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He runs. “Why are you following me?”"
msgstr "Anakimbia. \"Kwanini unanifuata?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Leave me ALONE!"
msgstr "Niache!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Go away. Go away.GO AWAY! “Teju! What are you doing?” “It won’t go away!” “Your shadow?”"
msgstr ""
"Nenda huko. Nenda huko. NENDA HUKO! \"Teju! unafanya nini?\" \n"
" \"Hakiwezi kuondoka!\" \"Kivuli chako?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“It follows me everywhere! It’s like a super secret spy!”"
msgstr "\"Kinanifuata kila sehemu! Ni kama jasusi wa siri sana!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Well, there’s one way to make a shadow disappear...”"
msgstr "\"Vizuri, kuna njia moja kufanya kivuli kiondoke...\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "MAMA!"
msgstr "MAMA!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Later that night in Teju’s bedroom, the light goes off...  ...and then on. And off... ...and on. Teju can’t sleep."
msgstr "Baadae usiku ule chumbani kwa Teju, Taa ilizimika... ...na ikawaka tena. Na ikazima... ...na ikawaka. Teju anashindwa kulala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "<<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>   <<CLICK>>"
msgstr "<<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>  <<<BOFYA>>>"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“What’s wrong Teju?” “It only goes away in the dark, but I’m scared of the dark!” Mum gives Teju a big hug. “Do you want to see something amazing?”"
msgstr "\"Nini shida Teju?\" \"Kinaondoka kwenye giza tu, lakini naogopa giza!\" Mama anamkumbatia Teju. \"Unataka kuona kitu kizuri cha kushangaza?\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "OOOHHHH! AAAAHH!"
msgstr "OOOHHHH! AAAAHH!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mum and Teju make shadow puppets until he falls asleep."
msgstr "Mama na Teju wanatengeneza vimdoli vya kivuli hadi analala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Cool!” After school, Teju waits for Mum. “I’m bored.” Teju stands up, he jumps, he dances.His shadow does the same."
msgstr "\"Safi!\" Baada ya shule, Teju anamsubiri Mama. \" Nimechoka/sijisikii vizuri.\" Teju anasimama, anarukaruka, anacheza. Kivuli chake kinafanya hivyohivyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When he goes to bed that night, Teju leaves his night Light on. “Goodnight Shadow!”"
msgstr "Alipoenda kulala usiku ule, Teju aliacha taa inawaka. \" Usiku mwema kivuli!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Paint Dat, Plant Day"
msgstr "Kupaka rangi ya Dat, siku ya kupanda"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi enjoys plant day, music day and paint day, and being busy throughout the week. Join in as Avi potters about the house, in this book about noticing and recognising patterns."
msgstr "Avi aliifurahia siku ya kupanda, siku ya muziki na siku ya kupaka rangi, na kuwa na mambo mengi ya kufanya wiki nzima. Ungana nao kadili ambavyo Avi anafinyanga nyumba, katika kitabu hiki kinachohusu kutambua na kujua miundo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi stretches and jumps out of bed. Today is Plant Day."
msgstr "Avi anajinyoosha na kuruka nje ya kitanda. Leo ni siku ya kupanda."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama takes out the seeds. Avi places them carefully in the pots. Small pot, tall pot, square pot. Small pot— Avi waters the plants."
msgstr "Mama anatoa mbegu nje. Avi anaziweka kwenye vyungu kwa uangalifu. Chungu kidogo, chungu kirefu, chungu cha pembe nne. Chungu kidogo -- Avi anamwagilia mimea."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi washes the brushes. Papa mixes the paints. Today is Paint Day. Swish, dip, squash, swirl. Swish, dip— Avi loves mixing the colours."
msgstr "Avi huosha brashi, Baba huchanganya rangi. Leo ni siku ya kupaka rangi. Swish, chovya, boga, zungusha, swish, chovya-- Avi anapenda kuchanganya rangi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today is Fixing Day. Mama and Avi tighten the screws on the table. Tighten, thamp! Tighten, thamp! Avi checks to see if the table is still wobbly."
msgstr "Leo ni siku ya marekebisho. Mama na Avi wanakaza skrubu kwenye meza. Kaza, thamp! kaza, thamp! Avi anakagua kuona kama meza bado inatikisika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today is Cleaning Day. Avi helps Mama and Papa dust everything. Dhup, wipe, cough, clean. Dhup, wipe— ACHOO!"
msgstr "Leo ni siku ya kufanya usafi. Avi humsaidia Mama na Baba kufuta vumbi vitu vyote. Dhup, futa, kukohoa, safisha, Dhup, futa--- ACHOO!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today is Sheet Day. Avi is changing the sheets on the beds. Pull, tuck, pull, tuck, pat-pat. Pull, tuck—"
msgstr "Leo ni siku ya shuka. Avi anabadilisha mashuka kitandani. Vuta, piga, vuta, piga, vuta, funga--"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi lines up all the cushions and pillows on the floor. Cushion, cushion, pillow, bolster. Cushion, cushion— JUMP!"
msgstr "Avi anapanga foronya zote na mito sakafuni. Foronya, Foronya, foronya, mito, kuimarisha, foronya, foronya--- RUKA!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Music Day is Avi’s favourite. No one stops the loud sounds! Dham-dhoom- japh, dham- dhoom- japh. Avi hits the drums again. Dham—"
msgstr "Siku ya muziki ni siku pendwa ya Avi. Hakuna anayezima sauti kubwa! Dham,-dhoom-japh, dham,-dhoom-japh"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is Bird Day. Avi watches the birds with Mama and Papa. Brown bird, slow-walker, long legs. Brown bird—"
msgstr "Ni siku ya ndege. Avi anawatazama ndege na Mama na Baba. Ndege wa kahawia, mtembea polepole, miguu mirefu, ndege wa kahawia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Avi yawns. He is tired but excited about waking up in the morning. Tomorrow is Plant Day again!"
msgstr "Avi anapiga mwayo. Amechoka lakini amefurahia kuhusu kutembea asubuhi. Kesho ni siku ya kupanda tena!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Patterns Are All Around Us. The days, the weeks, the months, and the years always follow a pattern. Look at the days in your week. Is any day kept for a special activity? Make a calendar for yourself and fill it with the patterns you see."
msgstr "Miunganiko iko kila mahali imetuzunguka. Siku, Wiki, Miezi, na Miaka daima hufuata muunganiko. Angalia Siku katia wiki yako. Je, kuna siku yoyote kwaajili ya shughuli maalum? Tengeneza kalenda yako mwenyewe na ijaze miunganiko unayoona."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My little garden"
msgstr "Bustani yangu ndogo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A little boy and his dad find a plot full of litter. Can they turn it into something wonderful?"
msgstr "Kijana mdogo na baba yake waliona shamba lililojaa takataka. Je wanaweza kuligeuza kuwa kitu kizuri?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."
msgstr "Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mama, What's For Lunch"
msgstr "Mama. Tunakula chakula gani mchana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Join Thabo and his sister Tumi for magical lunches with Mama!"
msgstr "Ungana na John na dada yake Tumi kwenye chakula cha maajabu cha mchana na Mama!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Hurry,Thabo. Mama is making lunch,” calls Tumi."
msgstr "''Harakisha.John, Mama anapika chakula cha mchana,'' anaita Tumi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child to describe the picture: “What is the girl doing? What else is happening?”"
msgstr "Mwambie mtoto wako aielezee picha: “Msichana anafanya nini”? Nini kingine kinatokea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Where are you going, Thabo?”"
msgstr "''Unaenda wapi John?''"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: “What do you think the boy is doing? Why do you think the boy is doing that?”"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: “Unafikiri mvulana anafanya nini? Unafikiri kwanini mvulana anafanya vile?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "His friends don’t understand why he chooses lunch over their game, but Thabo has a secret. Mama’s lunches are special."
msgstr "Rafiki zake hawaelewi kwa nini anachagua chakula dhidi ya mchezo wao. Lakini John ana siri. Chakula cha mama cha mchana ni maalumu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point to the boy and ask: “How do you think the boy is feeling? What do you think he is going to do next? Can you also describe the feelings of the other children, how do you think they feel?”"
msgstr "Muonyeshe kwa kumuelekezea kidole mvulana na umuulize: “Unafikiri mvulana anajiskiaje? Unafikiri atafanya nini baadae? Unaweza pia kuelezea hisia za watoto wengine, Unafikiri wanajiskiaje?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On Monday, Mama shapes their food like little bugs that wriggle and crawl, making Tumi shriek in fright. “EEEE!” But they are yummy fruit and vegetables, and not very scary at all."
msgstr "Siku ya Jumatatu, Mama hutengeneza chakula chenye maumbo ya wadudu wadogo wanaotambaa na hivyo kumfanya Tumi alie kwa hofu.''EEE!'' lakini ni matunda matamu na mboga, na sio za kutisha hata kidogo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Point to different images and ask your child to name them. You can ask: “How did they make those shapes out of the food? What foods are red? And what food is green?”"
msgstr "Onyesha picha tofauti kwa kidole na mwambie mtoto wako azipe majina. Unaweza kumuuliza: “Walitengenezaje hayo maumbo kutoka kwenye chakula? Vyakula gani ni vya rangi nyekundu? Na chakula gani ni cha rangi ya kijani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On Tuesday, she makes a lion that roars so loudly the house shakes. “ROAR!” ut it’s just delicious pasta and cheese."
msgstr "Siku ya Jumanne, anatengeneza Simba anayeunguruma kwa sauti kubwa na kutikisa nyumba,'' Mngurumo mkubwa wa Simba!,'' kumbe ni Tambi tamu zenye jibini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Use descriptive words and explanations to talk about pictures. This helps your child learn new words. “Look, they have created a roaring lion out of the pasta and cheese.”\n"
"\n"
"Then mimic the sound of the roaring lion."
msgstr ""
"Tumia maneno na maelezo yanayodadavua na kuzungumzia kuhusu picha. Hii husaidia mtoto wako kujifunza maneno mapya. “Tazama, wametengeneza simba ananguruma kutokana na tambi na jibini.”\n"
"\n"
"Halafu igiza sauti ya simba ananguruma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On Wednesday, Mama creates a chicken that wakes up the whole street. “CLUCK CLUCK PAKAA!” But it’s just a plate of juicy fruit."
msgstr "Siku ya Jumatano, mama anatengeneza kuku ambaye anawaamsha wote mtaani.“KOKORIKOOOOOOO!” Lakini ni sahani tu ya matunda ya juisi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Point to the image and ask your child what the picture looks like. You can ask: “What animal did they make? (mimic the sound of a chicken). What did they use for the chicken’s tail? And what did they use for its beak?” \n"
"\n"
"You can ask: Have you seen chickens in our area?"
msgstr ""
"Onyeshea picha na muulize mtoto wako picha inafanana na nini. Unaweza kuuliza: “Walitengeneza mnyama gani? (Igiza sauti ya kuku). Walitumia nini kutengeneza mkia wa kuku? Na walitumia nini kutengeneza mdomo?”\n"
"\n"
"Unaweza kumuuliza: Umeona kuku katika eneo letu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On Thursday, she builds a noisy truck. Thabo and Tumi cover their ears. “VROOOM!” But it’s a sweet strawberry jam sandwich."
msgstr "Siku ya alhamisi, alitengeneza lori lenye kelele. John na Tumi waliziba masikio yao. ^VRUUUUM!^ Lakini ni mkate mtamu wa jamu ya stroberi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What did they make here? What did they use to make it? Then say, “oh no! that’s a noisy truck, let's cover our ears.”"
msgstr "Muulize: Walitengeneza nini hapa? Walitumia nini kutengenezea hiyo? Halafu sema, “oh hapana! hiyo ni sauti ya gari kubwa ya mizigo, na tuzibe masikio yetu.”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "On Friday, Mama makes a beautiful garden filled with flowers, birds and ladybugs. “TWEET TWEET!” But it’s healthy pap, beans and a crunchy salad"
msgstr "Siku ya ijumaa, Mama hutengeneza bustani nzuri inayojaa maua, ndege na wadudu.^TWIIT TWIIT!^ Lakini ni ugali wenye afya, maharage na kachumbari"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many insects can you see? And how many trees can you see? What colors are the leaves on the trees? Are they all the same shape?”"
msgstr "Muulize: “Unaweza kuona wadudu wangapi? Na unaweza kuona miti mingapi? Majani ya kwenye miti yana rangi gani? Je, yote yana umbo sawa?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“Mama, what’s for lunch?” asks Tumi. “Yes, Mama,” says Thabo. “What are you making today?”"
msgstr "^Mama, tunakula nini mchana? Tumi anauliza. ^Ndio, mama,^ anasema John. ^Unaandaa nini leo?^"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “How many people are sitting down and how many are standing? What can you see that is blue? And what can you see that is pink?”"
msgstr "Muulize: “Ni watu wangapi wamekaa chini na ni wangapi wamesimama? Unaweza kuona nini chenye rangi ya bluu? Na nini unaweza kuona chenye rangi ya pinki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thabo and Tumi can’t wait another second. Their tummies are grumbling. Finally, Mama is ready. “What is it Mama?” asks Thabo, licking his lips."
msgstr "John na Tumi hawawezi kusubiri kwa sekunde zaidi. Matumbo yao yanaunguruma. Mwisho, Mama amemaliza kuandaa chakula. ^Ni nini hiyo mama?^ John anauliza, akilamba midomo yake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: “Why do you think the boy is licking his lips? What do you do when you are hungry?”"
msgstr "Muulize: “Unafikiri kwanini mvulana analamba midomo yake? Unafanya nini unapokuwa na hasira?”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s Thabo, Tumi and Mama! “Mmm, our favourite, your famous stew and rice.” “Thank you, Mama!”"
msgstr "Ni John, Tumi na Mama! ^Mmm, ni chakula tunachokipenda, kitoweo chako maarufu na wali.\". \"Asante mama!\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: “Yey, the food is finally ready!” Ask: How many dishes can you see? How many people do you think are going to eat? How do you think the boy is feeling now that the food is ready? How do you normally feel when you are given food?”"
msgstr "Sema: “Yey, hatimaye chakula kipo tayari!” Unaweza kuona vyombo vingapi? Unafikiri ni watu wangapi wanaenda kula? Unafikiri mvulana anajiskiaje sasa kwamba chakula kipo tayari? Kwa kawaida huwa unajiskiaje pale unapopewa chakula?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What will Mama make on Sunday?"
msgstr "Mama ataandaa nini siku ya Jumapili?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Ask: “Can you name the different foods in the picture? What food do you like? And what food don’t you like?\n"
"\n"
"Let’s go to the kitchen and cut up some food into interesting shapes like they did in the story!”"
msgstr ""
"Muulize: “Unaweza kutaja majina mbalimbali ya vyakula vya kwenye picha? Na ni chakula gani hukipendi?\n"
"\n"
"Twende jikoni tukakate baadhi ya vyakula katika maumbo ya kuvutia kama walivyofanya kwenye hadithi!”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's go on a litter hunt"
msgstr "Wacha tuendelee kuondoa takataka"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The yard is a mess. How will the children clean up?"
msgstr "Uwanja ni mchafu sana, Je watoto watausafishaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Papa says, “This yard is a MESS. The wind blew the rubbish in.” Mama says, “Let’s go on a litter hunt. First look for tins.” Papa says, “Wear these gloves.” Yuck!"
msgstr "Baba anasema, '' Huu uwanja ni MCHAFU SANA. Upepo ulileta takataka.\" Mama anasema, ''Twendeni tukaondoe takataka. Kwanza angalieni makopo.''Baba anasema,'' Vaa glavu hizi,'' Uchafu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’re going on a tin hunt. We look up high and down low. We look under the bushes and against the fence."
msgstr "Tunakwenda kuokota makopo. Tunatazama juu na chini kabisa. Tunaangalia chini ya vichaka na kwenye uzio."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’ve found red tins and green tins, rusty tins and shiny tins, clean tins and dirty tins. Yuck!"
msgstr "Tumepata makopo mekundu na ya kijani, makopo yenye kutu na makopo yanayong'aa, makopo masafi na makopo machafu. Uchafu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What must we do with all these tins? Find a bin and put them in! Now look for plastic."
msgstr "Tufanye nini na makopo haya? Tafuta pipa na uweke humo! sasa tafuta plastiki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’re going on a plastic hunt. We look up high and down low. We look behind the chicken coop and in front of the house."
msgstr "Tunakwenda kuondoa takataka za plastiki, Tunaangalia juu na chini kabisa. Tunatazama nyuma ya banda la kuku na mbele ya nyumba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’ve found milk bottles and bottle tops, shopping bags and sucker sticks, straws and broken buckets. Yuck!"
msgstr "Tumepata chupa za maziwa na vifuniko vya chupa, mifuko ya kubebea vitu na mirija ya kunywea vinywaji na ndoo zilizopasuka. Uchafu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What must we do with all this plastic? Find a bin and put it in! Now look for paper."
msgstr "Tufanye nini na hizi plastic zote? Tafuta pipa na uweke humo! sasa tafuta karatasi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’re going on a paper hunt. We look up high and down low. We look near the water barrel and on top of the bench."
msgstr "Tunakwenda kuokota karatasi. Tunaangalia juu na chini kabisa. Tunaangalia karibu na pipa la maji na juu ya benchi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We’ve found wet paper and dry paper, cardboard boxes and newspaper, old paper plates and dirty tissues. Yuck!"
msgstr "Tumepata karatasi iliyoloana na karatasi kavu, boksi na gazeti, sahani za karatasi za zamani na tishu chafu. Uchafu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What must we do with all this paper? Find a bin and put it in! What else can you look for? Hmm ..."
msgstr "Tufanye nini na karatasi zote hizi? Tafuta pipa na uweke humo! Nini kingine unaweza kuangalia? Hmm..."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "There’s no more mess! Wow! This place is so clean. Thanks, litter hunters."
msgstr "Hakuna tena uchafu sana! Waoo! Mahali hapa ni pasafi sana. Asante, waokotaji wa takataka."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You deserve a treat! And remember ... what must you do with your litter? Find a bin and put it in!"
msgstr "Unastahili pongezi! Na kumbuka... unalazimika kufanya nini na takataka zako? Tafuta pipa na uweke humo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep?"
msgstr "Unalalaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you sleep with one eye open? Can you sleep in a tree? Pula has a bed, but he wants to know how other creatures sleep."
msgstr "Unaweza kulala jicho moja likiwa wazi? Unaweza kulala kwenye mti? Pula ana kitanda, ila anataka kujua viumbe vingine vinalalaje."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, bird? I fly in my sleep"
msgstr "Unalalaje ndege? ninaruka usingizini"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, bat? I sleep upside down."
msgstr "Unalalaje, popo? Ninalala kichwa chini miguu juu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, bullfrog? I rest on my side"
msgstr "Unalalaje Chura? Napumzika kwa upande"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, octopus? I change colour in my dreams."
msgstr "Unalala namna gani, Pweza? nabadilisha rangi kwenye ndoto zangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, duck? We take turns to guard each other."
msgstr "Unalala namna gani bata? Tunapeana zamu kulindana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, baby owl? I sleep on my face."
msgstr "Unalalaje, bundi mtoto? Nalalia uso wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, otter? We sleep holding hands."
msgstr "Unalalaje ota? Tunalala huku tumeshikana mikono."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, walrus? I sleep on the land and under the water."
msgstr "Unallalaje walrus? Nalala juu ya ardhi na chini ya maji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, giraffe? We sleep on each other."
msgstr "Unalalaje twiga? Tunalala tukiwa tumeegamiana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, meerkat? We sleep in a heap."
msgstr "Unalalaje, miakati? Tunalala kwenye lundo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you sleep, Pula? Good night! Sleep tight!"
msgstr "Unalalaje, pula? Usiku mwema! lala vyema!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grandpa Farouk’s garden"
msgstr "Bustani ya Babu Faruku"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Amir loves Grandpa Farouk’s garden. But it’s dying. What can Amir do to help?"
msgstr "Amiri anaipenda bustani ya Babu Faruku. Lakini inakufa. Amiri anaweza kufanya nini kusaidia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Deep in the city, surrounded by houses and bricks and tar, you’ll find Grandpa Farouk’s garden."
msgstr "Ndani kabisa ya Jiji, kumezungukwa na nyumba na matofali na lami, utaikuta bustani ya Babu Faruku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Amir visits Grandpa once a week. He loves the leaves and flowers and trees."
msgstr "Amiri huwa anamtembelea mara moja kwa wiki. Anapenda majani na maua na miti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Amir helps to water the plants. He helps with the compost, and works with his Grandpa all day."
msgstr "Amiri anasaidia kumwagilia mimea. Anasaidia kuweka mboji, na hufanya kazi na babu yake siku nzima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When they finish, they feast on a harvest of fruit. One day, Grandpa didn’t eat his pear. “What’s wrong?” asked Amir."
msgstr "Wanapomaliza, wanasherehekea mavuno ya matunda. Siku moja, Babu hakula peasi lake. \" shida ni nini?\" Amiri anauliza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“My garden is dying,” replied Grandpa. “Why?” asked Amir. “Look closely,” said Grandpa. “Some pests are eating the plants.”"
msgstr "\"Bustani yangu inakufa\" Babu alijibu. \"Kwanini?\" Amiri aliuliza. \"Angalia kwa karibu,\" alisema Babu. \"Kuna wadudu wanakula mimea.\""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "“We need ladybirds!” said Grandpa. “They are the bugs that eat the pests that kill the plants. Without ladybirds, the garden will die.” “I’ll bring you a bug or two,” said Amir."
msgstr "\"Tunahitaji wadudu\" alisema Babu. \"Ni mende ambao wanakula wadudu wanaoua mimea. Bila wadudu hao, bustani itakufa.\" \" Nitakuletea mdudu mmoja au wawili,\" amiri alisema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "For a whole week, Amir looked and searched and collected. He found one ladybird on the sports field."
msgstr "Kwa wiki nzima, Amiri aliangalia na alitafuta na alikusanya. Alikuta mdudu mmoja kwenye eneo la michezo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Two more at the shop. Three at the park."
msgstr "Wawili zaidi dukani. Watatu mbugani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And four behind the TV. Next week, Amir went to visit Grandpa Farouk, and showed him his jar of ten bugs. “You’ve done well, oh my boy, you’ve done well,” Grandpa said, with a tear in his eye."
msgstr "Na wanne nyuma ya TV. Wiki iliyofuata, Amiri alienda kumtembelea Babu Faruku, na alimuonesha chupa yenye wadudu kumi. \"umefanya vizuri, oh kijana wangu, umefanya vizuri,\" Babu alisema, akitokwa na machozi machoni mwake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Grandpa was very happy. The ladybirds were very hungry!"
msgstr "Babu alifurahi sana. Wadudu walikuwa na njaa sana!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The ladybirds ate the pests, and the garden blossomed."
msgstr "Nyenyere walikula wadudu waharibifu na bustani ikachanua."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "From that day on, Grandpa Farouk’s garden did what gardens should do. It grew and grew and grew."
msgstr "Kuanzia siku ile na kuendelea, bustani ya Babu Faruku ilifanya kile ambacho bustani zinatakiwa kufanya. Ilikua na kukua na kukua."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Colours"
msgstr "Rangi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A white bear likes colours a lot, and he falls in love with new ones all the time. Join him as he explores a world of rainbows."
msgstr "Dubu mweupe hupenda sana rangi, na huwa anapenda nyingine mpya kila wakati. Ungana nae anapochunguza dunia ya upinde wa mvua."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Room to Read, 2015. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "Haki zote zimehifadhiwa © Room to Read, 2015. Imetolewa chini ya CC BY 4.0 license."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Bear likes colours."
msgstr "Dubu hupenda rangi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her ears are yellow."
msgstr "Sasa, maskio yake ni ya njano."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her tummy is brown."
msgstr "Sasa, Tumbo lake ni la kahawia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her mouth is red."
msgstr "Sasa, Mdomo wake ni mwekundu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her hands are blue."
msgstr "Sasa, mikono yake ni ya bluu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her back is green."
msgstr "Sasa, Mgongo wake ni wa kijani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, her legs are pink."
msgstr "Sasa, Miguu yake ni ya pinki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now, Bear is colourful!"
msgstr "Sasa, Dubu ana rangi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh no! Where did all her the_colours go?"
msgstr "Hapana! Rangi zake zote zimeenda wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Circles in the park"
msgstr "Miduara kwenye mbuga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Golu and Tama go to the park to play. What do they see all around them? This wordless book introduces circles, semi-circles and quarter-circles."
msgstr "Golu na Tama wanaenda mbugani kucheza. Wanaona vilivyowazunguka? Hiki kitabu kisicho na maneno kinatambulisha miduara, nusu miduara na robo miduara."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "© Pratham Books, 2021. Some rights reserved. Released under CC BY 4.0 license."
msgstr "© Vitabu vya Pratham, 2021. Haki zingine zimehifadhiwa. Imetolewa chini ya leseni ya CC BY 4.0."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Circle Semi-circle Quarter-cricle How many semi-circles make a circle? How many quarter-circles make a semi-circle?"
msgstr "Nusu duara-Robo-duara Je ni nusu duara ngapi hufanya duara? Ni robo duara ngapi hufanya nusu duara?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Discuss the book’s cover.  Ask: What do you see? What do you think this story is about?"
msgstr "Jadilli jalada la kitabu. Uliza: Unaona nini? Unafikiri hadithi hii inahusu nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lefa's Bath"
msgstr "Lefa anaoga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Lefa wants her bath, but where does all the water go?"
msgstr "Lefa anataka kuoga, lakini maji yake yote yameenda wapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This work is licensed under a [Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."
msgstr "Kazi hii imepewa Kibali na [Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 Licence](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: what is the girl doing? Why do you think she is doing that? What animals are those? How many are there?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Msichana anafanya nini? Unafikiri ni kwanini anafanya hivyo? hao ni wanyama gani? Wako wangapi?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mimic sounds and actions from the story, like the cows drinking the water."
msgstr "Igiza sauti na vitendo kutoka kwenye hadithi, kama vile n’gombe wanakunywa maji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: oh no! Where has all the water gone? How do you think the girl is feeling?"
msgstr "Sema: Oh hapana! maji yameenda wapi? Unafikiri msichana anajiskiaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use descriptive words to talk about the pictures. Say: she is pouring water from her yellow bucket into the large orange bath."
msgstr "Tumia maneno ya maelezo kuzungumzia picha. Sema: Msichana anamimina maji kutoka kwenye ndoo yake ya njano na kumiminia katika beseni kubwa la kuogea la rangi ya machungwa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: look! The ducks are splashing in the water! What do you think will happen next?"
msgstr "Sema: Tazama bata wanarusha maji! Je unadhani nini kitatokea baada ya hapo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: oh no! The bath has been emptied again! How did that happen? How is the girl feeling now?"
msgstr "Sema: Oh hapana! Benseni la kuogea halina maji tena! Nini kimetokea? Je msichana atajiskiaje sasa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: What is the girl doing now? What animal can we see coming closer?"
msgstr "Uliza: Msichana anafanya nini sasa hivi? Ni mnyama gani tunamuona anakuja kwa karibu?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask your child: What is the pig doing? What is happening to the water? Can the girl see what is happening?"
msgstr "Muulize mtoto wako: Je nguruwe anafanya nini? Nini kinatokea kwenye maji? Je msichana anaweza kuona nini kinatokea?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say: oh no! What happened to the bath now? How is the girl feeling?"
msgstr "Sema: Oh hapana! Nini kinatokea kwenye beseni la kuogea sasa? Je msichana anajiskiaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use your voice and face to demonstrate emotions from the pictures. Say: look, she is crying? Why do you think she is feeling sad? How do you think the animals are feeling?"
msgstr "Tumia sauti na uso wako kuonyesha hisia kutoka kwenye picha. Sema: Tazama, analia? unafikiri ni kwanini anajiskia huzuni? Unafikiri wanyama wanajiskiaje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: what are the animals doing? Why are they doing that? Say: Can you count the buckets of water? Are they all the same colour? What colours can you see?"
msgstr "Uliza: Wanyama wanafanya nini? Kwanini wanafanya hivyo? Sema: Unaweza kuhesabu ndoo za maji? Je wote wana rangi moja? Je unaweza kuona rangi gani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask: How do you think the girl is feeling now? Why?"
msgstr "Uliza: Unafikiri msichana anajiskiaje sasa? Kwanini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Reflect on the story with your child. Ask: What did you think about the story? How would you feel if you were in the story? What would you have done?"
msgstr "Tafakari juu ya hadithi na mtoto wako. Uliza: Ulifikiri nini kuhusu hadithi? Ungejiskiaje kama ungekuwa kwenye hadithi? Ungefanya nini?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "List of Things"
msgstr "Orodha ya vitu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Make a list of healthy activities that you like to do. Here are some suggestions:\n"
"* Listening to your favourite music\n"
"* Going for a walk (if possible)\n"
"* Doing some exercise\n"
"* Drinking a cup of tea by yourself\n"
"* Calling up a friend\n"
"* Singing, dancing, praying, or reading\n"
"* Sitting in the sun with your eyes closed\n"
"* Watching your favourite TV show\n"
"\n"
"Pick one and do it today!"
msgstr ""
"Tengeneza orodha ya shughuli zinazoleta afya unazopenda kufanya. Haya ni baadhi ya mapendekezo:\n"
"* Kusikiliza muziki unaoupenda\n"
"* Kwenda matembezini (kama inawezekana)\n"
"* Kufanya mazoezi\n"
"* Kunywa kikombe cha chai peke yako\n"
"* Kumpigia rafiki simu\n"
"* Kuimba, kucheza, kusali, au kusoma\n"
"* Kuketi juani huku umefumba macho\n"
"* Kutazama kipindi cha runinga unachokipenda\n"
"\n"
"Chagua shughuli moja na uifanye leo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a moment for yourself first."
msgstr "Chukua muda kwa ajili yako mwenyewe kwanza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is great to hear you are feeling positive today. You make a real difference for your family!"
msgstr "Inafurahisha kusikia unajisikia vizuri leo. Unafanya mabadiliko ya kweli kwa familia yako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Life has its great and hard moments – that is okay. You are on the right track."
msgstr "Maisha yana nyakati ngumu na nzuri – hiyo ni sawa. Uko kwenye njia sahihi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is normal to have hard days as a parent. Take a deep breath and know you are not alone!"
msgstr "Ni kawaida kuwa na siku ngumu kama mzazi. Vuta pumzi ndefu na ujue hauko peke yako!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Creating time and space for children to play is as important as eating and sleeping!"
msgstr "Kutengeneza muda na nafasi kwaajili ya watoto kucheza ni muhimu kama ilivyo kula na kulala!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When you join your child in playful activities, you take their learning to the next level. You might even have some fun yourself."
msgstr "Unapojiunga na mtoto wako katika shughuli za kucheza, unapelekea kujifunza kwao kuwa kwenye kiwango cha juu. Unaweza hata kujifurahisha mwenyewe."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes children play with friends, and other times, on their own. Sometimes play is busy and loud, and other times it is quiet and relaxed. No matter what it looks like, when children play, they learn. Today we will look at ways you can support your child through play. You don’t need special toys or a lot of time. What’s important is that you have some fun together."
msgstr "Wakati mwingine watoto hucheza na marafiki, na wakati mwingine peke yao. Wakati mwingine wanacheza sana na kwa sauti na nyakati zingine kunakuwa na ukimya na utulivu. Haijalishi inavyoonekana, watoto wanapocheza wanajifunza. Leo tutaangalia njia ambazo unaweza kuzitumia kumsaidia mtoto wako kupitia mchezo. Hauna haja ya kuwa na midoli maalumu au muda mwingi. Jambo muhimu ni kuwa na furaha pamoja."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "In @global.app_name, we use the image of a garden to think about what children need in their lives to grow and thrive. Let’s see how play forms a part of the garden image."
msgstr "Katika @global.app_name, tunatumia picha ya bustani kufikiri kuhusu nini wanahitaji watoto katika maisha yao kukua na kustawi. Hembu tuone ni kwa namna gani mchezo unafanya sehemu ya picha ya bustani."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "In the same way that fertiliser boosts plant growth, playing with your child is the magic ingredient that supercharges their learning and development."
msgstr "Kama jinsi ilivyo mbolea, huongeza ukuaji wa mmea, kucheza na mtoto wako ni kiungo cha muhimu sana ambacho husaidia kujifunza kwake na ukuaji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fertiliser or “plant food” boosts the quality of the soil around the plant and the plant’s growth. When you sprinkle playfulness throughout your interactions with your child, it will make a big difference to their development. It doesn’t have to be a lot at once, but doing it regularly can improve your relationship while also helping your child learn important skills."
msgstr ""
"Mbolea au’’Chakula cha mmea’’ huongeza ubora wa udongo karibu na mmea na ukuaji wa mmea. Vivyo hivyo, mwingiliano wa kucheza na mtoto wako utaongeza uwezo wake wa kujifunza.\n"
"Ukijigawa na kuwa sehemu ya mchezo na mtoto wako muda wote, italeta mabadiliko makubwa katika ukuaji wake, si lazima iwe kwa kiasi kikubwa kwa mara moja, ila kwa kufanya mara kwa mara inaboresha uhusiano wako, huku pia ikimsaidia mtoto wako kujifunza juzi muhimu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "There is no right or wrong way to play. The important thing is to have fun together."
msgstr "Hakuna njia sahihi au mbaya ya kucheza. Kitu cha muhimu ni kufurahia pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some ideas for supporting your child through play:"
msgstr "Haya ni baadhi ya mawazo mbalimbali ya njia tofauti za kumsaidia mtoto wako kupitia mchezo:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Create space and time for children to play.**\n"
"\n"
"Children enjoy playing in the presence of their parents. Create space for them to play around you. Give your child praise and encouragement as they play."
msgstr ""
"**Tengeneza nafasi na muda wa watoto kucheza.**\n"
"\n"
"Watoto hufurahia kucheza mbele ya wazazi wao. Watengenezee nafasi ya kucheza karibu yako. Msifie mtoto wako na mtie moyo wanapocheza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Join your child in their play from time to time.** \n"
"Look for opportunities to sit down and engage in a positive way with what your child is doing. Even 10 minutes will boost your child’s development."
msgstr ""
"**Jiunge na mtoto wako katika mchezo wake mara kwa mara.**\n"
"Tafuta fursa ili kukaa chini na kushiriki kwa njia chanya na kile anachofanya mtoto wako. Hata dakika kumi itaongeza maendeleo ya mtoto wako."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Connecting with your child in a playful way every day helps your child to feel close to you, and it helps them to grow and learn. Joining your child in play does not mean taking over what they are doing or telling them what to do differently. It means being part of the activity in a way that your child will enjoy."
msgstr "Kuungana na mtoto wako kwa njia ya kimichezo kila siku husaidia mtoto wako kujiskia yuko karibu na wewe, na humsaidia kukua na kujifunza. Kujiunga na mtoto wako kwa njia ya kimchezo haimaanishi ni kumnyang'anya anachofanya au kumwambia afanye nini tofauti. Inamaanisha kuwa sehemu ya shughuli kwa mtindo ambao mtoto wako atafurahia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Keep it joyful and fun!**\n"
"Being playful does not mean that your child won’t respect you or take you seriously: play actually helps to strengthen your relationship with your child. And when relationships are strong, dealing with stress and challenges become easier."
msgstr ""
"**Endelea kufanya iwe ya furaha na kuburudisha!**\n"
"Kuwa kimchezo haimaanishi kuwa mtoto wako hatakuheshimu au kutokukuchukulia kwa uzito unaotakiwa: kimsingi mchezo husaidia kuimarisha uhusiano wenu na mtoto wako. Na pale ambapo mahusiano ni imara, kushughulika na msongo wa mawazo na changamoto inakuwa rahisi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When I first heard that playing with my child was important, I was not interested in trying it. My father never used to play with me when I was a child. I didn’t think it was something that parents do. But one day, I saw my child playing outside and I decided to take a closer look. I was actually amazed at what my child had built with just rocks, sticks and some cardboard boxes. I told my child I thought that it looked really great. Together we created animals using cardboard pieces and some sticks. It was quite fun to build something together, and to see how much my child enjoyed it.\n"
"\n"
"I really like that ParentApp has suggestions for different activities that I can do with my child. It makes it easier for me to decide what to do when my child and I are together."
msgstr ""
"Mara ya kwanza niliposikia kwamba kucheza na mtoto wangu ni muhimu, sikuvutiwa kujaribu. Baba yangu hakuwahi kucheza na mimi nilipokuwa mtoto, sikufikiria kuwa ni jambo ambalo wazazi wanafanya. Lakini siku moja nilimuona mtoto wangu anacheza nje, niliamua kuangalia kwa ukaribu. Kwa kweli nilishangazwa na kile mtoto wangu alichokuwa amejenga kwa mawe na kwa vijiti tu na baadhi ya maboksi. Nilimwambia mtoto wangu nadhani inaonekana nzuri kweli. Pamoja tukatengeneza wanyama kwa kutumia mawe, vipande vya maboksi na baadhi ya vijiti. Ilikuwa ni furaha sana kujenga kitu pamoja na kuona jinsi mtoto wangu alivyofurahi.\n"
"\n"
"Nimeipenda sana Programu ya wazazi ya malezi ina mapendekezo ya shughuli mbalimbali ambazo naweza kufanya na mtoto wangu. inafanya iwe rahisi kwangu kuamua nini cha kufanya tukiwa pamoja na mtoto wangu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Did you know that you can use play to your advantage?"
msgstr "Ulijua kwamba unaweza kutumia kucheza kwa faida yako?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Playful interactions can help your child cooperate and follow instructions."
msgstr "Ukishiriki kucheza unaweza kumsaidia mtoto wako kushirikiana na kufuata maelekezo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes children don’t want to cooperate or listen, which is very frustrating for parents. Our first reaction might be to yell, scream or threaten our child so that they will listen or do as we say. This may seem like a good idea in the moment, but it doesn’t help us or our children long term.  \n"
"Because children love to play games, be silly and have fun, you can use this to help your child cooperate and complete tasks. They won’t even realise they are doing as they are told!"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine watoto hawataki kushirikiana au kusikiliza, jambo ambalo linachanganya wazazi.  Kitu tunachofanya cha kwanza inaweza kuwa ni kuwakaripia, kuwagombeza au kuwatisha watoto wetu ili wasikie au wafanye kama tunavyowaambia. Hili linaweza kuonekana kama ni wazo zuri kwa wakati huo, lakini haitusaidii sisi au watoto wetu  kwa kipindi kirefu. Kwa Sababu watoto wanapenda kucheza michezo, kufanya mizaha, na kufanya vichekesho vya kujifurahisha, unaweza kutumia hii kusaidia mtoto wako kushirikiana na kukamilisha kazi. Hawawezi kufikiria hata kuwa wanafanya kama walivyoambiwa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is normal to feel frustrated when our children don’t cooperate. But sometimes it can be more effective to work *with* your child than *against* them."
msgstr "Ni kawaida kujiskia kuchanganyikiwa pale watoto wetu wanapokuwa hawatoi ushirikiano. Lakini wakati mwingine inaweza kuwa na matokeo zaidi kufanya kazi *na* mtoto wako kuliko kufanya kazi *dhidi* yake."

