#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Book activities offer many opportunities to help children learn key life skills. \n"
"\n"
"Here are some ideas for using books and stories to help children build their social and emotional skills."
msgstr ""
"Shughuli za vitabu hutoa fursa nyingi za kuwasaidia watoto kujifunza stadi muhimu za maisha.\n"
"\n"
"Haya hapa ni baadhi ya mawazo ya kutumia vitabu na hadithi ili kuwasaidia watoto, kujenga ujuzi wao wa kijamii na kihisia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use stories to discuss different feelings, experiences and actions."
msgstr "Tumia hadithi kujadili hisia, uzoefu na vitendo tofauti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This helps children better understand their own experiences, and the behaviours of others too."
msgstr "Hii huwasaidia watoto kuelewa vyema uzoefu wao wenyewe, na tabia za wengine pia.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watch this video for an example of how you can use stories to build your child’s understanding of different emotions and behaviours."
msgstr "Tazama video hii kama mfano wa jinsi unavyoweza kutumia hadithi kujenga uelewa wa mtoto wako kuhusu hisia na tabia tofauti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Three easy ways to use book activities to build your child’s skills:\n"
"1. Talk about what the characters are feeling\n"
"2. Ask questions about what the characters are doing and why\n"
"3. Reflect together on the story and what you have learned"
msgstr ""
"Njia tatu rahisi za kutumia shughuli za vitabu kujenga stadi za maisha:\n"
"1. Zungumzia kuhusu wahusika wanavyojisikia\n"
"2. Uliza maswali kuhusu  wahusika wanafanya nini na  kwanini\n"
"3. Tafakari kile kilichotokea kwenye hadithi  na kile ulichojifunza.\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Small actions, big results! Parents who practice at home get better results.\n"
"\n"
"For your home practice:\n"
"🤝 Use challenging moments as an opportunity to model healthy coping skills.\n"
"📖 Use story books to learn about different feelings and actions.\n"
"😌 Setbacks and challenges are a normal part of life. Remember to be kind to yourself."
msgstr ""
"Vitendo kidogo, matokeo makubwa! Wazazi wanaofanya mazoezi kwa vitendo nyumbani wanapata matokeo mazuri. Hii ni kwa mazoezi yako ya nyumbani:\n"
"🤝 Tumia nyakati zenye changamoto kama fursa ya kuiga ujuzi mzuri kiafya wa kukabiliana na hali hiyo.\n"
"📖Tumia hadithi kujifunza kuhusu hisia, mawazo na vitendo tofauti.\n"
"😌Vikwazo na changamoto ni vitu vya kawaida kwenye maisha. Kumbuka kujitendea wema wewe mwenyewe."

