msgid "That’s why every ParentApp module starts with a “Relax” activity to help you slow down and take a moment for yourself."
msgstr "Ni kwasababu hiyo kila mada ya programu ya wazazi ya malezi inaanza na shughuli ya \"kupumzika\" kukusaidia kupunguza kasi na kupata muda kwaajili yako mwenyewe."

