msgstr "Vuta pumzi mara Tatu"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Close your eyes. \n"
"\n"
"Use the magic power of three to stay connected and relax.\n"
"\n"
"Breathe in to the count of three. 1, 2, 3. \n"
"Breathe out to the count of three. 1, 2, 3. \n"
"Breathe in to the count of three. 1, 2, 3. \n"
"Breathe out to the count of three. 1, 2, 3.\n"
"\n"
"Do you feel any different? Deep breathing helps our whole body and mind to calm down. \n"
"\n"
"Well done on taking a pause."
msgstr ""
"Funga macho yako.\n"
"Tumia nguvu ya maajabu ya tatu kubaki kwenye muunganiko na pumzika.\n"
"Vuta pumzi ndani na uhesabu mpaka tatu 1,2,3\n"
"Toa pumzi nje na uhesabu mpaka tatu 1,2,3\n"
